#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/community/_index.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Community"
msgstr "Comunidade"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Whether it be to solve a problem or to contribute in any way, the Xfce communities are a good place to get help or to share your ideas. You might also want to have a look at the communities of the different distributions which provide Xfce.\n"
msgstr "Tanto se se trata de resolver un problema ou de contribuír de algunha maneira, a comunidade Xfce é un bo lugar para obter axuda ou compartir as súas ideas. Tamén pode querer consultar á comunidade das diferentes distribucións que fornece Xfce.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mailing lists"
msgstr "Listas de correo"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Almost all development and coordination work is taking place on the Xfce mailing lists. A summary of all lists is available at [mail.xfce.org](https://mail.xfce.org). There is also a user-specific list where you can ask questions and freely discuss about the desktop.\n"
msgstr "Case todas as tarefas de desenvolvemento e coordinación teñen lugar nas listas de correo Xfce. En [mail.xfce.org](https://mail.xfce.org) está dispoñíbel un resumo de todas as listas. Tamén hai unha lista específica do usuario onde pode facer preguntas e falar libremente sobre o escritorio.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "**NOTE:** In order to post to these lists, you must first subscribe.\n"
msgstr "**NOTA**: para poder publicar nestas listas, primeiro debe subscribirse.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Matrix"
msgstr "Matrix"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "If you have a problem that you cannot resolve, you might want to try asking a question in our Matrix channel [#xfce](https://matrix.to/#/#xfce:matrix.org). The channel has several active users. It is recommended that you consult the [documentation](https://docs.xfce.org/) about your problem before asking your question.\n"
msgstr "Se ten un problema que non pode resolver, é posíbel que queira probar a facer unha pregunta na nosa canle Matix [#xfce](https://matrix.to/#/#xfce:matrix.org). A canle ten varios usuarios activos. Recoméndase que consulte a [documentación](https://docs.xfce.org/) sobre o problema antes de facer a súa pregunta.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Forums"
msgstr "Foros"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "For users who prefer forums, the [Xfce Forum](https://forum.xfce.org/) is the place to be. Active contributors will be able to help you, but please do not use it for bug reports.\n"
msgstr "Para os usuarios que prefiren foros, o [Foro Xfce](https://forum.xfce.org/) é o lugar onde acudir. Os colaboradores activos poderán axudalo, lembre non empregalo para os informes de fallos.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/community/_index.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "Social Networks"
msgstr "Redes sociais"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/community/_index.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can follow us on the official [Mastodon account](https://floss.social/@xfce) or [Twitter account](https://twitter.com/xfceofficial)\n"
msgstr "Pode seguirnos na conta oficial de[ Mastodon](https://floss.social/@xfce) ou na conta de [Twitter](https://twitter.com/xfceofficial)\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/_index.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "About"
msgstr "Sobre"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/_index.md:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce is a lightweight desktop environment for UNIX-like operating systems. It aims to be fast and low on system resources, while still being visually appealing and user friendly.\n"
msgstr "O Xfce é un contorno de escritorio lixeiro para sistemas operativos como UNIX. Pretende ser rápido e lixeiro no uso dos recursos do sistema, aínda asi tamén procura ser atractivo visualmente así como doado de usar.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/_index.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce embodies the traditional UNIX philosophy of modularity and re-usability. It consists of a number of components that provide the full functionality one can expect of a modern desktop environment. They are packaged separately and you can pick among the available packages to create the optimal personal working environment.\n"
msgstr "O Xfce abraza a filosofía tradicional de UNIX da utilización de módulos e reutilización. Consiste nunha serie de compoñentes que fornecen a funcionalidade completa que se pode agardar dun contorno de escritorio moderno. Ditos compoñentes están empaquetados por separado e pode escoller entre os paquetes dispoñíbeis para crear o contorno persoal ideal.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/_index.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Another priority of Xfce is adherence to standards, specifically those defined at [freedesktop.org](https://freedesktop.org).\n"
msgstr "Outra prioridade do Xfce é a adherencia a padróns, especialmente os definidas en [freedesktop.org](https://freedesktop.org).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/_index.md:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce can be installed on several UNIX platforms. It is known to compile on Linux, NetBSD, FreeBSD, OpenBSD, Solaris, Cygwin and MacOS X, on x86, PPC, Sparc, Alpha...\n"
msgstr "O Xfce pode instalarse en varias plataformas UNIX. Sábese que compila en Linux, NetBSD, FreeBSD, OpenBSD, Solaris, Cygwin e MacOS X, en x86, PPC, Sparc, Alpha...\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/_index.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Features"
msgstr "Características"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/_index.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce contains a number of core components for the minimum tasks you'd expect from a desktop environment:\n"
msgstr "O Xfce contén unha serie de compoñentes básicos para as tarefas mínimas que espera dun contorno de escritorio:\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/_index.md:18 content/about/tour44.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window Manager"
msgstr "Xestor de xanelas"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "Manages the placement of windows on the screen, provides window decorations and manages workspaces or virtual desktops.\n"
msgstr "Xestiona a colocación de xanelas na pantalla, fornece decoracións de xanelas e xestiona espazos de traballo ou escritorios virtuais.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/_index.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "Desktop Manager"
msgstr "Xestor do escritorio"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "Sets the background image and provides a root window menu, desktop icons or minimized icons and a windows list.\n"
msgstr "Define a imaxe de fondo e fornece un menú da xanela raíz, iconas de escritorio ou iconas minimizadas e unha lista de xanelas.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/_index.md:26 content/about/tour44.md:69
#, no-wrap
msgid "Panel"
msgstr "Panel"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "Switch between opened windows, launch applications, switch workspaces and menu plugins to browse applications or directories.\n"
msgstr "Alterna entre xanelas abertas, inicia aplicacións, alterna entre espazos de traballo e engadidos de menú para navegar por aplicacións ou cartafoles.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/_index.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "Session Manager"
msgstr "Xestor de sesións"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Controls the login and power management of the desktop and allows you to store multiple login sessions.\n"
msgstr "Controla o inicio de sesión e a xestión de enerxía do escritorio e permite almacenar varias sesións de inicio de sesión.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/_index.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "Application Finder"
msgstr "Buscador de aplicacións"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:37
#, no-wrap
msgid "Shows the applications installed on your system in categories, so you can quickly find and launch them.\n"
msgstr "Amosa as aplicacións instaladas no seu sistema en categorías, para que poida atopalos e inicialos rapidamente.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/_index.md:38 content/about/tour44.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "File Manager"
msgstr "Xestor de ficheiros"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "Provides the basic file-management features and unique utilities like the bulk renamer.\n"
msgstr "Fornece as funcións básicas de xestión de ficheiros e utilidades únicas como o renomeado de múltiples ficheiros á vez.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/_index.md:42 content/about/tour410.md:69
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings Manager"
msgstr "Xestor de configuración"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/_index.md:45
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tools to control the various settings of the desktop; like keyboard shortcuts, appearance, display settings, etc.\n"
msgstr "Ferramentas para controlar as diferentes configuracións do escritorio como atallos de teclado, aparencia, configuración de visualización, etc.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/_index.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "Beside the basic set of modules, Xfce also provides numerous additional applications and plugins so you can extend your desktop the way you like, for example a terminal emulator, text editor, sound mixer, application finder, image viewer, iCal based calendar and a CD and DVD burning application. You can read more about the modules of Xfce in the [projects](/projects) page.\n"
msgstr "Ademais do conxunto básico de módulos, o Xfce tamén fornece numerosas aplicacións e engadidos adicionais para que poida estender o escritorio de maneira que lle guste, por exemplo un emulador de terminal, editor de texto, mesturador de son, buscador de aplicacións, visor de imaxes, calendario baseado en iCal e unha aplicación de gravación de cedés e deuvedés. Pode ler máis sobre os módulos do Xfce na páxina de proxectos\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Get Involved"
msgstr "Participe"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:7
#, no-wrap
msgid "Welcome to the Xfce community. By joining our team, you will be part of an international effort by hundreds of people working to deliver a stunning Free Software computing experience. You will meet new friends, learn new skills and make a difference to millions of users while working with people from all around the globe. There are many different ways you can become part of this, just read on and pick an area which interests you or seems challenging.\n"
msgstr "Dámoslle a benvida á comunidade do Xfce. Ao unirse ao noso equipo, formará parte dun esforzo internacional realizado por centos de persoas que traballan para fornecer unha sorprendente experiencia informática de soporte lóxico libre. Poderá coñecer novos amigos, aprender novas habilidades e marcar a diferenza con millóns de usuarios mentres traballa con persoas de todo o mundo. Hai moitas maneiras diferentes de formar parte disto, só ten que ler e escoller unha área que lle interese ou pareza desafiante.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Possible tasks include testing, bug reporting; writing code, developing artwork, documentation or translations; or spreading the word and helping out with promotion and marketing both on line and at tradeshows and conferences.\n"
msgstr "As tarefas posíbeis inclúen probas, informes de fallos; escribir código, desenvolver ilustracións, documentación ou traducións; ou falar sobre o Xfce e axudar con promoción e publicidade tanto en liña como en feiras e conferencias.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "Documentation"
msgstr "Documentación"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "There's lots of people using and testing Xfce. By providing useful and up-to-date documentation, you will make a big impact on helping people understand how to make the most of the Xfce Desktop Environment. [Learn More →](https://docs.xfce.org/contribute/documentation)\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Translation"
msgstr "Tradución"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "Are you fluent in multiple languages? By contributing your translations of text to the Xfce Desktop Environment, you will help Xfce be a better part of the global market and more accessible to the millions of potential users out there. [Learn More →](https://docs.xfce.org/contribute/translate/start)\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Development"
msgstr "Desenvolvemento"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "By becoming a developer, you can make a big difference while enjoying a challenging and fun experience. You'll learn to be a better coder, you will get to implement new features and defeat daunting bugs, creating a stunning product, all the while collaborating with people from all around the world. You can start by browsing the [source code](https://gitlab.xfce.org).\n"
msgstr "Ao facerse un desenvolvedor, pode marcar unha gran diferenza ao gozar dunha experiencia retadora e divertida. Aprenderá a ser un mellor programador, terá que crear novas características e depurar fallos incómodos, crear un produto sorprendente, á vez que colabora con persoas de todo o mundo. Pode comezar examinando o [código fonte](https://gitlab.xfce.org).\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "Promotion"
msgstr "Promoción"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "If you own a blog or website you can greatly help by spreading the word and encouraging new users to give Xfce a try. If you have a Mastodon or Twitter account you can also help by reposting any announcements we make to help us reach a larger audience.\n"
msgstr "Se ten unha bitácora ou un sitio web, pode axudar a difundir falando e animando aos novos usuarios a dar unha oportunidade ao Xfce. Se ten unha conta de Mastodom ou Twitter tamén pode axudar respondendo aos anuncios que realizamos para axudarnos a chegar un público máis amplo.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "Bug Reporting and testing"
msgstr "Informando de fallos e facendo probas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:29
#, no-wrap
msgid "One of the most useful tasks that we rely on the community for is testing and reporting of bugs. Since Xfce runs on various platform and in a lot of different setups, testing all changes in every possible situation is an impossible task. As such we kindly ask users to assist in testing, and reporting all bugs they may find, using our [bug tracker](https://gitlab.xfce.org).\n"
msgstr "Unha das tarefas máis útiles que confiamos na comunidade é a realización de probas e os informes de fallos. Dado que o Xfce funciona en varias plataformas e en moitas configuracións diferentes, probar todos os cambios en todas as situacións posíbeis é unha tarefa imposíbel. Por iso, solicitamos aos usuarios que axuden a probar e informen sobre todos os fallos que poidan atopar, utilizando o noso [rastrexador de fallos](https://gitlab.xfce.org).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:31
#, no-wrap
msgid "Once a bug has been found, the cause of the bug needs to be tracked down, and then (obviously) fixed. If you want to get involved in the actual development process of Xfce a great way to start is by solving bugs and then submitting a patch file.\n"
msgstr "Unha vez que se atopou un fallo, debe rastrexar a causa e logo (obviamente) corrixir o fallo. Se quere involucrarse no proceso de desenvolvemento real do Xfce, unha boa forma de comezar é resolvendo fallos e enviar un ficheiro de parche.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "OpenCollective"
msgstr "OpenCollective"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/getinvolved/_index.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "If you want to fund the project, you can use OpenCollective. Xfce has created two collectives, known as [Xfce ($)](https://opencollective.com/xfce) and [Xfce-Eu (€)](https://opencollective.com/xfce-eu) respectively. [Learn More →](https://mail.xfce.org/pipermail/xfce/2021-May/037348.html)\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour420.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.20 tour"
msgstr "Visita ao Xfce 4.20"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to new major features of Xfce 4.20. It only covers improvements made on the (user-visible) surface.\n"
msgstr "Este percorrido presentaralle as novas características principais de Xfce 4.20. Só cobre as melloras feitas na superficie (visible polo usuario).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "Check the full [Xfce 4.20 changelog](/download/changelogs/4.20/) for a detailed list of changes.\n"
msgstr "Consulte o rexistro de [cambios completo do Xfce 4.20](/download/changelogs/4.20/) para obter unha lista detallada dos cambios.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour420.md:11 content/about/tour420.md:204
#: content/about/tour418.md:223
#, no-wrap
msgid "General"
msgstr "Xeral"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Wayland"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Important Notice:** Please be aware that the Wayland support in Xfce 4.20 is experimental. It is recommended for advanced users only, as you may encounter bugs and experience incomplete functionality. Proceed with caution!\n"
msgstr "<b>Nota importante:</b> Teña en conta que a compatibilidade de Wayland no Xfce 4.20 é experimental. Só se recomenda para usuarios avanzados, pois pode atopar erros e experimentar unha funcionalidade incompleta. Proceda con precaución!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thanks to [Brian](https://gitlab.xfce.org/kelnos) and [Gaël](https://gitlab.xfce.org/Tamaranch) almost all Xfce components are able to run on Wayland windowing, while still keeping support for X11 windowing.\n"
msgstr "Grazas a [Brian](https://gitlab.xfce.org/kelnos) e [Gaël](https://gitlab.xfce.org/Tamaranch), case todos os compoñentes de Xfce poden executarse en xanelas Wayland, mantendo a compatibilidade coas xanelas X11.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "This major effort was achieved by abstracting away any X11/Wayland windowing specific calls and making use of Wayland/Wlroots protocols. A whole new Xfce library, \"libxfce4windowing\" was introduced during that process. XWayland will not be required to run any of the ported Xfce components.\n"
msgstr "Este gran esforzo conseguiuse abstraendo calquera chamada específica de xanlas X11/Wayland e facendo uso dos protocolos Wayland/Wlroots. Durante ese proceso introduciuse unha nova biblioteca Xfce, «libxfce4windowing». XWayland non terá que executar ningún dos compoñentes de Xfce portados.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "So far Xfce does not feature a compositor which supports Wayland. If you want to run Xfce in Wayland, Labwc and Wayfire will give you the best results. A detailed instruction on this can be found [here](https://wiki.xfce.org/releng/wayland_roadmap#testing). Please be aware that Wayland support is still experimental!\n"
msgstr "Polo de agora o Xfce non conta cun compositor que admita Wayland. Se quere executar Xfce en Wayland, Labwc e Wayfire daranlle os mellores resultados. Pode atopar [aquí](https://wiki.xfce.org/releng/wayland_roadmap#testing) instrucións detalladas sobre isto. Teña en conta que o soporte de Wayland aínda é experimental.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "Plans are underway to add Wayland support to Xfwm4 while preserving its existing X11 functionality. However, such a restructurization will be a major effort and we cannot tell yet when/if it will be done, so please don't hold your breath waiting for it.\n"
msgstr "Están en marcha plans para engadir compatibilidade con Wayland a Xfwm4 preservando a súa funcionalidade X11 existente. No entanto, dita reestruturación será un esforzo importante e aínda non podemos dicir cando/se se fará, así que lle rogamos que non agarde por isto.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "For few components and multiple features, it was not possible to port them to Wayland, partly because there are no standardized Wayland protocols available yet to provide the required services:\n"
msgstr "Non se puideron migrar algúns compoñentes e varias funcións a Wayland, en parte porque aínda non hai protocolos de Wayland estandarizados dispoñíbeis para fornecer os servizos necesarios:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Workspace support is missing (ext-workspace protocol [was just merged](https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/wayland/wayland-protocols/-/merge_requests/40)).\n"
msgstr "Falta a compatibilidade con espazo de traballo ([acaba de fusionarse](https://gitlab.freedesktop.org/wayland/wayland-protocols/-/merge_requests/40) o protocolo de espazo de traballo externo).\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Systray icons will be missing for multiple applications (required to use StatusNotifier instead of GtkStatusIcon)\n"
msgstr "Faltarán as iconas da zona do sistema para varias aplicacións (necesario para usar StatusNotifier en lugar de GtkStatusIcon)\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce4-settings: Keyboard and mouse settings so far are internal to the Wayland compositor and as such the according Xfce dialogs won't be available on Wayland yet.\n"
msgstr "Configuración do Xfce4: a configuración do teclado e do rato até o de agora son internas ao compositor de Wayland e, como tal, os diálogos de Xfce correspondentes aínda non estarán dispoñíbeis en Wayland.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Power related keyboard handling (brightness keys, suspend, etc.) is internal to the Wayland compositor and as such cannot be supported yet by Xfce components.\n"
msgstr "O manexo do teclado relacionado coa enerxía (teclas de brillo, suspensión, etc.) é interno ao compositor Wayland e, como tal, aínda non pode ser compatíbel cos compoñentes do Xfce.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Wayland does not specify a native protocol for taking screenshots. However, xfce4-screenshooter already supports screenshots via the wlroots 'screencopy' protocol (entire screen). Screenshots of a rectangle selection or the active window are not yet supported via Wayland.\n"
msgstr "Wayland non especifica un protocolo nativo para facer capturas de pantalla. No entanto, a captura de pantalla do Xfce xa admite capturas de pantalla a través do protocolo «screencopy» de wlroots (pantalla enteira). As capturas de pantalla dunha selección de rectángulo ou da xanela activa aínda non son compatíbeis con Wayland.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "Some other Xfce components don't run at all on Wayland:\n"
msgstr "Algúns outros compoñentes do Xfce non funcionan en absoluto en Wayland:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfwm4\n"
msgstr "Xfwm4\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfdashboard\n"
msgstr "Xfdashboard\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce4-screensaver (porting to Wayland [completed but not merged](https://gitlab.xfce.org/apps/xfce4-screensaver/-/merge_requests/28), as it requires the experimental [libwlembed library](https://gitlab.xfce.org/kelnos/libwlembed))\n"
msgstr "O protector de pantalla do Xfce ([completouse a migración a Wayland pero non se fusionou](https://gitlab.xfce.org/apps/xfce4-screensaver/-/merge_requests/28), xa que require a [biblioteca experimental libwlembed](https://gitlab.xfce.org/kelnos/libwlembed))\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce4-windowck-plugin (needs to be [ported to libxfce4windowing](https://gitlab.xfce.org/panel-plugins/xfce4-windowck-plugin/-/issues/37))\n"
msgstr "Xfce4-windowck-plugin (necesita ser [migrado a libxfce4windowing](https://gitlab.xfce.org/panel-plugins/xfce4-windowck-plugin/-/issues/37))\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce4-xkb-plugin (keyboard handling is internal to the Wayland compositor)\n"
msgstr "Xfce4-xkb-plugin (o manexo do teclado é interno ao compositor Wayland)\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "More detailed info on the current Wayland status can be found on our [Wayland roadmap.](https://wiki.xfce.org/releng/wayland_roadmap)\n"
msgstr "Pode atopar información máis detallada sobre o estado actual de Wayland na nosa [folla de ruta de Wayland.](https://wiki.xfce.org/releng/wayland_roadmap)\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:43 content/about/tour418.md:225
#, no-wrap
msgid "Scaling"
msgstr "Escalado"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "Icons and thumbnail scaling was fixed for various components. Various missing icons for larger scales were added. Any blurriness when using Xfce components on a HiDPI display should be gone now.\n"
msgstr "Corrixiuse a escala das iconas e miniaturas de varios compoñentes. Engadíronse varias iconas que faltaban para escalas maiores. Calquera borrosidade ao usar compoñentes Xfce nunha pantalla HiDPI agora debería ter desaparecido.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Icon View Performance"
msgstr " Rendemento da vista de iconas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "By using different container types, the \"Exo-Icon-View\" now can handle 100,000 files and more without freezing.\n"
msgstr "Empregando diferentes tipos de contedores, o «Exo-Icon-View» agora pode xestionar 100.000 ficheiros e máis sen conxelarse.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:53
#, no-wrap
msgid "Type ahead search box"
msgstr "Caixa de busca con suxestións"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "The type ahead search box in the exo icon view now always stays inside the according view widget.\n"
msgstr "A caixa de busca con suxestións na vista da icona «exo» agora permanece sempre dentro do trebello da vista correspondente.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:59
#, no-wrap
msgid "Shortcut Editor"
msgstr "Editor de atallos"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "Shortcuts now can be used for multiple actions if they don't conflict with each other.\n"
msgstr "Os atallos agora poden usarse para varias accións se non entran en conflito con outros.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:63
#, no-wrap
msgid "About Dialog"
msgstr "Xanela sobre o Xfce"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "The dialog now shows the distribution logo, information about the used windowing system and the used GPU.\n"
msgstr "O diálogo agora amosa o logotipo da distribución, información sobre o sistema de xanelas usado e a GPU utilizada.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "![libxfce4ui - about dialog][img-libxfce4ui_about]\n"
msgstr "![libxfce4ui - diálogo «sobre»][img-libxfce4ui_about]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "This library is new to Xfce. Libxfce4windowing is an abstraction library that attempts to present windowing concepts (screens, top level windows, workspaces, etc.) in a windowing-system-independent manner.\n"
msgstr "Esta biblioteca é nova para Xfce. Libxfce4windowing é unha biblioteca de abstracción que tenta presentar conceptos de xanelas (pantallas, xanelas de nivel superior, espazos de traballo, etc.) de forma independente do sistema de xanelas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "Currently, X11 is fully supported via libwnck. Wayland is partially supported by using various Wayland protocol extensions. However, the full range of operations available on X11 is not available on Wayland, due to missing features in these protocols extensions.\n"
msgstr "Actualmente, X11 é totalmente compatible con libwnck. Wayland é parcialmente compatible co uso de varios engadidos de protocolo Wayland. No entanto, a gama completa de operacións dispoñíbeis en X11 non está dispoñíbel en Wayland, debido a que faltan funcións nestes engadidos de protocolos.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:77
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mounted and Remote Locations"
msgstr "Localizacións montadas e remotas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mount points now show an emblem and have a specific type description.\n"
msgstr "Os puntos de montaxe agora amosan un emblema e teñen unha descrición de tipo específica.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "Ipv6 remote URLs are now supported.\n"
msgstr "Agora son compatíbeis os URL remotos Ipv6.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:84
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to create symbolic links as well on remote locations.\n"
msgstr "Agora tamén é posíbel crear ligazóns simbólicas en lugares remotos.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:85
#, no-wrap
msgid "Search"
msgstr "Buscar"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is not required any more to wait until a search is finished to open the context menu on search results.\n"
msgstr "Non é preciso agardar até que remate unha busca para abrir o menú contextual dos resultados da busca.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:89 content/about/tour418.md:107
#, no-wrap
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Barra de ferramentas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "A couple of new toolbar buttons were added:\n"
msgstr "Engadíronse un par de novos botóns da barra de ferramentas:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:97
#, no-wrap
msgid "View Switcher - A drop-down button to select a view.\n"
msgstr "Selector de vistas: un botón despregábel para seleccionar unha vista.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:97
#, no-wrap
msgid "Menu - This hamburger button will show automatically in the toolbar, when the menubar is hidden. It will reveal a vertical menu, bar, when pressed.\n"
msgstr "Menú: este botón do tipo «hamburguesa» aparecerá automaticamente na barra de ferramentas, cando a barra de menú estea agochada. Se se preme, amosará unha barra de menú vertical.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:97
#, no-wrap
msgid "New Tab - Open a new tab using the current directory.\n"
msgstr "Nova lapela: abre unha nova lapela usando o cartafol actual.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour420.md:97
#, no-wrap
msgid "New Window - Open a new window using the current directory.\n"
msgstr "Nova xanela: abre unha nova xanela usando o cartafol actual.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:99
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - new toolbar buttons][img-thunar_toolbar_new_items]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - novos botóns da barra de ferramentas][img-thunar_toolbar_new_items]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:101
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - improved hamburger toolbar button][img-thunar_toolbar_hamburger]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - botón do tipo «hamburguesa» na barra de ferramentas mellorado][img-thunar_toolbar_hamburger]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:103
#, no-wrap
msgid "On shrinking the Thunar window, toolbar items will now be moved to an overflow menu. Like that, it is possible to maintain smaller thunar windows.\n"
msgstr "Ao reducir a xanela Thunar, os elementos da barra de ferramentas moveranse agora a un menú de desbordamento. Grazas a elo, é posíbel facer as xanelas de thunar máis pequenas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:105
#, no-wrap
msgid "Furthermore, a bug was fixed which prevented the usage of submenu custom actions in the toolbar.\n"
msgstr "Ademais, solucionouse un erro que impedía o uso de accións personalizadas do submenú na barra de ferramentas.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window Decorations"
msgstr "Decoracións de xanelas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:109
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now an option to use client side decorations in Thunar (CSD).\n"
msgstr "Agora hai unha opción para usar as decoracións do lado do cliente no Thunar (CSD).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:111
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - CSD with menu][img-thunar_csd_with_menu]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - co menú CSD][img-thunar_csd_with_menu]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:113
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - CSD without menu][img-thunar_csd_without_menu]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - sen o menú CSD][img-thunar_csd_without_menu]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:114 content/about/tour418.md:127
#, no-wrap
msgid "Statusbar"
msgstr "Barra de estado"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:117
#, no-wrap
msgid "An option to show the number of hidden files in the statusbar was added.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse unha opción na barra de estado que amosa o número de ficheiros agochados.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:118
#, no-wrap
msgid "Recently Used Files"
msgstr "Ficheiros usados recentemente"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:121
#, no-wrap
msgid "Only files which were successfully opened are now added to the list of recently used files.\n"
msgstr "Agora só se engaden á lista de ficheiros usados ​​recentemente os ficheiros que se abriron correctamente.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:123
#, no-wrap
msgid "Directories won't be added to the recently used files anymore.\n"
msgstr "Xa non se engadirán cartafoles á lista de ficheiros usados ​​recentemente.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:124
#, no-wrap
msgid "Symbolic Icons"
msgstr "Iconas simbólicas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:127
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now an option to use symbolic icons in the side pane and colored icons in the toolbar.\n"
msgstr "Agora hai unha opción para usar iconas simbólicas no panel lateral e iconas de cores na barra de ferramentas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:129
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - symbolic icons][img-thunar_symbolic_icons]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - iconas simbólicas][img-thunar_symbolic_icons]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:131
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - colored icons][img-thunar_colored_icons]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - iconas de cores][img-thunar_colored_icons]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:132
#, no-wrap
msgid "Drag and Drop"
msgstr "Arrastrar e soltar"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:135
#, no-wrap
msgid "While dragging files, folders are now opened automatically on hover.\n"
msgstr "Mentres se arrastra ficheiros, agora os cartafoles ábrense automaticamente ao pasar o cursor.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:137
#, no-wrap
msgid "While dragging files, the focus of the split view pane is now updated when hovered.\n"
msgstr "Mentres se arrastran ficheiros, agora actualízase o foco do panel de vista dividida cando se pasa o rato.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:138
#, no-wrap
msgid "Performance"
msgstr "Rendemento"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:141
#, no-wrap
msgid "In the past, you might have faced situation involving bigger numbers of files in which thunar showed a freeze. Due to various different performance measures, thunar now is much more bullet-proof for action involving huge numbers of files.\n"
msgstr "No pasado, é posíbel que se enfrontase a unha situación que implicaba un gran número de ficheiros nos que thunar amosaba unha conxelación. Debido a varias medidas de rendemento diferentes, thunar agora é moito máis robusto para accións que impliquen un gran número de ficheiros.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:143
#, no-wrap
msgid "This was achieved by using appropriate container types, moving some actions into separate jobs and throttling of view-updates.\n"
msgstr "Isto conseguiuse empregando tipos de contedores axeitados, movendo algunhas accións a traballos separados e limitando as actualizacións da visualización.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:145
#, no-wrap
msgid "A [number of integration test cases](https://wiki.xfce.org/thunar/dev/integration_testcases) will be used in order to keep performance on the current level in the future.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:146 content/about/tour418.md:171
#, no-wrap
msgid "Custom Actions"
msgstr "Accións personalizadas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:149
#, no-wrap
msgid "Shortcuts for custom action will now as well work when the custom action is located in a sub-menu.\n"
msgstr "Os atallos para as accións personalizadas agora tamén funcionarán cando a acción personalizada estea situada nun submenú.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:150
#, no-wrap
msgid "File Transfer"
msgstr "Transferencia de ficheiros"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:153
#, no-wrap
msgid "For file validation in thunar 4.18.x a md5 checksum was calculated for source and target file. This calculation turned out to be rather slow and actually superfluous. Now files are just compared directly. In addition, the usage of direct I/O operations now attempts to prevent comparison of possibly cached buffers.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:155
#, no-wrap
msgid "An option was added to only copy files in parallel if the relevant devices are in idle state. This prevents possible fragmentation during copy for HDD drives.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse unha opción para copiar só ficheiros en paralelo se os dispositivos correspondentes están en estado inactivo. Isto evita a posíbel fragmentación durante a copia das unidades HDD.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:157
#, no-wrap
msgid "Transferring files no longer steals the current focus.\n"
msgstr "A transferencia de ficheiros xa non rouba o foco actual.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:159
#, no-wrap
msgid "The file transfer question dialog now provides the same options while having less buttons. In addition, file thumbnails now are properly requested by the dialog.\n"
msgstr "O diálogo de preguntas sobre a transferencia de ficheiros fornece agora as mesmas opcións con menos botóns. Ademais, agora as miniaturas dos ficheiros son solicitadas correctamente polo diálogo.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:161
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - file transfer dialog][img-thunar_transfer_dialog]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - diálogo de transferencia de ficheiros][img-thunar_transfer_dialog]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:162
#, no-wrap
msgid "Launchers"
msgstr "Iniciadores"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:165
#, no-wrap
msgid "By default, launcher names instead of filenames are shown now for trusted launchers.\n"
msgstr "De forma predeterminada, agora amósanse os nomes dos iniciadores no lugar de nomes de ficheiros para os iniciadores de confianza.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:166
#, no-wrap
msgid "Undo/Redo"
msgstr "Desfacer/Refacer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:169
#, no-wrap
msgid "The user now will be asked before any deletion will be done by an undo operation.\n"
msgstr "Agora, a persoa usuaria será preguntada antes de que se faga calquera eliminación mediante unha operación de desfacer.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:170 content/about/tour418.md:73
#, no-wrap
msgid "List View"
msgstr "Vista de lista"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:173
#, no-wrap
msgid "Similar to the tree-view side pane, the main view now also supports folder expansion.\n"
msgstr "Semellante ao panel lateral da vista en árbore, a vista principal agora tamén admite a expansión de cartafoles.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:175
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - expandable folders][img-thunar_expandable_folders]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - cartafoles expansíbeis][img-thunar_expandable_folders]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:176 content/about/tour418.md:121
#, no-wrap
msgid "Split View"
msgstr "Vista dividida"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:179
#, no-wrap
msgid "A shortcut now can be used to toggle between split-view panes, and the focused pane now uses different coloring.\n"
msgstr "Agora pode usar un atallo para alternar entre paneis de vista dividida, e o panel enfocado agora usa unha cor diferente.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:181
#, no-wrap
msgid "![thunar - split view][img-thunar_split_view]\n"
msgstr "![thunar - vista dividida][img-thunar_split_view]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:183
#, no-wrap
msgid "A dialog will now ask for confirmation when closing a split-pane with multiple tabs.\n"
msgstr "Agora unha caixa de diálogo pedirá confirmación ao pechar un panel dividido con varias lapelas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:187
#, no-wrap
msgid "The application list now as well can be navigated via Ctrl+N / Ctrl+P keys (VI default).\n"
msgstr "Agora tamén se pode navegar pola lista de aplicacións a través das teclas Ctrl+N / Ctrl+P (predeterminado VI).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:189
#, no-wrap
msgid "An option was added to close the Appfinder window automatically when focus is lost.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse unha opción para pechar automaticamente a xanela do buscador de aplicacións cando este perde o foco.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:191
#, no-wrap
msgid "Ctrl+Enter can be used to execute commands immediately when selecting entries from the dropdown.\n"
msgstr "Ctrl+Intro pode usarse para executar ordes inmediatamente ao seleccionar entradas no menú despregábel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:193
#, no-wrap
msgid "Within the new version, application specific actions will show on right click.\n"
msgstr "Dentro da nova versión, as accións específicas da aplicación amósanse ao facer clic co botón dereito.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:195
#, no-wrap
msgid "An option to show generic names of launchers was added.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse unha opción para amosar os nomes xenéricos dos iniciadores.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:197
#, no-wrap
msgid "Appfinder optionally can now be launched as a daemon, so that it will respond even quicker.\n"
msgstr "Agora o buscador de aplicacións pode iniciarse como un servizo, para así responder aínda máis axiña.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:199
#, no-wrap
msgid "An option allows now to launch items on a single click.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse unha opción que permite iniciar elementos cun só clic.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:201
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-appfinder - settings][img-appfinder_new]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-appfinder - configuración][img-appfinder_new]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:207
#, no-wrap
msgid "The border width of the panel is now configurable.\n"
msgstr "Agora pode configurarse a largura do bordo do panel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:209
#, no-wrap
msgid "For manual installations: the panel now does its best to find plugins in XDG base directories, and better preserves its configuration when it can't find them.\n"
msgstr "Para instalacións manuais: agora o panel fai todo o posíbel para atopar complementos nos directorios base de XDG e conserva mellor a súa configuración cando non os atopa.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:210
#, no-wrap
msgid "Clock"
msgstr "Reloxo"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:213
#, no-wrap
msgid "LCD clock: An option was added to visualize inactive segments.\n"
msgstr "Reloxo LCD: engadiuse unha opción para visualizar os segmentos inactivos.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:215
#, no-wrap
msgid "Analog: There is now an optional 24h mode.\n"
msgstr "Analóxico: agora hai unha opción co modo 24 horas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:217
#, no-wrap
msgid "Digital: Week numbers now are shown optionally.\n"
msgstr "Dixital: agora poden amosarse os números da semana opcionalmente.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:218
#, no-wrap
msgid "Show Desktop"
msgstr "Amosar o escritorio"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:221
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now the possibility to show the desktop when hovering the mouse on the \"show desktop\" panel icon.\n"
msgstr "Agora existe a posibilidade de amosar o escritorio ao pasar o rato sobre a icona do panel «amosar o escritorio».\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:222
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tasklist"
msgstr "Lista de tarefas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:225
#, no-wrap
msgid "Icon size management has been improved overall, notably by switching to libxfce4windowing.\n"
msgstr "A xestión do tamaño das iconas mellorouse en xeral, especialmente ao cambiar a libxfce4windowing.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:226 content/about/tour420.md:354
#: content/about/tour418.md:179
#, no-wrap
msgid "Preferences"
msgstr "Preferencias"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:229
#, no-wrap
msgid "The 'delete' key can now be used to remove panel objects, and several objects can be removed at once.\n"
msgstr "Agora pode usarse a tecla «suprimir» para retirar obxectos de panel, poden ser retirados varios obxectos á vez.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:231
#, no-wrap
msgid "Panel objects in the panel configuration list now will have the same icons as in the panel itself.\n"
msgstr "Os obxectos de panel da lista de configuración agora terán as mesmas iconas que no propio panel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:233
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-panel - panel configuration list][img-panel_item_list]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-panel - lista de configuración do panel][img-panel_item_list]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:236
#, no-wrap
msgid "Screen Locking"
msgstr "Bloqueo da pantalla"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:239
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is no dedicated \"security\" tab anymore. Lock screen management was massively simplified and \"Light Locker\" was dropped. \"lock-on-sleep\" is now synchronized with xfce4-session and xfce4-screensaver.\n"
msgstr "Xa non hai unha lapela adicada á «seguranza». A xestión da pantalla de bloqueo simplificouse enormemente e abandonouse «Light Locker». O «lock-on-sleep» agora está sincronizado con xfce4-session e xfce4-screensaver.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:241
#, no-wrap
msgid "Screen locking settings are now only handled by xfce4-screensaver to avoid conflicts. A button to open xfce4-screensaver-preferences was added:\n"
msgstr "Xfce4-screensaver só xestiona a configuración de bloqueo da pantalla para evitar conflitos. Engadiuse un botón para abrir xfce4-screensaver-preferences:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:243
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-power-manager - settings][img-power_manager_settings]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-power-manager - configuración][img-power_manager_settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:245
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-screensaver - settings][img-power_manager_screensaver]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-screensaver - configuración][img-power_manager_screensaver]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:246
#, no-wrap
msgid "Power Settings"
msgstr "Configuración de enerxía"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:249
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support for handling different power profiles via power-profiles-daemon was added.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse a funcionalidade para manexar diferentes perfís de enerxía a través de power-profiles-daemon.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:251
#, no-wrap
msgid "The overall charge state calculation was wrong for some cases and is now fixed.\n"
msgstr "O cálculo xeral do estado de carga foi incorrecto nalgúns casos e agora está corrixido.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:253
#, no-wrap
msgid "When the critical power dialog pops up, unintentional user actions are now prevented.\n"
msgstr "Cando aparece o diálogo de potencia crítica, agora impídense as accións non intencionadas do usuario.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:255
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now support for the hybrid sleep mode.\n"
msgstr "Agora hai compatibilidade para o modo de suspensión híbrido.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:257
#, no-wrap
msgid "The device details tab now as well shows the energy rate.\n"
msgstr "A lapela de detalles do dispositivo agora tamén amosa a taxa de enerxía.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:258
#, no-wrap
msgid "Others"
msgstr "Outros"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:261
#, no-wrap
msgid "Several use-cases for lid close were fixed.\n"
msgstr "Arranxáronse varios casos de uso para o peche da tapa.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:263
#, no-wrap
msgid "There are now the options \"shutdown\" and \"do nothing\" on lid close.\n"
msgstr "Agora están dispoñíbeis as opcións para «apagar» e «non facer nada» cando se pecha a tapa.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:265
#, no-wrap
msgid "Buttons to change the brightness exponentially and keyboard backlight toggle keys now are supported.\n"
msgstr "Agora son compatíbeis os botóns para cambiar o brillo de forma exponencial e as teclas para alternar da retroiluminación do teclado.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:269
#, no-wrap
msgid "The logout dialog will not provide a checkbox to enable session saving anymore.\n"
msgstr "O diálogo de saír da sesión xa non proporcionará unha caixa de verificación para activar ou gardar a sesión.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:271
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to start a Wayland session via `startxfce4 --wayland`.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:273
#, no-wrap
msgid "Minimal support for xdg-desktop-portal was added by registering for a wallpaper, screenshot and background xapp.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse unha compatibilidade mínima para xdg-desktop-portal ao rexistrarse para obter un fondo de pantalla, unha captura de pantalla e unha aplicación de fondo.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:276 content/about/tour418.md:65
#: content/about/tour412.md:73 content/about/tour410.md:95
#, no-wrap
msgid "Appearance Settings"
msgstr "Configuración da aparencia"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:279
#, no-wrap
msgid "Icon themes are now loaded in a separate thread, in order to prevent a possible freeze.\n"
msgstr "Os temas de iconas agora son cargados nun fío separado, para evitar unha posíbel conxelación.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:281
#, no-wrap
msgid "For icon themes which are known to be incomplete, a warning now will be shown.\n"
msgstr "Para os temas de iconas que se sabe que están incompletos, agora amosarase unha advertencia.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:283
#, no-wrap
msgid "The usage of client side decorations is opt-in now, not opt-out.\n"
msgstr "O uso das decoracións do lado do cliente agora é opcional, no canto de ser unha opción desmarcada de xeito predeterminado.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:285
#, no-wrap
msgid "Dark themes now are identified and supported in a more reliable way. (Relevant e.g. for the Qogir and Orchis themes)\n"
msgstr "Agora identifícanse os temas escuros e son compatíbeis dun xeito máis fiable. (Relevante, por exemplo, para os temas Qogir e Orchis)\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:286 content/about/tour418.md:59
#: content/about/tour412.md:65
#, no-wrap
msgid "Display Settings"
msgstr "Configuración de pantalla"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:289
#, no-wrap
msgid "The default display profile has been added to the list of profiles that can match, and will be used if more than one matches now.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse á lista de perfís o perfil de visualización predeterminado, o cal será empregado no caso de haber máis dunha coincidencia.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:291
#, no-wrap
msgid "Profile management has been extended to all profiles, not just those that match, and their names can now be edited.\n"
msgstr "A xestión de perfís estendeuse a todos os perfís, non só aos que coinciden, e agora poden modificarse os seus nomes.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:293
#, no-wrap
msgid "Scaling now always is done for both dimensions, and the preview shows the resulting size.\n"
msgstr "O escalado agora faise sempre para ambas dimensións e a vista previa amosa o tamaño resultante.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:295
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mirror state management has been improved overall, in particular by removing the need to match refresh rates.\n"
msgstr "A xestión do modo en espello foi mellorada en xeral, e en particular eliminouse a necesidade de igualar as taxas de actualización.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:297
#, no-wrap
msgid "The minimal dialog has been improved, in particular by allowing the display to be extended to the left and from top to bottom, and with compact profile display.\n"
msgstr "Mellorouse o diálogo mínimo, en particular ao permitir que a pantalla se estenda á esquerda e de arriba a abaixo, e cunha visualización de perfil compacta.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:299
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-settings - minimal display][img-settings_display]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-settings - pantalla mínima][img-settings_display]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:300
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mouse Settings"
msgstr "Configuración do rato"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:303
#, no-wrap
msgid "A checkbox was added to toggle between adaptive and flat mouse accel profile.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse unha caixa de verificación para alternar entre o perfil de aceleración do rato adaptativo e o perfil plano.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:305
#, no-wrap
msgid "High resolution scrolling can now be enabled for mice which do support it.\n"
msgstr "Agora pode activarse o desprazamento de alta resolución para os ratos que o admiten.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:307
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-settings - mouse][img-settings_mouse]\n"
msgstr "![xfce4-settings - rato][img-settings_mouse]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:308
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mime Settings"
msgstr "Configuración de mime"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:311
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to select/change multiple items at once.\n"
msgstr "Agora é posíbel seleccionar/cambiar varios elementos á vez.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:315
#, no-wrap
msgid "A systemd user unit, corresponding to the D-Bus session service, is now added.\n"
msgstr "Agora engádese unha unidade de usuario «systemd» correspondente ao servizo de sesión D-Bus.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:317
#, no-wrap
msgid "Whitespaces are now properly escaped when writing a xfconf channel to disk.\n"
msgstr "Os espazos en branco agora escapan correctamente ao escribir unha canle «xfconf» no disco.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:319
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfconf-query now displays array contents.\n"
msgstr "O «Xfconf-query» agora amosa o contido das matrices.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:322
#, no-wrap
msgid "Background Management"
msgstr "Xestión do fondo de pantalla"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:325
#, no-wrap
msgid "For random wallpaper cycling, wallpapers now are only repeated after all other wallpapers were shown.\n"
msgstr "Para o ciclo de fondos de pantalla aleatorios, os fondos de pantalla agora só se repiten despois de que se amosaran todos os demais.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:327
#, no-wrap
msgid "Old Xfce backgrounds were ported from .png to .svg to be usable for large screens.\n"
msgstr "Os fondos antigos de Xfce migráronse de .png a .svg para que se poidan usar en pantallas grandes.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:329
#, no-wrap
msgid "Gradients will now be rendered in a gamma-correct way.\n"
msgstr "Os degradados agora representaranse de forma correcta en canto a gamma.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:330
#, no-wrap
msgid "Icon grid"
msgstr "Grade de iconas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:333
#, no-wrap
msgid "The confirmation dialog for arranging desktop icons now is optional.\n"
msgstr "Agora, o diálogo de confirmación para organizar as iconas do escritorio é opcional.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:335
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to set custom colors for icon labels and icon background.\n"
msgstr "Agora poden configurarse cores personalizadas para as etiquetas e o fondo das iconas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:337
#, no-wrap
msgid "The icon grid on each monitor is now independent of one another.\n"
msgstr "A grade de iconas de cada monitor agora é independente unha das outras.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:338
#, no-wrap
msgid "Minimized Application Icons"
msgstr "Iconas de aplicacións minimizadas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:341
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window icons are now initially shown on the monitor where the window was present before being minimized.\n"
msgstr "As iconas das xanelas agora amósanse inicialmente no monitor onde estaba a xanela antes de ser minimizada.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:343
#, no-wrap
msgid "The context menu (when clicking on an empty space) now has more useful options than before.\n"
msgstr "O menú contextual (ao facer clic nun espazo baleiro) ten agora máis opcións útiles que antes.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:344
#, no-wrap
msgid "File Icons"
msgstr "Iconas de ficheiros"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:347
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now an option to sort folders before files.\n"
msgstr "Agora hai unha opción para ordenar os cartafoles antes dos ficheiros.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:349
#, no-wrap
msgid "The positions of the icons are now saved in a way that should avoid icons moving around in unexpected ways when monitors are added and removed.\n"
msgstr "As posicións das iconas gárdanse agora dun xeito que debería evitar que as iconas se movan de forma inesperada cando se engaden e eliminan pantallas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:351
#, no-wrap
msgid "New files and dropped files now will be placed near the current cursor location.\n"
msgstr "Os ficheiros novos e os ficheiros soltos agora colocaranse preto da localización actual do cursor.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:353
#, no-wrap
msgid "Icons of fixed disks and drives can now be optionally shown.\n"
msgstr "Agora poden amosarse de forma opcional as iconas de discos e unidades fixas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:357
#, no-wrap
msgid "The 'Desktop Icons' tab was fully reworked.\n"
msgstr "A lapela «iconas do escritorio» foi totalmente reelaborada.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:359
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfdesktop - settings - desktop icons][img-xfdesktop_settings_icons]\n"
msgstr "![xfdesktop - configuración - iconas de escritorio][img-xfdesktop_settings_icons]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:361
#, no-wrap
msgid "All shortcuts of Xfdesktop now can be configured, using the XfceShortcutsManagers widget.\n"
msgstr "Agora poden configurarse todos os atallos de Xfdesktop mediante o trebello XfceShortcutsManagers.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:363
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfdesktop - settings - keyboard shortcuts][img-xfdesktop_settings_shortcuts]\n"
msgstr "![xfdesktop - configuración - atallos de teclado][img-xfdesktop_settings_shortcuts]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:365
#, no-wrap
msgid "More folders that hold background images were added as shortcuts in the settings dialog.\n"
msgstr "Engadíronse máis cartafoles que conteñen imaxes de fondo como atallos no diálogo de configuración.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:367
#, no-wrap
msgid "The settings dialog will update if the background is changed from outside the dialog.\n"
msgstr "O diálogo de configuración actualizarase se se cambia o fondo desde fóra do diálogo.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:369
#, no-wrap
msgid "Wallpaper image folders now are loaded fully asynchronously to prevent lag.\n"
msgstr "Os cartafoles de imaxes de fondo de pantalla agora cárganse de forma totalmente asíncrona para evitar o atraso.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour420.md:370
#, no-wrap
msgid "Context Menu"
msgstr "Menú contextual"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:373
#, no-wrap
msgid "Cascading custom actions will now as well shown correctly in Xfdesktop.\n"
msgstr "As accións personalizadas en cascada tamén se amosarán correctamente no Xfdesktop\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:375
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to open multiple selected folders at once.\n"
msgstr "Agora é posíbel abrir varios cartafoles seleccionados á vez.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:377
#, no-wrap
msgid "The context menu now opens on button press rather than button release, as most users will expect.\n"
msgstr "O menú contextual agora abre ao premer o botón en lugar de cando se solta, como esperarán a maioría dos usuarios.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:379
#, no-wrap
msgid "The middle-click window list menu has new styling and added features.\n"
msgstr "O menú de lista de xanelas do botón do medio do rato ten un estilo novo e funcións engadidas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:383
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support for stretch theme variants\n"
msgstr "Compatibilidade para variantes de temas estricábeis\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:385
#, no-wrap
msgid "Compositor: Block softpipe for GLX vsync\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:387
#, no-wrap
msgid "Focus: Include skip taskbar/pager when passing focus\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:389
#, no-wrap
msgid "Fix crash when alt-tabbing ([#762](https://gitlab.xfce.org/xfce/xfwm4/-/issues/762))\n"
msgstr "Corrixe o fallo ao pulsar alt-tab ([#762](https://gitlab.xfce.org/xfce/xfwm4/-/issues/762))\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour420.md:391
#, no-wrap
msgid "<p align=\"right\"><small>Used theme: \"Greybird-dark\". Used icon-theme: \"elementary Xfce dark\".</small></p>\n"
msgstr "<p align=\"right\"><small>Tema usado: «Greybird-dark». Icona-tema usado: «Xfce escuro elemental».</small></p>\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour418.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.18 tour"
msgstr "Visita ao Xfce 4.18"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to new major features of Xfce 4.18. It only covers improvements made on the (user-visible) surface.\n"
msgstr "Este percorrido presentaralle as novas características principais de Xfce 4.18. Só cobre as melloras feitas na superficie (visible polo usuario).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:10
#, no-wrap
msgid "Check the full [Xfce 4.18 changelog](/download/changelogs/4.18/) for a detailed list of changes.\n"
msgstr "Consulte o rexistro de [cambios completo do Xfce 4.18](/download/changelogs/4.18/) para obter unha lista detallada dos cambios.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Widget Library *(libxfce4ui)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Filename Input Dialog"
msgstr "Diálogo de entrada de nome de ficheiro"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "XfceFilenameInput is a comfortable widget for filename input, which was added in order to prevent invalid filenames at an early stage and to give detailed feedback on the concrete problem.\n"
msgstr "Inserción de nome de ficheiro do Xfce é un control cómodo para a entrada de nomes de ficheiros, que se engadiu para evitar nomes de ficheiros non válidos nunha fase inicial e para dar retroalimentación sobre o problema concreto.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "![XfceFilenameInput - trailing whitespaces][img-xfce4ui-new-file-dialog1]\n"
msgstr "![Inserción de nome de ficheiro do Xfce - espazos en branco ao final][img-xfce4ui-new-file-dialog1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "![XfceFilenameInput - slash][img-xfce4ui-new-file-dialog2]\n"
msgstr "![inserción de nome de ficheiro do Xfce - barra][img-xfce4ui-new-file-dialog2]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "Generic Shortcut Editor"
msgstr "Editor de atallos xenérico"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "This widget is a shortcut editor which was introduced in order to have a graphical interface to modify component-specific shortcuts. Currently, it is only used inside Thunar, Xfce4-terminal and Mousepad, though other components might follow.\n"
msgstr "Este control é un editor de atallos que se introduciu co fin de ter unha interface gráfica para modificar atallos específicos de compoñentes. Actualmente, só se usa dentro de Thunar, Xfce4-terminal e Mousepad, aínda que poderían seguir outros compoñentes.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "![XfceShortcutsEditor in Thunar][img-xfce4ui-shortcuts-editor]\n"
msgstr "![Editor e atallos do Xfce no Thunar][img-xfce4ui-shortcuts-editor]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thumbnail Service *(tumbler)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "Some performance improvements for the pixbuf-thumbnailer and the scheduler were done. As well now there are multiple overwrite options for the desktop-thumbnailer.\n"
msgstr "Realizáronse algunhas melloras de rendemento para o xerador de miniaturas pixbuf e o programador. Agora tamén hai varias opcións de sobrescritura para o xerador de miniaturas do escritorio.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now support for the thumbnail sizes x-large and xx-large, which are very useful for high resolution displays.\n"
msgstr "Agora admítense os tamaños de miniaturas extra-grande e extra-extra-grande, que son moi útiles para as pantallas de alta resolución.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tumbler and Thunar now support shared thumbnail repositories, like described in the freedesktop.org thumbnail specification. This feature can be used to produce thumbnails for a folder in advance, directly located near the pictures. Like that, the thumbnails don't need to be re-generated for each individual user.\n"
msgstr "O Tumbler e o Thunar agora admiten repositorios de miniaturas compartidos, como se describe na especificación de miniaturas de freedesktop.org. Esta función pode usarse para producir miniaturas dun cartafol con antelación, situado directamente preto das imaxes. Así, as miniaturas non precisan ser xeradas de novo para cada usuario individual.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "For more information on shared thumbnails, check the [related blog post](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog03.html).\n"
msgstr "Para obter máis información sobre as miniaturas compartidas, consulte [a publicación do blog relacionada](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog03.html).\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:37 content/about/tour416.md:47
#: content/about/tour414.md:33 content/about/tour412.md:39
#: content/about/tour410.md:25 content/about/tour48.md:29
#: content/about/tour46.md:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "Panel *(xfce4-panel)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "The DateTime and the Clock plugins provided overlapping functionality. In order to prevent parallel development, they have been merged into a single plugin.\n"
msgstr "Os engadidos «Data e hora» e «Reloxo» forneceron funcións superpostas. Co fin de evitar o desenvolvemento paralelo, fusionáronse nun único engadido.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new 'Clock' panel widget][img-panel-clock1]\n"
msgstr "![O novo engadido de panel «Reloxo»][img-panel-clock1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "The new Clock plugin received a new binary time mode now and provides a sleep monitor. Here's a screenshot of all possible layouts which are: Analog, Binary, Digital, Fuzzy and LCD.\n"
msgstr "O novo engadido Reloxo recibiu agora un novo modo de tempo binario e ofrece un monitor de sono. Velaquí unha captura de pantalla de todos os deseños posíbeis que son: analóxico, binario, dixital, difuso e LCD.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "![All possible Clock Modes][img-panel-clock2]\n"
msgstr "![Todos os posíbeis modos do Reloxo][img-panel-clock2]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:47 content/about/tour412.md:55
#: content/about/tour410.md:99 content/about/tour46.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Desktop Manager *(xfdesktop)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "Like in Thunar, the 'Delete' menu entry in the context menu can now be hidden.\n"
msgstr "Do mesmo xeito que en Thunar, agora pode agocharse a entrada do menú \"Eliminar\" do menú contextual.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "In order to don't mess the desktop by accident on pressing 'rearrange desktop icons', the user is asked for confirmation now.\n"
msgstr "Para non reorganizar o escritorio por accidente ao premer «reorganizar as iconas do escritorio», agora pídese confirmación á persoa usuaria.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:53 content/about/tour416.md:17
#: content/about/tour414.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings Manager *(xfce4-settings)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "The search entry for xfce4-settings-manager was a bit simplified. Now it will always be shown, without any slider or button.\n"
msgstr "A caixa de busca do xestor de configuración simplificouse un pouco. Agora amósase sempre, sen control desprazábel nin botón.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:58
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-settings-manager - the search entry is always shown][img-settings-main-dialog]\n"
msgstr "![Xestor de configuración - A caixa de busca agora amósase sempre][img-settings-main-dialog]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "xfce4-display-settings got some minor improvements and the possibility to decide what to do when new displays are connected.\n"
msgstr "A configuración da pantalla recibiu algunhas melloras menores e a posibilidade de decidir que facer cando se conectan novas pantallas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:64
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-display-settings - minor improvements][img-settings-display]\n"
msgstr "![Configuración da pantalla - melloras menores][img-settings-display]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "On selecting a new theme, there is now the option to automatically set a matching xfwm4 theme, if available.\n"
msgstr "Ao seleccionar un novo tema, agora hai a opción de estabelecer automaticamente un tema xfwm4 correspondente, se está dispoñíbel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-appearance-settings - toggle to set matching Xfwm4 theme][img-settings-appearance]\n"
msgstr "![Configuración da aparencia - alternar para configurar o tema Xfwm4 coincidente][img-settings-appearance]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:71 content/about/tour416.md:41
#: content/about/tour414.md:55 content/about/tour412.md:105
#: content/about/tour410.md:49 content/about/tour48.md:9
#: content/about/tour46.md:67
#, no-wrap
msgid "File Manager *(thunar)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "For directories, the count of containing files can now be displayed in the size column. It is now possible to add a 'file creation date' column, and the 'configure columns' dialog can be opened with a right-click on any column head.\n"
msgstr "Para os cartafoles, a contaxe de ficheiros que conteñen agora pode amosarse na columna de tamaño. Agora é posíbel engadir unha columna «data de creación do ficheiro» e o diálogo «Configurar columnas» pode abrirse facendo clic co botón dereito sobre calquera cabeceira de columna.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - List View - Preferences][img-thunar-listview1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Vista de lista - Preferencias][img-thunar-listview1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - List View - File count and file creation date][img-thunar-listview2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Vista de lista - Contaxe de ficheiros e data de creación do ficheiro][img-thunar-listview2]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:81
#, no-wrap
msgid "Image Preview"
msgstr "Vista previa da imaxe"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:84
#, no-wrap
msgid "Finally, an image preview side pane has been added to Thunar. No, wait, actually two of them! You can choose to either use the 'embedded' mode which will take no extra space, but hide parts of the left side pane. Or you can go for the 'standalone' mode, which will use a separate pane on the right and display as well some basic information.\n"
msgstr "Finalmente, engadiuse a Thunar un panel lateral de vista previa da imaxe. Non, espera, en realidade dous deles! Pode optar por utilizar o modo «incrustado», que non ocupará espazo extra, pero agochará partes do panel lateral esquerdo. Ou pode optar polo modo «independente», que utilizará un panel separado á dereita e amosará tamén información básica.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Embedded Image Preview][img-thunar-preview1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Vista previa da imaxe incrustada][img-thunar-preview1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Standalone Image Preview][img-thunar-preview2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Vista previa da imaxe independente][img-thunar-preview2]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:89
#, no-wrap
msgid "Undo and Redo"
msgstr "Desfacer e refacer"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to undo basic file operations and to redo them. Undo and Redo can be used for 'move', 'rename', 'trash', 'link' and 'create' operations. Per default, a history of the last 10 operations is stored, though the history length is configurable. Whenever an Undo/Redo is triggered, a notification with few details will be shown.\n"
msgstr "Agora é posíbel desfacer operacións básicas de ficheiros e refacelas. Desfacer e refacer poden usarse para as operacións de «mover», «renomear», «lixo», «ligar» e \"crear\". De xeito predeterminado, gárdase un historial das últimas 10 operacións, aínda que a lonxitude do historial é configurábel. Sempre que se active un Desfacer/Refacer, amosarase unha notificación con uns poucos detalles.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Undo and Redo][img-thunar-undo-redo]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Desfacer e refacer][img-thunar-undo-redo]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:95
#, no-wrap
msgid "File Highlight"
msgstr "Realzado de ficheiro"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "Files now can be highlighted by setting the background and the filename to different colors. This can be done via an additional tab, located in the 'properties' dialog. The view menu provides a checkbox in order to enable/disable the feature. Once enabled, files now can be shown in all the colors of the rainbow.\n"
msgstr "Os ficheiros agora poden realzarse configurando o fondo e o texto do nome do ficheiro en cores diferentes. Isto pode facerse a través dunha lapela adicional, situada no diálogo «Propiedades». O menú de visualización fornece unha caixa de verificación para activar/desactivar a funcionalidade. Unha vez activada, os ficheiros poden amosarse en todas as cores do arco da vella.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - File Highlight Options][img-thunar-hightlight1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Opcións de realzado de ficheiro][img-thunar-hightlight1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Highlighted files in List View][img-thunar-hightlight2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Realzado de ficheiros na vista de lista][img-thunar-hightlight2]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:104
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Highlighted files in Icon View][img-thunar-hightlight3]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Realzado de ficheiros na vista de iconas][img-thunar-hightlight3]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "For more information on file highlight, check the [related blog post](https://elessar-space.blogspot.com/2022/08/gsoc22-file-highlighting-in-thunar.html).\n"
msgstr "Para obter máis información sobre o realzado de ficheiros, consulte a [publicación do blog relacionada](https://elessar-space.blogspot.com/2022/08/gsoc22-file-highlighting-in-thunar.html).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to customize the toolbar according to your personal needs! An additional dialog has been added for that purpose, on which the visibility and position of specific items can be managed. As well custom actions, which appear for folders can be used in the toolbar.\n"
msgstr "Agora é posíbel personalizar a barra de ferramentas segundo as súas necesidades persoais. Engadiuse un diálogo adicional para ese fin, no que se pode xestionar a visibilidade e a posición de elementos específicos. Tamén poden usarse accións personalizadas, que aparecen para cartafoles, na barra de ferramentas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:112
#, no-wrap
msgid "When the menubar is hidden, an additional toolbar button which can be used to show the menu will be displayed.\n"
msgstr "Cando a barra de menú está agochada, amosarase un botón adicional na barra de ferramentas que se pode usar para ensinar o menú.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:114
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Toolbar with all configurable Elements][img-thunar-toolbar1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Barra de ferramentas con todos os elementos configurábeis][img-thunar-toolbar1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:116
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Toolbar Configuration Dialog][img-thunar-toolbar2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Diálogo de configuración da barra de ferramentas][img-thunar-toolbar2]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:118
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Show Menubar button][img-thunar-toolbar3]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Amosar o botón da barra de menú][img-thunar-toolbar3]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:120
#, no-wrap
msgid "For more information on the configurable toolbar, check the [related blog post](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog10.html).\n"
msgstr "Para obter máis información sobre a barra de ferramentas configurábel, consulte [a publicación do blog relacionada](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog10.html).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:124
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thunar now provides the option to use split panes. The pane separator can be moved, and its position will be stored. Via a xfconf setting, it is as well possible to have a vertical split.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:126
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Split Panes][img-thunar-splitpanes]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Paneis divididos][img-thunar-splitpanes]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:130
#, no-wrap
msgid "The status bar style was tweaked and '|' is now used to separate entries. Furthermore, it is now possible to customize it by using the context menu.\n"
msgstr "O estilo da barra de estado foi axustado e agora úsase a «|» para separar os elementos. Alem diso, agora é posíbel personalizalo empregando o menú contextual.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:132
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Statusbar Customization][img-thunar-statusbar]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Personalización da barra de estado][img-thunar-statusbar]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:133
#, no-wrap
msgid "Recursive Search"
msgstr "Busca recursiva"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:136
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thunar has now the possibility to search recursively, directly inside Thunar itself. The search is done in a separate thread and search results are added rapidly into a List View. A new row 'Location' shows where the search results are located, and the context menu provides the option 'Open Item Location' in order to travel there quickly. The preferences dialog provides an option to limit recursive search to local folders, or to disable it.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:138
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Recursive Search][img-thunar-search1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Busca recursiva][img-thunar-search1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:140
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Recursive Search Preferences][img-thunar-search2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Preferencias da busca recursiva][img-thunar-search2]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:142
#, no-wrap
msgid "For more information on the recursive search feature, check the [related blog post](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog04.html).\n"
msgstr "Para obter máis información sobre a función de busca recursiva, consulte a [publicación do blog relacionada](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog04.html).\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:143
#, no-wrap
msgid "Recently used Files"
msgstr "Ficheiros usados recentemente"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:146
#, no-wrap
msgid "Recently used files now can be accessed in the side pane. Like for the 'Recursive Search' feature, the new 'Location' row can be used in List View. Additionally, for 'Recent' a new row 'Recency' can be added to sort the files by their latest usage.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:148
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Recently Used Files][img-thunar-recent]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Ficheiros usados recentemente][img-thunar-recent]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:150
#, no-wrap
msgid "For more information on 'Recent' in Thunar check the [related blog post](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog02.html).\n"
msgstr "Para obter máis información sobre «Recente» no Thunar, consulte a [publicación do blog relacionada](http://users.uoa.gr/~sdi1800073/sources/xfce_blog02.html).\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:151
#, no-wrap
msgid "Bookmark Menu"
msgstr "Menú de marcadores"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:154
#, no-wrap
msgid "In order to keep the 'Go' menu compact, bookmarks have been moved into a separate, new 'Bookmarks' menu. The menu item 'add Bookmark' was rather hidden in the 'send to' menu in Thunar 4.18. As part of the new 'Bookmarks' menu, it is more prominent now.\n"
msgstr "Para manter o menú \"Ir\" compacto, os marcadores movéronse a un novo menú separado, chamado «Marcadores». O elemento de menú «engadir marcador» estaba bastante agochado no menú «enviar a» no Thunar 4.18. Como parte do novo menú «Marcadores», agora está máis visíbel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:156
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Bookmarks Menu][img-thunar-bookmarks]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Menú de marcadores][img-thunar-bookmarks]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:157
#, no-wrap
msgid "Trash directory"
msgstr "Cartafol da papeleira"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:160
#, no-wrap
msgid "With the new release, the trash directory provides an info bar which gives easy access to `Empty Trash` and 'Restore' functionality. When using List View, a 'Date Deleted' column will be shown, so that the files can be sorted by deletion date. Via context menu, it is now possible to select 'Restore and Show' in order to automatically open a new tab in the folder of the restored file(s).\n"
msgstr "Con esta nova versión, o cartafol da papeleira fornece unha barra de información que permite un acceso doado ás funcións «Baleirar a papeleira» e «Restaurar». Ao usar a Vista de lista, amosarase unha columna «Data de eliminación», para que os ficheiros se poidan ordenar por data de eliminación. A través do menú contextual, agora é posíbel seleccionar «Restaurar e amosar» para abrir automaticamente unha nova lapela no cartafol dos ficheiros restaurados.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:162
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Trash Infobar and Date Deleted Column][img-thunar-trash]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Barra de información da papeleira e columna coa data de eliminación][img-thunar-trash]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:163 content/about/tour416.md:23
#, no-wrap
msgid "Default Applications"
msgstr "Aplicacións predeterminadas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:166
#, no-wrap
msgid "The management to set/unset default applications for specific mime types was improved. The context menu got a dedicated item 'Set Default Application' which will open the 'ApplicationChooserDialog' with 'use as default' preselected. The dialog now has a section 'Default Application' in order to make clear which default application currently is set. If you want to remove applications from the list, right click it and select 'forget association'.\n"
msgstr "Mellorouse a xestión para estabelecer/retirar aplicacións predeterminadas para tipos MIME específicos. O menú contextual ten un elemento adicado «Estabelecer aplicación predeterminada» que abrirá o diálogo de «Aplicacións predeterminadas» con «usar de xeito predeterminado» preseleccionado. O diálogo agora ten unha sección «Aplicación predeterminada» coa finalidade de aclarar cal é a aplicación predeterminada definida actualmente. Se quere retirar aplicacións da lista, faga clic co botón dereito e seleccione «esquecer a asociación».\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:168
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Context Menu Entry to set Default Application][img-thunar-default-application1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Entrada do menú contextual para configurar a aplicación predeterminada][img-thunar-default-application1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:170
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Revamped Application Chooser Dialog][img-thunar-default-application2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Diálogo de selección de aplicacións renovado][img-thunar-default-application2]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:174
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to arrange custom actions in cascading submenus. Just enter the same submenu name for a custom action in order to place it into the same menu. If you require multiple menu levels, you can achieve that by using '/' in the path of the 'Submenu' entry.\n"
msgstr "Agora é posíbel organizar as accións personalizadas en submenús en cascada. Só ten que introducir o mesmo nome do submenú para unha acción personalizada para colocala no mesmo menú. Se precisa de varios niveis de menú, pode conseguilo usando «/» na ruta da entrada «Submenú».\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:176
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Custom Action Submenu][img-thunar-uca-submenu1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Submenú de acción personalizada][img-thunar-uca-submenu1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:178
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Custom Action Configuration Dialog][img-thunar-uca-submenu2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Diálogo de configuración de acción personalizada][img-thunar-uca-submenu2]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:182
#, no-wrap
msgid "The thumbnail settings in the preferences dialog got grouped together, and meanwhile it is possible to limit the file size for which thumbnails should be generated. That should mitigate possible performance issues by preventing thumbnail generation for huge video files.\n"
msgstr "As configuracións das miniaturas no diálogo de preferencias agrupouse e, mentres tanto, é posíbel limitar o tamaño do ficheiro para o que se deberían xerar as miniaturas. Isto debería mitigar posíbeis problemas de rendemento ao evitar a xeración de miniaturas para ficheiros de vídeo enormes.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:184
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Thumbnail Preferences][img-thunar-preferences1]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Preferencias de miniaturas][img-thunar-preferences1]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:186
#, no-wrap
msgid "File transfer operations optionally can use *.partial~ as an intermediate file now. After a transfer operation, there is now the option to verify the file checksums in order to make sure that no single bit got corrupted. Note that the checksum feature will require some extra time during copy when activated.\n"
msgstr "Opcionalmente, as operacións de transferencia de ficheiros poden usar agora *.partial~ como ficheiro intermedio. Despois dunha operación de transferencia, agora existe a opción de verificar as sumas de comprobación do ficheiro para asegurarse de que ningún bit se corrompiu. Teña en conta que a función de suma de comprobación requirirá un tempo extra durante a copia cando estea activada.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:188
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - File Transfer Preferences][img-thunar-preferences2]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Preferencias de transferencia de ficheiros][img-thunar-preferences2]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:190
#, no-wrap
msgid "For more information on the new file transfer options, check the [related blog post](https://dev.ikx.kr/GSOC-5th/).\n"
msgstr "Para obter máis información sobre as novas opcións de transferencia de ficheiros, consulte a [publicación do blog relacionada](https://dev.ikx.kr/GSOC-5th/).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:192
#, no-wrap
msgid "A checkbox was added in order to allow running shell scripts. In Thunar 4.18 it only was possible to change that behavior by changing a hidden setting. Use that option with caution!\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse unha caixa de verificación para permitir a execución de códigos do interprete de ordes. No Thunar 4.18 só era posíbel cambiar ese comportamento cambiando unha configuración oculta. Use esa opción con precaución!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:194
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Script Execution Preferences][img-thunar-preferences3]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Preferencias de execución de código][img-thunar-preferences3]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:196
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is now the possibility to restore tabs on startup, and to show the full directory path in the tab title.\n"
msgstr "Agora existe a posibilidade de restaurar as lapelas ao iniciar e amosar a ruta completa do cartafol no título da lapela.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:198
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar - Tab and Window Preferences][img-thunar-preferences4]\n"
msgstr "![Thunar - Preferencias de lapelas e xanelas][img-thunar-preferences4]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:199 content/about/tour410.md:17
#: content/about/tour46.md:131
#, no-wrap
msgid "Application Finder *(xfce4-appfinder)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:201
#, no-wrap
msgid "Configuration"
msgstr "Configuración"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:204
#, no-wrap
msgid "Application Finder got support for the 'PrefersNonDefaultGPU' property, which is useful for systems with hybrid graphic cards.\n"
msgstr "O buscador de aplicacións obtivo compatibilidade para a propiedade «Prefirir GPU non predeterminada», que é útil para sistemas con tarxetas gráficas híbridas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:206
#, no-wrap
msgid "Environment variables are now parsed when passed in collapsed mode.\n"
msgstr "Agora analízanse as variables de contorno cando se pasan en modo contraído.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:207
#, no-wrap
msgid "Appearance"
msgstr "Aparencia"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:210
#, no-wrap
msgid "An option to hide the window decorations was added.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse unha opción para agochar as decoracións das xanelas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:212
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce4-appfinder without window decorations][img-appfinder]\n"
msgstr "![O buscador de aplicacións do Xfce sen as decoracións de xanela][img-appfinder]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour418.md:213 content/about/tour412.md:9
#: content/about/tour410.md:107 content/about/tour46.md:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window Manager *(xfwm4)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:215
#, no-wrap
msgid "Workspaces"
msgstr "Espazos de traballo"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:218
#, no-wrap
msgid "Workspace setting will now work as well with other window managers.\n"
msgstr "A configuración do espazo de traballo agora funcionará tamén con outros xestores de xanelas.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:219
#, no-wrap
msgid "Compositor"
msgstr "Compositor"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:222
#, no-wrap
msgid "The compositor now supports adaptive vsync with GLX.\n"
msgstr "O compositor agora admite vsync adaptativo con GLX.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:228
#, no-wrap
msgid "Improved support for UI scaling and fix for many blurry icons in the core components when scaling is used. This will be particularly useful for Hi DPI screens.\n"
msgstr "Mellorouse a compatibilidade do escalado na interface de usuario/a e corrixíronse de moitas iconas borrosas nos compoñentes principais cando se usa o escalado. Isto será especialmente útil para pantallas Hi DPI.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour418.md:229
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window Header Bars"
msgstr "Barras de cabeceira da xanela"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:232
#, no-wrap
msgid "All header bars of Xfce Windows/Dialogs by default will be drawn by the window manager now (Xfwm4). Some dialogs optionally support 'GtkHeaderBar' (CSD) which can be enabled via a xfconf setting.\n"
msgstr "Todas as barras de cabeceira de Xfce Xanelas/Diálogos de xeito predeterminado serán debuxadas polo xestor de xanelas agora (Xfwm4). Algúns diálogos admiten opcionalmente «Barra de encabezado GTK» (CSD) que se pode activar mediante unha configuración xfconf.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour418.md:234
#, no-wrap
msgid "![xfce-appearance-settings - Preference to enable GtkHeaderBar][img-general-gtkheaderbar]\n"
msgstr "![Configuración da aparencia do Xfce - Preferencias para activar a barra de encabezado GTK][img-general-gtkheaderbar]\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour416.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.16 tour"
msgstr "Visita ao Xfce 4.16"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to new major features of Xfce 4.16. It only covers improvements made on the (user-visible) surface; for the full list of changes, see the [changelog](/download/changelogs/4.16/).\n"
msgstr "Esta visita presenta as novas características principais do Xfce 4.16. Só abrangue as melloras feitas na parte visual; para a lista completa de cambios (visíbeis para quen o usa), consulte os [rexistros de cambios](/download/changelogs/4.16/).\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour416.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Visual identity: New icons and palette"
msgstr "Identidade visual: novas iconas e paleta."

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "In order to make Xfce shine a little more out of the box and to strengthen its visual identity we created new icons for all of our core applications and based them on a shared palette to ensure consistency. We also set some further (implicit) design constraints, loosely following Adwaita's principles.\n"
msgstr "Para facer que o Xfce brille un pouco máis de fábrica e para fortalecer a súa identidade visual, creamos novas iconas para todas as nosas principais aplicacións e baseámolas nunha paleta compartida para garantir a consistencia. Tamén estabelecemos algunhas restricións de deseño (implícitas), seguindo vagamente os principios de Adwaita.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The Xfce palette][img-palette]\n"
msgstr "![A paleta Xfce][img-palette]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New upstream Xfce icons, coming in many sizes for sharp appearance][img-upstream-icons]\n"
msgstr "![Novas iconas do Xfce, en moitos tamaños para unha aparencia nítida][img-upstream-icons]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Settings Manager itself received a visual refresh of its filter box, which can now be hidden permanently. At the same time the search capabilities of the filter box were improved by searching the descriptive 'Comments' part of each dialog's launcher (aka [.desktop](https://specifications.freedesktop.org/desktop-entry-spec/desktop-entry-spec-latest.html)) file.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Visually cleaner, more powerful filter box][img-settings-manager]\n"
msgstr "![Caixa de filtro visualmente máis limpa e máis potente][img-settings-manager]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "This new dialog represents a merger between the previously available 'Mime Settings' and the 'Preferred Applications' dialogs. Consolidating both in one place means users have an easier time setting default applications to handle certain file types.\n"
msgstr "Esta nova xanela representa unha fusión entre as xanelas «Configuración Mime» dispoñíbeis anteriormente e a xanela «Aplicacións preferidas». A consolidación de ámbalas nun só lugar significa que os usuarios teñen máis doado definir aplicacións predeterminadas para manexar determinados tipos de ficheiros.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new Default Applications dialog][img-default-applications]\n"
msgstr "![A nova xanela de Aplicacións predeterminadas][img-default-applications]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour416.md:29 content/about/tour414.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "Display Dialog"
msgstr "Xanela da pantalla"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "To better support high-density displays - which come in various sizes and densities - we added fractional scaling based on the RandR extension of X11. Furthermore the preferred mode of a display is now marked with an asterisk and aspect ratios are shown along display resolutions.\n"
msgstr "Para mellorar a compatibilidade coas pantallas de alta densidade, que teñen varios tamaños e densidades, engadimos unha escala fraccionada baseada na extensión RandR de X11. Ademais, o modo preferido dunha pantalla agora está marcado cun asterisco e as relacións de aspecto amósanse ao longo das resolucións de pantalla.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Fractional scaling support][img-display-dialog]\n"
msgstr "![Admisión de escala fraccionada][img-display-dialog]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour416.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Keyboard Shortcuts"
msgstr "Atallos do teclado"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "In order to make things easier for our users we added more default keyboard shortcuts out of the box, for instance for window tiling or to open Thunar. The keyboard shortcuts dialog itself was also visually updated.\n"
msgstr "Para facilitar as cousas aos nosos usuarios, engadimos máis atallos de teclado predeterminados de fábrica, como por exemplo, para o mosaico de xanelas ou para abrir o Thunar. A xanela de atallos de teclado tamén se actualizou visualmente.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Visually updated keyboard shortcuts dialog][img-keyboard-shortcuts]\n"
msgstr "![A xanela de atallos de teclado actualizouse visualmente][img-keyboard-shortcuts]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "In Thunar's copy and move dialogs users can now easily pause the respective file operation. Furthermore support for queued file transfer, remembering view settings per folder and support for transparency in Gtk themes was added.\n"
msgstr "Nas xanelas de copia e movemento de Thunar os usuarios agora poden interromper doadamente a respectiva operación de ficheiro. Amais, engadiuse a capacidade de  transferir ficheiros en cola, lembrar as opcións de visualización por cartafol e transparencia nos temas Gtk.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar can now pause copying/moving files][img-thunar-copy]\n"
msgstr "![Agora Thunar pode interromper a copia e movemento de ficheiros][img-thunar-copy]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel received quite a few noteworthy updates, an animation for autohide and intellihide, a new 'Status Tray' plugin that combines both legacy Systray item support with modern StatusNotifier item support, dark mode support, launchers showing additional actions on right-click, window buttons offering to 'Launch a new instance...' and much more.\n"
msgstr "O panel recibiu bastantes actualizacións dignas de mención, unha animación para o agochado automático e  o agochado intelixente, un novo engadido de \"Zona de estado\" que combina tanto a compatibilidade de elementos herdados da zona do sistema como elementos modernos do notificador de estado, compatibilidade co modo escuro, iniciadores que amosan accións adicionais ao facer clic co botón dereito, xanela con botóns que fornecen a opción de \"Iniciar unha nova instancia ...\" e moito máis.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Dark mode enabled in the panel's settings dialog][img-panel-dark]\n"
msgstr "![O  modo escuro activado na xanela de configuración do panel][img-panel-dark]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:54
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new statustray plugin][img-panel-statustray]\n"
msgstr "![O novo engadido de zona do sistema][img-panel-statustray]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Autohide animation][img-panel-autohide]\n"
msgstr "![Animación de agochado automático][img-panel-autohide]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:58
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Launch a new instance!][img-panel-launch]\n"
msgstr "![Iniciar unha nova instancia!][img-panel-launch]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour416.md:59
#, no-wrap
msgid "About Dialog *(xfce4-about)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "Not only was the Xfce tab reworked to be more visually appealing and easily parsable, a separate tab showing basic information about the user's system was also added.\n"
msgstr "Non só se refixo a lapela do Xfce para ser máis atractiva visualmente e doadamente analizábel, tamén se engadiu unha nova lapela que amosa información básica sobre o sistema do usuario.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:64
#, no-wrap
msgid "![About Xfce][img-about-xfce]\n"
msgstr "![Sobre o Xfce][img-about-xfce]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "![About System][img-about-system]\n"
msgstr "![Sobre o sistema][img-about-system]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour416.md:67 content/about/tour414.md:69
#: content/about/tour412.md:81
#, no-wrap
msgid "Power Manager *(xfce4-power-manager)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "The settings dialog of the power manager was cleaned up and shows either 'on battery' or 'plugged in' settings as opposed to both in a huge table.\n"
msgstr "Limpouse a xanela de axustes do xestor de enerxía e amosa a configuración \"con batería\" ou \"conectado\" en contraposición ás dúas nunha enorme táboa.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour416.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Power Manager settings][img-powermanager]\n"
msgstr "![Configuración do xestor de enerxía][img-powermanager]\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour414.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.14 tour"
msgstr "Visita ao Xfce 4.14"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to new major features of Xfce 4.14. It only covers improvements made on the surface; for the full list of changes, see the [changelogs](/download/changelogs/).\n"
msgstr "Esta visita presenta as novas características principais do Xfce 4.14. Só abrangue as melloras feitas na parte visual; para a lista completa de cambios (visíbeis para quen o usa), consulte os [rexistros de cambios](/download/changelogs/).\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Color Profiles Dialog"
msgstr "Xanela de perfís de cor"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new dialog for setting [color profiles](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/4.14/color) for monitors, printers and scanners was introduced. It acts as a frontend to various daemons that talk directly to colord, e.g. saned (scanners), cupsd (printers) or xiccd (monitors).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new color profiles dialog][img-color-profiles]\n"
msgstr "![A nova xanela de perfís de cor][img-color-profiles]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "Several improvements were made to the [display dialog](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/4.14/display). Apart from tweaks to the user interface to make the interaction more intuitive (introducing display numbering, showing a primary indicator with quick access to panel, notification and desktop settings etc.) a feature to save and restore complete display profiles was added. If a single profile exists for a setup, the Xfce settings daemon will automatically enable it. If multiple profiles exist, it will pop up the minimal dialog and offer all profiles in addition to the previously available pre-sets (internal only, mirror, extend and external only).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The primary indicator][img-display-general]\n"
msgstr "![O indicador primario][img-display-general]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The display profile list][img-display-advanced]\n"
msgstr "![A lista de perfís de pantalla][img-display-advanced]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The improved minimal dialog - in this case only showing one profile only which never happens anymore now ;)][img-display-minimal]\n"
msgstr "![A xanela mínima mellorada - neste caso só amosa un perfil ;)][img-display-minimal]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "Accessibility"
msgstr "Accesibilidade"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "One [accessibility](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/4.14/accessibility) feature that people coming from other desktop environments or operating systems were still missing is to set a (custom) keyboard shortcut (by default: Super+F1) to visually locate the mouse pointer. This feature was added in Xfce 4.14.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The mouse pointer location animation][img-locate-mouse]\n"
msgstr "![A animación da localización do punteiro do rato][img-locate-mouse]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "General: Icon size"
msgstr "Xeral: tamaño das iconas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new feature that we introduced in the [panel](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-panel/4.14/start) is being able to control the icon size of all plugins. ('All' may not be technically correct, as not all plugins support the new API as of now, but now they *can*. Plus the Window buttons plugin is an exception, because libwnck doesn't allow anything other than 16px or 32px.) This means setups that were previously impossible, because icons would upscale automatically according to size-steps hard-coded in the panel, are now possible (see below).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "![A 32px tall panel with 16px icons][img-panel-iconsize]\n"
msgstr "![Un panel de 32 píxeles de alto con iconas de 16 píxeles][img-panel-iconsize]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window buttons: Grouping"
msgstr "Botóns de xanela: agrupamento"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "Grouping was improved in the [Window buttons plugin](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-panel/4.14/tasklist), both functionally (by improving the matching and icon-finding) and visually by providing a new group indicator that is less likely to clash with window titles containing an enumeration in brackets.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new group indicator (two terminal windows)][img-panel-group]\n"
msgstr "![O novo indicador de agrupamento (con dúas xanelas de terminal)][img-panel-group]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour414.md:47
#, no-wrap
msgid "Session *(xfce4-session)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:49 content/about/tour412.md:89
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings Dialog"
msgstr "Diálogo de configuración"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "As soon as a [session](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-session/4.14/preferences) has been saved a new tab is dynamically added to the settings dialog displaying all saved sessions and allowing to delete one or all of them. This should make it way more discoverable for users if they actually have saved sessions that influence the startup behavior - previously this had to be checked manually in the filesystem.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:54
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The settings dialog after saving a session][img-session-saved]\n"
msgstr "![A xanela de configuración despois de gardar unha sesión][img-session-saved]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:57
#, no-wrap
msgid "Pathbar"
msgstr "Barra de ruta"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "Up to Xfce 4.12 [Thunar](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/4.14/start) offered two options for the pathbar/locationbar. The best of both worlds has now been mixed into one powerful pathbar, featuring both clickable breadcrumbs (i.e. folders), an easily accessible way to hand-type a path as well as an improved look.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar's new pathbar][img-thunar-pathbar]\n"
msgstr "![A nova barra de ruta do Thunar][img-thunar-pathbar]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:63
#, no-wrap
msgid "Folder Thumbnailer"
msgstr "Miniatura de cartafol"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "Same as on the Desktop you can now save an image with the name 'folder.jpg' in a folder and get it displayed as its icon in the File Manager. Note: [Please read the docs](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/tumbler/available_plugins#customized_thumbnailer_for_folders) on how to set this up (if your distribution hasn't enabled it by default).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar's new folder thumbnails][img-thunar-folder-jpg]\n"
msgstr "![Novas miniaturas de cartafol do Thunar][img-thunar-folder-jpg]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:71 content/about/tour414.md:85
#: content/about/tour412.md:83
#, no-wrap
msgid "Panel Plugin"
msgstr "Engadido de panel"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [Power Manager's panel plugin](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-power-manager/4.14/panel-plugin) supports symbolic icons now and uses the standard UPower icon names (making it more compatible with all icon themes). It also shows an indicator if applications inhibit power management functions like suspend (when power is low) or display dimming (after a defined timeout).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Parole's video playback is inhibiting power management][img-xfpm-inhibitors]\n"
msgstr "![A reprodución de vídeo de Parole está inhibindo a xestión da enerxía][img-xfpm-inhibitors]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour414.md:77
#, no-wrap
msgid "Notification Service *(xfce4-notifyd)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour414.md:79 content/about/tour44.md:123
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings"
msgstr "Configuración"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "Several new features have been added in Xfce's [Notification service](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/notifyd/start), including a notifications log, the possibility to disable notifications per application, a global 'Do Not Disturb' mode, which inhibits all notifications, and finally a new animation ('slide out').\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:84
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new notification animation 'slide out'][img-notifyd-slideout]\n"
msgstr "![A nova animación de notificación «esborrexer»][img-notifyd-slideout]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "Furthermore a new panel plugin was added which provides quick access to both the 'Do Not Disturb' mode as well as the log of recent notifications.\n"
msgstr "Tamén se incorporou un novo engadido de panel que fornece acceso rápido tanto ao modo «Non molestar» como ao rexistro de notificacións recentes.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:90
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new panel plugin][img-notifyd-panel]\n"
msgstr "![O novo engadido de panel][img-notifyd-panel]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:91 content/about/tour412.md:141
#, no-wrap
msgid "Media Player *(parole)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:93
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mini Mode"
msgstr "Modo mini"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:96
#, no-wrap
msgid "[Parole](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/parole/start) now features a 'Mini Mode', where the interface is simplified to just display the album artwork and can be positioned over other windows without getting in the way.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Just right-click anywhere in the player window to select 'Mini Mode'...][img-parole-normal-mode]\n"
msgstr "![Só ten que facer clic co botón dereito en calquera lugar da xanela do reprodutor para seleccionar «Modo mini» ...][img-parole-normal-mode]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Afterwards, enjoy a truly minimalistic playback experience!][img-parole-mini-mode]\n"
msgstr "![Despois, goce dunha experiencia de reprodución realmente minimalista.][img-parole-mini-mode]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour414.md:101
#, no-wrap
msgid "Screensaver *(xfce4-screensaver)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour414.md:103
#, no-wrap
msgid "A Modern Locking Experience"
msgstr "Unha experiencia moderna de bloqueo"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "The new Xfce [Screensaver](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/screensaver/start) provides a configurable lockscreen experience. You can selectively toggle the lock screen and screensaver, and all Xscreensaver themes are supported (with configuration options) out of the box. If you prefer a blank screen, Xfce Screensaver also includes a blank screen option with DPMS integration.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:108
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The new lock screen, sharing styles with LightDM GTK+ Greeter for a consistent experience.][img-saver-dialog]\n"
msgstr "![A nova pantalla de bloqueo, que comparte estilos con LightDM GTK+ Greeter para unha experiencia consistente.][img-saver-dialog]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Make it your own. Xfce Screensaver supports a multitude of configuration options.][img-saver-preferences]\n"
msgstr "![Fágao seu. O protector de pantalla do Xfce admite multitude de opcións de configuración.][img-saver-preferences]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour414.md:111
#, no-wrap
msgid "Terminal *(xfce4-terminal)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:114
#, no-wrap
msgid "Lots and lots of features have accumulated in the [Terminal](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/terminal/start) over the last years. Amongst them 'Undo Close Tab' and 'Close Other Tabs' functionality (similar to web browsers), 'Copy Input to All Tabs', 'Set Title Color' (allows to customize tab text color), 'Save Contents' (saves tab contents to a file), an 'Unsafe Paste' dialog (which prevents the terminal from auto-executing pasted text as a command) and support for zooming. Finally when closing a tab or window, there is a new check for running processes which prevents accidentally closing a terminal that is running a process.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:116
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Zooming, 'Save Contents' and much more!][img-terminal]\n"
msgstr "![Aumentar/Diminuír, «gardar contido» e moito máis!][img-terminal]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour414.md:117
#, no-wrap
msgid "Screenshooter *(xfce4-screenshooter)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:120
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Xfce [Screenshooter](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/screenshooter/start) gained several notable features, amongst others seeing the size of the screenshot while dragging, moving the selection with the mouse and better [imgur](https://imgur.com) integration.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour414.md:122
#, no-wrap
msgid "![I can drag and move the screenshot area, whoop whoop!][img-screenshooter]\n"
msgstr "![Poda arrastrar e mover a área de captura de pantalla, vaia!][img-screenshooter]\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour412.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.12 tour"
msgstr "Visita ao Xfce 4.12"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to new major features of Xfce 4.12. It only covers improvements made on the surface; for the full list of changes, see the [changelogs](/download/changelogs/).\n"
msgstr "Esta visita presenta as novas características principais do Xfce 4.12. Só abrangue as melloras feitas na parte visual; para a lista completa de cambios, consulte os rexistros de cambios\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window Switcher Dialog"
msgstr "Diálogo de troco de xanelas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "The window manager's Alt+Tab dialog is now fully themeable and also gained two new modes: a 'List' mode and a 'Window Preview' mode. Furthermore users use their mouse to click/select the window they want to give focus to.\n"
msgstr "O diálogo de Alt + Tab do xestor de xanelas agora é totalmente personalizábel con temas e tamén gañou dous modos novos: un modo «Lista» e un modo «Vista previa de xanela». Ademais, os usuarios poden usar o seu rato para premer/seleccionar a xanela na que desexan poñer o foco.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The traditional dialog is fully themable now][img-tabwin-simple-crop]\n"
msgstr "![O diálogo tradicional agora é completamente personalizábel con temas][img-tabwin-simple-crop]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "The List mode of the Alt-Tab dialog.\n"
msgstr "O modo de lista do diálogo Alt-Tab.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "![List mode of Alt-Tab, showing all window titles][img-tabwin-list-crop]\n"
msgstr "![Modo de lista de Alt-Tab, amosando todos os títulos de xanela][img-tabwin-list-crop]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Window Preview mode shows thumbnails of windows' content alongside their icon. Activating the compositor is a prerequisite for this mode.\n"
msgstr "O modo vista previa de xanela amosa miniaturas do contido das xanelas xunto coa sua icona. A activación do compositor é un requisito previo para este modo.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Window thumbnails][img-tabwin-preview-crop]\n"
msgstr "![Miniaturas das xanelas][img-tabwin-preview-crop]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:25
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tiling, Zooming, Client-side Decorations"
msgstr "Mosaico, zum, decoracións do lado do cliente"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support for Client-Side Decorations (CSDs) has been improved. They now properly snap to screen and panel borders, and tile correctly, even with shadows.\n"
msgstr "A compatibilidade cos decoradores do lado do cliente (CSD) foi mellorada. Agora encaixan correctamente a pantalla e os bordos do panel, e xeran o mosaico correctamente, mesmo con sombras.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Gtk3 apps with their decorations drawn by the client][img-xfwm4-csd]\n"
msgstr "![Aplicacións de Gtk3 coas súas decoracións debuxadas polo cliente][img-xfwm4-csd]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window tiling mode was improved by providing support for corner-tiling, and a new zooming mode was added using Alt + Mouse Wheel.\n"
msgstr "O modo mosaico de xanelas mellorouse fornecendo compatibilidade para o mosaico de esquina, e engadiuse un novo modo de zum mediante Alt + Roda do rato.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Drag and drop a window to a corner to tile it][img-xfwm4-tiling-small]\n"
msgstr "![Arrastre e solte unha xanela cara a esquina para facela mosaico.][img-xfwm4-tiling-small]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "HiDPI Support"
msgstr "Compatibilidade HiDPI"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "In order to better support modern hi-resolution screens, two new Xfwm4 themes were added (hdpi, xhdpi).\n"
msgstr "Para mellor compatibilidade coas pantallas modernas de alta resolución, engadíronse dous novos temas de Xfwm4 (hdpi, xhdpi).\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "Intelligent Hiding"
msgstr "Agochar de xeito intelixente"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel can now intelligently hide itself when a window is dragged near it.\n"
msgstr "O panel agora pode agocharse de xeito intelixente cando se arrastra unha xanela cerca del.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Oh what is this window??][img-panel-shown]\n"
msgstr "![Oh, o que é esta xanela??][img-panel-shown]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Don't come closer!][img-panel-shown-stack]\n"
msgstr "![Non se achegue!][img-panel-shown-stack]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Hah! Now you don't see me!][img-panel-hidden]\n"
msgstr "![Agora non me ves!][img-panel-hidden]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:51
#, no-wrap
msgid "Gtk3 plugins"
msgstr "Engadidos de Gtk3"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:54
#, no-wrap
msgid "Infrastructure was added to be able to load Gtk3 plugins alongside Gtk2 plugins.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse a infraestrutura para poder cargar engadidos Gtk3 xunto a engadidos Gtk2.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:58
#, no-wrap
msgid "The desktop has a new wallpaper settings dialog with many new options and better multi-monitor support. Drag the dialog to the display or workspace where you want to change the wallpaper.\n"
msgstr "O escritorio ten un novo diálogo de configuración de fondos con moitas opcións novas e unha mellor compatibilidade con múltiples pantallas. Arrastre a caixa de diálogo á pantalla ou espazo de traballo onde desexa cambiar o fondo.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Better multi-monitor support][img-xfdesktop-properties-multiworkspace]\n"
msgstr "![Mellor compatibilidade para o uso de múltiples pantallas][img-xfdesktop-properties-multiworkspace]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "Uncheck 'apply to all workspaces' to set a different wallpaper for each workspace.\n"
msgstr "Desmarque «Aplicar a todos os espazos de traballo» para estabelecer un fondo de pantalla diferente para cada espazo de traballo.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour412.md:63 content/about/tour410.md:63
#: content/about/tour48.md:73 content/about/tour46.md:85
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings *(xfce4-settings)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support for multi-monitor use was vastly improved in the display settings dialog. Upon connecting a new display, a quick setup popup offers some of the most-used modes for users to quickly change their layout.\n"
msgstr "A compatibilidade para o uso de múltiples pantallas foi mellorado moito no diálogo de configuración de visualización. Ao conectar unha nova pantalla, unha xanela emerxente rápida fornece algúns dos modos máis empregados para que os usuarios muden rapidamente a disposición.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Configure multiple displays][img-xfce4-display-settings-twoscreens]\n"
msgstr "![Configure múltiples pantallas][img-xfce4-display-settings-twoscreens]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Choose your layout when plugging in a new display][img-xfce4-display-layout]\n"
msgstr "![Escolla a disposición ao conectar unha nova pantalla][img-xfce4-display-layout]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "The appearance dialog now showcases previews for styles and icons.\n"
msgstr "O diálogo de aparencia agora amosa as vistas previas de estilos e iconas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Gtk style preview][img-xfce4-appearance-settings-style]\n"
msgstr "![Vista previa do estilo Gtk][img-xfce4-appearance-settings-style]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Icon theme preview][img-xfce4-appearance-settings-icons]\n"
msgstr "![Vista previa do tema de iconas][img-xfce4-appearance-settings-icons]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new panel plugin was created which allows you to quickly control your screen brightness, either via the menu or by simply using your mouse's scroll wheel over the plugin. The plugin's menu also shows all other connected devices with a power status, e.g. bluetooth keyboards or wireless mice. It still offers quick access to the presentation mode, which inhibits your screensaver for as long as the option is active.\n"
msgstr "Creouse un novo engadido de panel que permite controlar rapidamente o brillo da pantalla, xa sexa mediante o menú ou simplemente usando a roda de desprazamento do rato sobre o engadido. O menú do engadido tamén amosa todos os outros dispositivos conectados cun estado de enerxía, por exemplo teclados bluetooth ou ratos sen fíos. Fornece un acceso rápido ao modo de presentación, o cal inhibe o protector de pantalla mentres a opción estea activa.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The plugin's menu allows users to control screen brightness and check on the remaining uptime their battery provides.][img-xfpm-plugin-crop]\n"
msgstr "![O menú do engadido permite aos usuarios controlar o brillo da pantalla e comprobar o tempo de funcionamento restante que fornece a batería.][img-xfpm-plugin-crop]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "The settings dialog was completely restructured (separating button/lid events from system and display behavior) and offers a clearer way of setting your preferences.\n"
msgstr "O diálogo de configuración foi completamente reestruturado (separando os eventos do botón/tampa do sistema e o comportamento da pantalla) fornecendo un xeito forma máis claro de configurar as súas preferencias.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Configure what action to take when certain buttons are pressed or the laptop lid is closed][img-xfpm-prefs-general]\n"
msgstr "![Configure a acción que se debe tomar cando se premen determinados botóns ou se pecha a tampa do portátil][img-xfpm-prefs-general]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:96
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Configure what to do when the user is inactive or battery is drained][img-xfpm-prefs-system]\n"
msgstr "![Configure o que facer cando o usuario está inactivo ou a batería está en niveis baixos][img-xfpm-prefs-system]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Manage display power management][img-xfpm-prefs-display]\n"
msgstr "![Configure a xestión de enerxía da pantalla][img-xfpm-prefs-display]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Display information on all connected devices][img-xfpm-prefs-devices]\n"
msgstr "![Amosar a información en todos os dispositivos conectados][img-xfpm-prefs-devices]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "When light-locker is available, you can control its settings directly via the power manager.\n"
msgstr "Cando o «light-locker» está dispoñíbel, pode controlar a súa configuración directamente a través do xestor de enerxía.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:104
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Setup light-locker integration][img-xfpm-prefs-security]\n"
msgstr "![Configurar a integración do «light-locker»][img-xfpm-prefs-security]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:107
#, no-wrap
msgid "Tab Support"
msgstr "Compatibilidade para lapelas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "A long-awaited feature was added: you can now open multiple folders in the same Thunar window.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse unha característica moi agardada: agora pode abrir varios cartafoles na mesma xanela de Thunar.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:112
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Browse multiple directories][img-thunar-tabs]\n"
msgstr "![Explorar múltiples cartafoles][img-thunar-tabs]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:114
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thunar now displays the remaining free space with a bar in a folder properties.\n"
msgstr "Thunar agora amosa o espazo libre restante cunha barra de propiedades no cartafol.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:116
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Freespace bar][img-thunar-freespace]\n"
msgstr "![Barra de espazo libre][img-thunar-freespace]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:118
#, no-wrap
msgid "And you can select multiple files to see their properties at once.\n"
msgstr "E pode seleccionar varios ficheiros para ver as súas propiedades ao mesmo tempo.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:120
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Multiple File Properties][img-thunar-multifiles-props]\n"
msgstr "![Propiedades de múltiples ficheiros][img-thunar-multifiles-props]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour412.md:121
#, no-wrap
msgid "Goodies"
msgstr "Extras"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:124
#, no-wrap
msgid "There have been lots of improvements to our goodies, and some new and shiny applications have been added by new contributors.\n"
msgstr "Houbo moitas melloras nos nosos extras e engadíronse novas e brillantes aplicacións por parte de novos colaboradores.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:125
#, no-wrap
msgid "Alternative panel menu plugin *(xfce4-whiskermenu)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:128
#, no-wrap
msgid "The whisker menu is an alternative to the traditional menu plugin, showing favourites, allowing to search through existing apps and much more.\n"
msgstr "O menú «whisker» é unha alternativa ao engadido tradicional do menú, que amosa os favoritos, permitindo buscar en aplicacións existentes e moito máis.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:130
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Browse through categories][img-whiskermenu-default]\n"
msgstr "![Explorar a través das categorías][img-whiskermenu-default]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:132
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Search for an application][img-whiskermenu-search]\n"
msgstr "![Buscar unha aplicación][img-whiskermenu-search]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:133
#, no-wrap
msgid "Task Manager *(xfce4-taskmanager)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:136
#, no-wrap
msgid "The task manager got a revamped user interface, a filter and also supports Gtk3 now.\n"
msgstr "O xestor de tarefas obtivo unha interface de usuario renovada, un filtro e agora tamén é compatíbel con Gtk3.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:138
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Show processes as a tree][img-taskman-tree]\n"
msgstr "![Mostrar os procesos nunha árbore][img-taskman-tree]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:140
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Filter processes by name][img-taskman-filter]\n"
msgstr "![Filtrar os procesos por nome][img-taskman-filter]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:144
#, no-wrap
msgid "Parole's UI was totally redone in Gtk3. It now supports multiple video backends, makes more efficient use of your resources and contains a few novel plugins.\n"
msgstr "A interface de usuario do Parole foi refeita totalmente en Gtk3. Agora admite varias infraestruturas de vídeo, fai un uso máis eficiente dos seus recursos e contén algúns engadidos novos.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:146
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Watch videos][img-parole]\n"
msgstr "![Ver vídeos][img-parole]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:148
#, no-wrap
msgid "The media controls are now contained in a slide-over overlay (with a configurable timeout).\n"
msgstr "Os controis multimedia agora están contidos nunha superposición de diapositivas (cun ​​tempo de espera configurábel).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:150
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Listen to music][img-parole-audio]\n"
msgstr "![Escoitar música][img-parole-audio]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour412.md:151
#, no-wrap
msgid "Text Editor *(mousepad)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:154
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mousepad was totally rewritten, gained a settings dialog and now supports Gtk3.\n"
msgstr "O mousepad foi totalmente rescrito, recibiu un diálogo de configuración e agora admite con Gtk3.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:156
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New mousepad settings][img-mousepad-prefs]\n"
msgstr "![Novas configuracións de mousepad][img-mousepad-prefs]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour412.md:157
#, no-wrap
msgid "A note on Xfce's portability"
msgstr "Unha nota sobre a migración do Xfce"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour412.md:160
#, no-wrap
msgid "All but one of those screenshots were taken on machines running OpenBSD -current, a good proof that Xfce is still portable and friendly to all Unix systems.\n"
msgstr "Todas agás unha destas capturas de pantalla foron tomadas en máquinas que executan unha versión actual de OpenBSD, unha boa proba de que Xfce aínda é portátil e amigábel con todos os sistemas Unix.\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour410.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.10 tour"
msgstr "Visita ao Xfce 4.10"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to new major features of Xfce 4.10. It only covers the visual part of what has been done; for the full list of changes, see the [changelogs](/download/changelogs/).\n"
msgstr "Esta visita presentaralle as novas características principais do Xfce 4.10. Só cobre a parte visual do que se fixo; para a lista completa de cambios, consulte os [rexistros de cambios](/download/changelogs/).\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour410.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Online Documentation"
msgstr "Documentación na rede"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "During the 4.10 development we've decided to remove user manuals from the packages and move them to an online wiki at [docs.xfce.org](https://docs.xfce.org). The reason for this change is to make [contributing](https://docs.xfce.org/wiki/documentation) and updating the documentation easier.\n"
msgstr "Durante o desenvolvemento da versión 4.10, decidimos eliminar os manuais de usuario dos paquetes e movelos a un wiki na rede en [docs.xfce.org](https://docs.xfce.org). O motivo deste cambio é facilitar a [contribución](https://docs.xfce.org/wiki/documentation) e a actualización da documentación.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "![When you click a Help button Xfce will ask you to go to an online wiki page][img-online-help]\n"
msgstr "![Cando preme nun botón de axuda, o Xfce pediralle que vaia a unha páxina wiki na rede][img-online-help]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "We hope that with the introduction of the wiki it will be easier for developers and contributors to maintain the documentation.\n"
msgstr "Agardamos que coa introdución do wiki sexa máis doado para os desenvolvedores e colaboradores manter a documentación.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Collapsed view of the Application Finder][img-appfinder-collapsed]\n"
msgstr "![Vista contraída do buscador de aplicacións][img-appfinder-collapsed]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "The application finder has been completely rewritten and combines the functionality of the old appfinder and xfrun4. Apart from user interface improvements, it now allows creating custom actions matching a prefix or a regex pattern.\n"
msgstr "O buscador de aplicacións foi completamente reescrito e combina a funcionalidade do antigo «appfinder» e «xfrun4». Alén das melloras na interface de usuario, agora permite crear accións personalizadas que coincidan cun prefixo ou un patrón de expresión regular.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Expanded view of the Application Finder][img-appfinder-expanded]\n"
msgstr "![Vista expandida do buscador de aplicacións][img-appfinder-expanded]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "Multiple Rows"
msgstr "Varias filas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "In 4.10 there is a single panel-wide option for configuring the number of rows in the panel. Some plugins (e.g. *launchers*) fit a single row, while others, like window buttons are allowed to occupy full width of the panel.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "![A horizontal panel with a number of rows set to three][img-panel-rows]\n"
msgstr "![Un panel horizontal cun número de filas definido a tres][img-panel-rows]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Deskbar Mode"
msgstr "Modo barra de escritorio"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel features a new configuration called a *deskbar* mode. In the deskbar mode the panel is aligned vertically, just like in the vertical mode, but the plugins are laid out horizontally. With multiple rows, it allows creating wide vertical panels suitable for wide-screen setups.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "![A panel in Deskbar mode with a number of rows set to five][img-panel-deskbar]\n"
msgstr "![Un panel no modo de barra de escritorio con varias filas estabelecidas a cinco][img-panel-deskbar]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:39
#, no-wrap
msgid "Actions Plugin"
msgstr "Engadido de accións"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "Session plugin from the xfce4-session package has been merged with a rewritten *actions* plugin\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Action plugin in a menu mode (left), and in a button mode (right)][img-panel-actions]\n"
msgstr "![O engadido acción nun modo menú (esquerda), e nun mofo botón (dereita)][img-panel-actions]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:45
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window Buttons"
msgstr "Botóns de xanela"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "The *window buttons* plugin no longer expands, which makes the plugin positioning more flexible. In order to restore the previous behavior please add a transparent *separator* plugin with the **Expand** option enabled just behind the window buttons plugin.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "There are few visual changes in this release of Thunar. The window has less padding and the position of the status bar has been adjusted.\n"
msgstr "Hai poucas diferenzas visuais neste lanzamento de Thunar. A xanela ten menos recheo e a posición da barra de estado foi axustada.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour410.md:53 content/about/tour46.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Session Manager *(xfce4-session)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "The *session manager*'s settings dialog has a button for clearing the saved session (no more `rm -r ~/.config/sessions`). Xfce4-tips has been removed and the session manager can now lock the screen before suspending or hibernating the system.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:57
#, no-wrap
msgid "Applications Autostart"
msgstr "Inicio automático de aplicacións"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "Another noticeable change is the way GNOME and KDE compatibility works. Compatibility check boxes only enable services, which have to be started before other applications (*gnome-keyring* and *gconf* for GNOME and *kdeinit* for KDE). All other autostart applications are available from **Applications Autostart**, but they are listed using an italic font and not enabled by default in order to distinguish them from Xfce applications. Unlike in previous versions of Xfce, compatibility services can be started independently from each other.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Applications, which are not a part of Xfce, are listed using an italic font][img-session-autostart]\n"
msgstr "![Aplicacións, as cales non forman parte do Xfce, son listadas usando unha letra cursiva.][img-session-autostart]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:65
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings Daemon"
msgstr "Daemon de configuración"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.8 used two processes for applying settings: `xfce4-settings-helper` and `xfsettingsd`. In 4.10 they have been merged into xfsettingsd, which now handles all system settings.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "The new *settings manager* groups configuration dialogs in categories and allows you to search for their names or descriptions. Most of the dialogs are also now embedded in the settings manager window (this was a compile-time option in Xfce 4.8).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "![The settings manager with icons grouped by category and a search filter applied][img-settings-manager]\n"
msgstr "![O xestor de configuración con iconas agrupadas por categoría e un filtro de busca aplicado][img-settings-manager]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:75
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings Editor"
msgstr "Editor da configuración"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "The *settings editor* no longer collapses the entire tree when you edit a property (this is because it now reloads a single cell rather than the whole tree). Most properties can now be edited in-place, making it easier to quickly adjust settings.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "Using settings editor you can also monitor changes of settings in a selected channel. Right-click on a channel in the main window, and select **Monitor** to display the monitor window.\n"
msgstr "Usando o editor de configuración tamén pode supervisar os cambios de configuración nunha canle seleccionada. Prema co botón dereito sobre unha canle na xanela principal e seleccione **Monitorizar** para amosar a xanela de monitorización.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Settings editor with an open channel monitor, while editing a property in-place][img-settings-editor]\n"
msgstr "![O editor de configuración cunha monitorización de canle aberta, ao modificar unha propiedade no mesmo][img-settings-editor]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:83
#, no-wrap
msgid "MIME Type Editor"
msgstr "Editor de tipos MIME"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "In the last couple of years, many people were asking for a tool to manage their file type associations. The new *MIME type editor* does just that. It allows you to easily assign a default application to a file type, see your changes and reset them to default settings when necessary. Note that it does not allow you to change the system MIME Type definitions (add or remove types and change icons).\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "![MIME types matching a pattern and a menu for selecting a default application][img-settings-mime]\n"
msgstr "![Os tipos MIME que coinciden cun patrón e un menú para seleccionar unha aplicación predeterminada][img-settings-mime]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour410.md:89
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mouse and Touchpad"
msgstr "Rato e área táctil"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "The *mouse and touchpad* dialog is capable of handling basic Synaptics and Wacom properties in the GUI. A settings daemon running in the background handles all kinds of device properties, as documented in the [mouse settings](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/mouse) wiki.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Synaptics touchpad settings in the mouse and touchpad dialog][img-settings-mouse]\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "In 4.10 you can drag and drop a tarball with a downloaded theme onto the *style* or *icon* list. Xfce will attempt to extract and install the files into the `~/.themes` or `~/.icons` directory.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "Although the initial plan for Xfce 4.10 was to integrate desktop handling in Thunar, we have decided not to do it at this time yet. Meanwhile, Xfdesktop has gained support for single-click operation, automated background image cycling and thumbnail rendering.\n"
msgstr "Aínda que o plan inicial para o Xfce 4.10 era integrar o manexo do escritorio en Thunar, decidiuse non facelo neste momento. Mentres tanto, «Xfdesktop» permite operacións dun só clic, ciclos automáticos de imaxes de fondo e renderización de miniaturas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:104
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Desktop with image thumbnails and support for single-click operation][img-xfdesktop]\n"
msgstr "![Escritorio con miniaturas de imaxe e compatibilidade para operacións dun só clic][img-xfdesktop]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfdesktop is now shipped with a new default background image.\n"
msgstr "O «Xfdesktop» é agora é distribuído cunha nova imaxe de fondo predeterminada.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour410.md:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfwm4 can now tile a window when you drag it to the edge of the screen. This feature is optional and is disabled by default. In such a case windows can still be tiled using a keyboard shortcut. Another improvement is a better theming support and cursor key navigation in the tab window (Alt+Tab).\n"
msgstr "O «Xfwm4» agora pode axustar unha xanela cando a arrastra até o bordo da pantalla. Esta característica é opcional e está desactivada por defecto. Nese caso, as xanelas aínda poden estar en mosaico usando un atallo de teclado. Outra mellora é a mellor compatibilidade de temas e na alternancia na navegación da xanela do tabulador (Alt + Tab).\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour48.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.8 tour"
msgstr "Visita ao Xfce 4.8"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "This tour will introduce you to all the new major visual features in Xfce 4.8. This is only the visual part of what has been done; for a full list of changes, see the [changelogs](/download/changelogs/).\n"
msgstr "Esta visita presentaralle todas as novas funcionalidades visuais no Xfce 4.8. Esta é só a parte visual do que se fixo. Para obter unha lista completa de cambios, consulte os [rexistros de cambios](/download/changelogs/).\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Remote shares browsing"
msgstr "Navegación por cartafoles remotos"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thunar now has optional support for GVFS which will allow you to browse remote shares using Thunar: FTP, Windows Shares, WebDav and SSH servers...\n"
msgstr "O Thunar agora ten compatibilidade opcional para GVFS que lle permitirá navegar por cartafoles remotos usando Thunar: servidores FTP, Windows Accións, WebDav e SSH ...\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar browsing a remote share][img-thunar-remote]\n"
msgstr "![O Thunar navegando nun cartafol remoto ][img-thunar-remote]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:17
#, no-wrap
msgid "New file operations progress dialog"
msgstr "Novo diálogo de progreso de operacións de ficheiros"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "When several file operations (copy or move) are being handled in parallel, Thunar now shows a single progress dialog which displays all the relevant information.\n"
msgstr "Cando varias operacións de ficheiros (copiar ou mover) están sendo manexadas en paralelo, o Thunar agora fornece un diálogo de progreso único que amosa toda a información relevante.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Progress dialog][img-thunar-progress]\n"
msgstr "![Diálogo de progreso][img-thunar-progress]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:23
#, no-wrap
msgid "Eject button for removable devices"
msgstr "Botón de expulsar para dispositivos extraíbeis"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is is now possible to eject removable devices by clicking the eject button near each removable device label in the side pane.\n"
msgstr "Agora é posíbel expulsar dispositivos extraíbeis premendo no botón de expulsión a carón de cada etiqueta de dispositivo extraíbel no panel lateral.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Eject button][img-thunar-eject]\n"
msgstr "![Botón de expulsar][img-thunar-eject]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Xfce panel has been totally rewritten in 4.8, here are the most visible changes.\n"
msgstr "O panel do Xfce foi totalmente reescrito no 4.8, aquí están os cambios máis visíbeis.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Improved positioning and size handling"
msgstr "Mellorouse o posicionamento e manexo do tamaño"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel has much better support for positioning panels on the screen. It can be dragged and snapped to screen borders; floating positions are only remembered when moving a panel and the length of the panel can be adjusted as a percentage of the monitor size.\n"
msgstr "O panel ten unha mellor compatibilidade para o posicionamento dos paneis na pantalla. Pode ser arrastrado e axustado aos límites da pantalla, só se memorizan as posicións flotantes ao mover un panel e a lonxitude do panel pode e a súa dimensión pode ser axustada como unha porcentaxe relativa do tamaño da pantalla.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:37
#, no-wrap
msgid "Transparent backgrounds"
msgstr "Fondos transparentes"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel is now able to draw transparent panel backgrounds with non transparent items. Your panel items will remain readable and you will enjoy a nice panel look.\n"
msgstr "O panel agora pode debuxar fondos de panel transparente con elementos non transparentes. Os elementos do panel permanecerán lexíbeis e gozarán dun bo aspecto de panel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Transparent panel background][img-panel-transparent]\n"
msgstr "![Fondo de panel transparente][img-panel-transparent]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "New item editor"
msgstr "Novo editor de elementos"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel now features an item editor which allows to modify, move, add and remove items quickly. This is particularly useful for items which are hard to right click and gives you an easy way to change your panel layout from a single place.\n"
msgstr "O panel agora presenta un editor de elementos que permite modificar, mover, engadir e eliminar elementos de xeito rápido. Isto é particularmente útil para elementos que son difíciles de facer clic dereito e dálle un xeito doado de mudar o deseño do panel desde un só lugar.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Panel item editor][img-panel-editor]\n"
msgstr "![Editor de elementos do panel][img-panel-editor]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Drag and drop to create launchers"
msgstr "Arrastre e solte para crear iniciadores"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can now drag and drop menu entries from the panel applications menu, application finder or Thunar to the panel to create launchers. This feature should please the huge number of people who had been requesting it for ages. The launcher also has an integrated application finder to add new items.\n"
msgstr "Agora pode arrastrar e soltar elementos desde o menú de aplicacións do panel, do buscador de aplicacións ou do Thunar ao panel para crear iniciadores. Esta característica debería agradar á gran cantidade de persoas que a solicitaron desde fai tempo. O iniciador tamén ten un buscador de aplicacións integrado para engadir novos elementos.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:53
#, no-wrap
msgid "Window buttons plugin"
msgstr "Engadido de botóns de xanela"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "The iconbox and tasklist plugins are new merged into 1 plugin, called window buttons. It implements different sorting modes, improved handling in vertical panels and can draw a similar frame as Xfwm4 Alt+tab when hovering a button.\n"
msgstr "Os engadidos de caixa de iconas e listas de tarefas son combinados nun novo engadido, chamado botóns de xanela. El incorpora diferentes métodos de clasificación, manexo mellorado en paneis verticais e pode debuxar un marco similar ao do Xfwm4 Alt+tab cando se move un botón.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:57
#, no-wrap
msgid "New fuzzy clock"
msgstr "Novo reloxo impreciso"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "An Xfce release without a new clock mode would not be a true Xfce release. Let us introduce you the 'fuzzy' clock mode!\n"
msgstr "Unha versión do Xfce sen un novo modo de reloxo non sería unha verdadeira versión do Xfce. Déixanos presentar o modo de reloxo 'impreciso'!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New fuzzy clock mode][img-panel-fuzzy-clock]\n"
msgstr "![Novo modo de reloxo impreciso][img-panel-fuzzy-clock]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:63
#, no-wrap
msgid "New directory menu plugin"
msgstr "Novo menú de cartafol de engadidos"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "The directory menu plugin provides a menu reproducing the arborescence of a particular folder. This allows you to open a terminal or a file manager in a sub-folder in a very fast and efficient way.\n"
msgstr "O engadido do menú cartafol fornece un menú que reproduce a arborescencia dun cartafol en particular. Isto permítelle abrir un terminal ou un xestor de ficheiros nun subcartafol dunha forma moi rápida e eficiente.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Directory menu plugin][img-panel-directorymenu]\n"
msgstr "![Engadido menú cartafol][img-panel-directorymenu]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:69
#, no-wrap
msgid "Applications menu edition"
msgstr "Modificación do menú de aplicacións"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can now edit the applications menu using any Freedesktop compliant menu editor, Alacarte being the one we used to test.\n"
msgstr "Agora pode modificar o menú de aplicacións empregando calquera editor de menús compatíbel con «Freedesktop», sendo «Alacarte» o que probamos.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:75
#, no-wrap
msgid "Improved multihead setup configuration"
msgstr "Mellorouse a configuración da instalación de múltiples pantallas"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce can now handle and setup multihead setups for any randr 1.2 compatible driver. Unfortunately, this means it will not work with Nvidia proprietary drivers.\n"
msgstr "O Xfce agora pode manipular e configurar as configuracións de múltiples pantallas para calquera controlador compatíbel con randr 1.2. Desafortunadamente, isto significa que non funcionará cos controladores propietarios de Nvidia.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can enable and disable plugged screens, set their resolution, refresh rate, rotation and reflection, clone screens or extend desktops.\n"
msgstr "Pode activar e desactivar as pantallas conectadas, configurar a resolución, a frecuencia de actualización, a rotación e a reflexión, clonar as pantallas ou estender os escritorios.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New display settings dialog][img-display-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Novo diálogo para amosar opcións][img-display-settings]\n"

#. type: Title ####
#: content/about/tour48.md:83
#, no-wrap
msgid "Timed confirmation"
msgstr "Confirmación temporizada"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "Any change made with the settings dialog will have to be confirmed within ten seconds or they will be reverted. This prevents broken video drivers from leaving your computer unusable.\n"
msgstr "Calquera cambio realizado co diálogo de configuración terá que ser confirmado dentro de dez segundos ou será revertido. Isto impide que os controladores de vídeo rotos deixen o seu computador inutilizábel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Timed confirmation for display settings changes][img-display-settings-confirmation]\n"
msgstr "![Confirmación temporizada para os cambios na configuración de pantalla][img-display-settings-confirmation]\n"

#. type: Title ####
#: content/about/tour48.md:89
#, no-wrap
msgid "Quick setup dialog"
msgstr "Diálogo de instalación rápida"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "The quick setup dialog allows you to configure a dual screen setup in a second. Plug the second screen, press the display key or Windows + p and select the wanted layout. Done!\n"
msgstr "O diálogo de configuración rápida permítelle configurar unha instalación de dobre pantalla nun segundo. Conecte a segunda pantalla, prema a tecla de pantalla ou Windows + p e seleccione o deseño desexado. Feito!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Quick multihead setup][img-minimal-display-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Instalación multipantalla rápida][img-minimal-display-settings]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:95
#, no-wrap
msgid "Settings edition in the Xfce Settings Editor"
msgstr "Opcións da modificación no Editor de Opcións do Xfce"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Xfce Settings Editor now deserves its name, it is no longer a simpler Xfconf settings viewer. You can now modify, delete, add and reset settings through its interface. It also monitors changes to update its view.\n"
msgstr "O Editor de configuracións do Xfce agora merece o seu nome, xa non é un sinxelo visor de configuración Xfconf. Agora pode modificar, eliminar, engadir e restabelecer as configuracións a través da súa interface. Tamén monitoriza os cambios para actualizar a súa vista.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Editing Xfconf properties with the Settings Editor][img-settings-editor]\n"
msgstr "![Modificando as propiedade do Xfconf coas Opcións do Editor][img-settings-editor]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour48.md:101
#, no-wrap
msgid "Improved keyboard layout selection"
msgstr "Mellorouse a selección da disposición do teclado"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:104
#, no-wrap
msgid "The layout selection dialog received a lot of love: it no longer displays cryptic language/variants codes but uses localized languages/variants names. Layout edition was also made easier by prefilling the dialogs with the current values.\n"
msgstr "O diálogo de selección da disposición recibiu moito agarimo: xa non amosa códigos críticos de idiomas/variantes senón que emprega nomes de idiomas/variantes localizados. Tamén se facilitou a modificación da disposición co recheo dos diálogos cos valores actuais.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour48.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Layouts and variants list][img-keyboard-settings-list]\n"
msgstr "![Listaxe de disposicións e variantes][img-keyboard-settings-list]\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour46.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.6 tour"
msgstr "Visita ao Xfce 4.6"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "The long awaited 4.6.0 version of the Xfce Desktop Environment is finally available. We will try to highlight some of the new features which have been added since the last stable release.\n"
msgstr "A tan esperada versión 4.6.0 do Contorno de escritorio Xfce está finalmente dispoñíbel. A seguir destácanse algunhas das novas funcións que se engadiron desde o último lanzamento estábel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Since desktop icons have been introduced in Xfce 4.4, people have expressed the need to allow the selection of multiple icons (rubber banding). With **Xfce 4.6**, the **Xfdesktop** manager finally implements this feature: you can select multiple icons, remove them, etcetera...\n"
msgstr "Unha vez que as iconas de escritorio foron introducidas no Xfce 4.4, a xente expresou a necesidade de permitir a selección de múltiples iconas (bandas de goma). Con <b>Xfce 4.6</b>, o xestor de <b>Xfdesktop</b> finalmente admite esta función: polo que xa pode seleccionar varias iconas, eliminalas, etcétera ...\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Multiple icons selection][img-xfdesktop-rubberbanding]\n"
msgstr "![Selección de varias iconas][img-xfdesktop-rubberbanding]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfce 4.6** features a brand new desktop menu which allows you to manipulate files as with the **Thunar** filemanager contextual menu, but also to open applications, exit your session, or access the help documentation.\n"
msgstr "O <b>Xfce 4.6</b> dispón dun novo menú de escritorio que permite manipular tanto ficheiros como o menú contextual do xestor de ficheiros <b>Thunar</b>, máis tamén para abrir aplicacións, saír da súa sesión ou acceder á documentación de axuda.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New desktop menu][img-xfdesktop-menu]\n"
msgstr "![Novo menú de escritorio][img-xfdesktop-menu]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "A lot of long standing bugs have been fixed in **Xfce4 Panel**, particularly for multiple screen setups, but this new release also brings an improved set of panel plugins.\n"
msgstr "Resolvéronse moitos fallos de longa duración no <b>Panel Xfce4</b>, particularmente no relativo a configuracións de pantalla múltiple, máis esta nova versión tamén trae un conxunto mellorado de engadidos de panel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New binary clock][img-xfce4-panel-clock]\n"
msgstr "![Novo reloxo binario][img-xfce4-panel-clock]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **clock plugin** has been rewritten to consume fewer system resources and to fix some display bugs, but there is also a new clock mode for the geek in you: binary clock! The new **notification area plugin** allows you to hide selected notification icons to keep your notification area clean and readable.\n"
msgstr "O <b>engadido de reloxo</b> foi reescrito para consumir menos recursos do sistema e para corrixir algúns fallos de visualización, máis tamén hai un novo modo de reloxo, o reloxo binario! O novo <b>engadido de zona de notificación</b> permítelle agochar as iconas de notificación seleccionadas para que a área de notificación sexa limpa e lexíbel.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour46.md:27
#, no-wrap
msgid "Sound Mixer *(xfce4-mixer)*"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfce4 Mixer** has been rewritten from scratch to use [Gstreamer](https://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/). This allows us to more easily support multiple sound systems, the user interface is more polished, and you can manage several different sound cards. Additionally, a panel plugin allows you to set the system sound quickly using the mouse scroll wheel.\n"
msgstr "O <b>Xfce4 Mixer</b> foi reescrito de cero para usar [Gstreamer](https://gstreamer.freedesktop.org/). Isto permítenos admitir máis doadamente varios sistemas de son, a interface de usuario está máis pulida e pode xestionar varias tarxetas de son. Adicionalmente, un engadido de panel permítelle configurar o son do sistema rapidamente empregando a roda do rato.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New sound mixer][img-xfce4-mixer]\n"
msgstr "![Novo mesturador de son][img-xfce4-mixer]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfce 4.6** comes with an enhanced session manager: your session should be started faster, and the settings dialog has been reworked to ease the management of session-aware applications. Additionally, the session manager will now automatically restart session applications which crashed so that you are not left without a desktop, panel, window manager, etcetera, if a crash occurs.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Session settings dialog][img-xfce4-session-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Diálogo de configuración das sesións][img-xfce4-session-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "The session manager also includes a new long-awaited feature: support for **suspend** and **hibernate** \"out of the box.\" The logout dialog now has two additional buttons which offer to suspend or hibernate your computer.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:42
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Session logout dialog][img-xfce4-session-logout]\n"
msgstr "![Diálogo de saída da sesión][img-xfce4-session-logout]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "As usual, **Xfwm4** has matured quite a bit during this release cycle: many bugs have been fixed, support for multiple displays has been added, and overall performance has been improved.\n"
msgstr "Como é habitual, <b>Xfwm4</b> madurou un pouco durante este ciclo de publicación: corrixíronse moitos fallos, engadiuse compatibilidade para múltiples pantallas e mellorou o rendemento global.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "In addition to some other new features, **Xfwm4** is now able to detect windows that do not respond and offer to terminate them.\n"
msgstr "Ademais dalgunhas outras características novas, <b>Xfwm4</b> agora é capaz de detectar as xanelas que non responden e ofrecen terminalas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:50
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Dialog to terminate busy applications][img-xfwm4-net-ping]\n"
msgstr "![Diálogo para terminar as aplicacións ocupadas][img-xfwm4-net-ping]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is also a new **actions menu** which allows you to quickly move and resize windows, put them above or below other windows, or fullscreen them.\n"
msgstr "Tamén hai un novo <b>menú de accións</b> que permite mover e redimensionar as xanelas rapidamente, poñelas por riba ou por baixo de outras xanelas ou a pantalla completa.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:54
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New actions menu][img-xfwm4-new-menu]\n"
msgstr "![Novo menú de accións][img-xfwm4-new-menu]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new **fill** operation has been implemented; it expands a given window to the available space without overlapping other adjacent windows.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse unha nova operación de <b>enchido</b>; expande unha xanela dada ao espazo dispoñíbel sen solapalo noutras xanelas adxacentes.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:58
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Fill operation][img-xfwm4-fill-operation]\n"
msgstr "![Operación de encher][img-xfwm4-fill-operation]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **compositor** has been optimized to reduce window flickering during resize operations.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Flicker free resizing][img-xfwm4-resize]\n"
msgstr "![Redimensionamento sen escintileo][img-xfwm4-resize]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:64
#, no-wrap
msgid "Some **tweakable options** have also been added: for example, you can now disable the blinking of windows when they receive an urgency hint.\n"
msgstr "Tamén se engadiron algunhas <b>opcións de axuste</b>: por exemplo, agora pode desactivar o escintileo de xanelas cando reciben unha suxestión de urxencia.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New tweakable options][img-xfwm4-new-tweaks]\n"
msgstr "![Novas opcións de axuste][img-xfwm4-new-tweaks]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:70
#, no-wrap
msgid "There have been many bug fixes and performance improvements in **Thunar**. It can use the mouse forward and backward buttons (if available) to navigate, and it includes a new plugin that allows you to set an image as wallpaper from the context menu.\n"
msgstr "Houbo moitas correccións de fallos e melloras de rendemento en <b>Thunar</b>. Pode usar os botóns de avanzar e retroceder do rato (se están dispoñíbeis) para navegar e inclúe un engadido novo que lle permite configurar unha imaxe como fondo de escritorio desde o menú contextual.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Set an image in a Thunar folder as wallpaper][img-thunar-wallpaper-plugin]\n"
msgstr "![Define unha imaxe nun cartafol de Thunar como fondo de escritorio][img-thunar-wallpaper-plugin]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Thunar** now follows the [XDG user directories](https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/xdg-user-dirs) specification; this allows you to have themed and localized user folders to store your music, documents, videos, templates, etcetera...\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar menu for user directories][img-thunar-xdg-user-dirs]\n"
msgstr "![Menú de Thunar para directorios de usuario][img-thunar-xdg-user-dirs]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Thunar** will now display a translucent icon for drives or volumes that are not mounted, so that you can distinguish them from the mounted ones.\n"
msgstr "O <b>Thunar</b> agora amosará unha icona translúcida para unidades ou volumes que non estean montadas, para que poida distinguilos das montadas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Translucent icons for unmounted drives and volumes][img-thunar-mounting]\n"
msgstr "![Iconas translúcidas para as unidades e volumes non montados][img-thunar-mounting]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "Last, but not least, **Thunar** now supports encrypted devices!\n"
msgstr "O último, mais non o menos importante, é que agora o <b>Thunar</b> admite dispositivos cifrados!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:84
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar support for encrypted devices][img-thunar-encrypted]\n"
msgstr "![Compatibilidade do Thunar cos dispositivos cifrados][img-thunar-encrypted]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:88
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.6 features a new settings interface, **Xfce Settings Manager**, which allows you to configure your desktop environment much more easily than before. The dialogs which are accessible by single clicking on the icons have been designed to be more compact and to allow you to customize your desktop quickly and in a more intuitive way.\n"
msgstr "O Xfce 4.6 dispón dunha nova interface de configuración, <b>Xestor de configuración Xfce</b>, que permite configurar o seu contorno de escritorio con moita máis facilidade que antes. Os diálogos que son accesíbeis premendo só nas iconas foron deseñadas para ser máis compactas e para que poida personalizar o seu escritorio de xeito máis rápido e intuitivo.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:90
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfce4 Settings Manager][img-xfce4-settings-manager]\n"
msgstr "![Xestor de configuración de Xfce4][img-xfce4-settings-manager]\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour46.md:91
#, no-wrap
msgid "Accessibility settings"
msgstr "Configuración da accesibilidade"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Accessibility settings dialog][img-xfce4-accessibility-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Diálogo de configuración da accesibilidade][img-xfce4-accessibility-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:96
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Accessibility settings** dialog allows you to set the accessibility related mouse and keyboard options, such as sticky keys, bounce keys, or mouse emulation.\n"
msgstr "O diálogo de <b>configuración de accesibilidade</b> permítelle configurar as opcións de rato e teclado relacionadas coa accesibilidade, como teclas pegañentas, rexeitamento de teclas ou emulación de rato.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour46.md:97
#, no-wrap
msgid "Appearance settings"
msgstr "Configuración da aparencia"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Appearance settings dialog][img-xfce4-appearance-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Diálogo de configuración da aparencia][img-xfce4-appearance-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Appearance settings** dialog allows you to set the widget style, the icon theme, and font, toolbar and menu options.\n"
msgstr "O diálogo de <b>configuración de aparencia</b> permítelle configurar o estilo do trebello, o tema da icona e a letra, as barras de ferramentas e as opcións do menú.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour46.md:103
#, no-wrap
msgid "Display settings"
msgstr "Opcións de pantalla"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Display settings dialog][img-xfce4-display-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Diálogo das opcións de pantalla][img-xfce4-display-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:108
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Display settings** dialog allows you to set the resolution, refresh rate, and the rotation for each screen that is connected.\n"
msgstr "O diálogo das <b>opcións de pantalla</b> permítelle estabelecer a resolución, frecuencia de actualización e a rotación para cada pantalla conectada.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour46.md:109
#, no-wrap
msgid "Keyboard settings"
msgstr "Configuración do teclado"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:112
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Keyboard settings dialog, layout tab][img-xfce4-keyboard-settings-layout]\n"
msgstr "![Diálogo de configuración do teclado, lapela de disposición][img-xfce4-keyboard-settings-layout]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:114
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Keyboard settings** dialog allows you to set keyboard preferences such as key repeating, keyboard shortcuts, and your keyboard layout.\n"
msgstr "O diálogo de <b>Opcións do teclado</b> permítelle configurar preferencias de teclado, como a repetición de teclas, atallos de teclado e a disposición do teclado.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:116
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Keyboard settings dialog, shortcuts tab][img-xfce4-keyboard-settings-shortcuts]\n"
msgstr "![Diálogo de configuración do teclado, lapela de atallos][img-xfce4-keyboard-settings-shortcuts]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:118
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can now configure shortcuts more simply, and any shortcut conflicts are automatically detected.\n"
msgstr "Agora pode configurar os atallos de xeito máis doado, calquera conflito entre atallos é automaticamente detectado.\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour46.md:119
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mouse settings"
msgstr "Configuración do rato"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:122
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Mouse settings dialog][img-xfce4-mouse-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Diálogo de configuración do rato][img-xfce4-mouse-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:124
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Mouse settings** dialog allows you to configure the different mice connected to your computer: button order, acceleration, double-click speed, mouse cursor theme, etcetera...\n"
msgstr "O diálogo das <b>Opcións de rato</b> permítelle configurar os distintos ratos conectados ao computador: orde dos botóns, aceleración, velocidade de dobre clic, tema de cursor do rato, etcétera...\n"

#. type: Title ###
#: content/about/tour46.md:125
#, no-wrap
msgid "Desktop settings"
msgstr "Configuración do escritorio"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:128
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Desktop settings dialog][img-xfdesktop-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Diálogo de configuración do escritorio][img-xfdesktop-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:130
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Desktop settings** dialog is now much more compact; it allows you to configure per-screen settings: wallpaper, brightness, desktop menu, displayed icons, etcetera...\n"
msgstr "O diálogo de <b>Opcións de escritorio</b> agora é moito máis compacto; permite configurar os axustes por pantalla: fondo de pantalla, brillo, menú de escritorio, iconas amosadas, etcétera...\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:134
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfce 4.6** also comes with a brand new application finder which features a cleaner user interface. It is also easier to use it with the keyboard, and it monitors installed applications to update the list \"on the fly.\" It also allows you to create panel launchers quickly by dragging an application icon to the launcher creation window.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour46.md:136
#, no-wrap
msgid "![New application finder][img-xfce4-appfinder]\n"
msgstr "![Novo buscador de aplicacións][img-xfce4-appfinder]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour46.md:137 content/about/tour44.md:139
#, no-wrap
msgid "Links"
msgstr "Ligazóns"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour46.md:141 content/about/tour44.md:143
#, no-wrap
msgid "[Xfce website](https://xfce.org/)\n"
msgstr "[Sitio web de Xfce](https://xfce.org/)\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour46.md:141
#, no-wrap
msgid "[Thunar website](https://xfce.org/projects/thunar)\n"
msgstr "[Sitio web de Thunar](https://xfce.org/projects/thunar)\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour46.md:142 content/about/tour44.md:144
#, no-wrap
msgid "Credits"
msgstr "Créditos"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour46.md:146
#, no-wrap
msgid "Written by Jérôme Guelfucci (February 2009)\n"
msgstr "Escrito por Jérôme Guelfucci (febreiro de 2009)\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour46.md:146
#, no-wrap
msgid "Screenshots by Jannis Pohlmann\n"
msgstr "Capturas de pantalla de Jannis Pohlmann\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/tour44.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.4 tour"
msgstr "Visita ao Xfce 4.4"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "As of today, the long awaited version 4.4.0 of the Xfce Desktop Environment is finally available. I will try to highlight some of the new features which have been added since the last stable release.\n"
msgstr "A partir de hoxe, a tan esperada versión 4.4.0 do Contorno de escritorio Xfce está finalmente dispoñíbel. A seguir destacan algunhas das novas funcións que se engadiron desde a última versión estábel.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "Desktop Icons"
msgstr "Iconas do escritorio"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "One of the most often requested features during the 4.0 and 4.2 was support for icons on the desktop. Now, with Xfce 4.4.0, this feature was finally added to the desktop manager **Xfdesktop**.\n"
msgstr "Unha das características máis solicitadas durante o 4.0 e 4.2 foi que se permitisen utilizar iconas no escritorio. Agora, co Xfce 4.4.0, esta función foi finalmente engadida ao xestor de escritorio <b>xfdesktop</b>.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Desktop Icons][img-desktop-icons]\n"
msgstr "![Iconas do escritorio][img-desktop-icons]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "The desktop manager utilizes **Thunar**'s libraries to handle application launchers and regular files/folders on the desktop. The desktop manager is also able to display icons for minimized windows on the desktop, which is quite a popular feature from the CDE world. Of course, you can disable the desktop icons altogether if you prefer a clean desktop.\n"
msgstr "O xestor de escritorio utiliza as bibliotecas de <b>Thunar</b> para xestionar os iniciadores de aplicacións e os ficheiros/cartafoles regulares no escritorio. O xestor de escritorio tamén é capaz de amosar iconas para minimizar as xanelas no escritorio, que é unha característica moi popular do mundo CDE. Por suposto, pode desactivar completamente as iconas do escritorio se prefire un escritorio limpo.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Desktop Settings][img-desktop-settings]\n"
msgstr "![Configuración do escritorio][img-desktop-settings]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfdesktop** also continues to provide access to the applications menu, as it did in the previous Xfce releases.\n"
msgstr "O <b>Xfdesktop</b> tamén continúa fornecendo acceso ao menú de aplicacións, como xa o facía nas versións anteriores do Xfce.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "The desktop icon support goes hand in hand with the new file manager [Thunar](http://thunar.xfce.org/) which replaces the previous file manager **Xffm**.\n"
msgstr "A posibilidade de engadir iconas de escritorio vai da man do novo xestor de ficheiros [Thunar](http://thunar.xfce.org/) quen substitúe ao xestor de ficheiros anterior <b>Xffm</b>.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar File Manager][img-thunar]\n"
msgstr "![Xestor de ficheiros Thunar][img-thunar]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Thunar** was written from scratch to provide an easy to use, but still very lightweight file manager for Xfce. Its user interface was designed to look similar to the file chooser which was introduced with GTK+ 2.4, and other file managers such as **Nautilus** and **pcmanfm** already picked up that idea as well.\n"
msgstr "O <b>Thunar</b> escribiuse desde cero para fornecer ao Xfce un xestor de ficheiros fácil de usar ávez que moi lixeiro. A súa interface de usuario foi deseñada para parecerse ao selector de ficheiros que se introduciu con GTK + 2.4 e outros xestores de ficheiros como <b>Nautilus</b> e <b>pcmanfm</b> xa tomaron esa idea.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:30
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Thunar** supports all the file management functionality which users will expect, and also several advanced features. For example, a so-called *Bulk Renamer* is included which allows users to rename multiple files at once using a certain criterion.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Thunar Bulk Rename][img-thunar-bulk-rename]\n"
msgstr "![Renomeador masivo do Thunar][img-thunar-bulk-rename]\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:33
#, no-wrap
msgid "Removable Drives and Media"
msgstr "Discos e recursos retirábeis"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.4.0 provides easy access to data on removable drives and media. Just insert the media into the drive or plug the new drive in to the computer and an icon representing the removable volume will appear on the desktop and in **Thunar**'s side pane.\n"
msgstr "O Xfce 4.4.0 fornece un acceso doado aos datos en unidades e medios extraíbeis. Simplemente insira os medios na unidade ou conecte a nova unidade ao computador e aparecerá unha icona que representa ao volume extraíbel no escritorio e no panel lateral do Thunar.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Removable Volumes][img-removable-volumes]\n"
msgstr "![Volumes retirábeis][img-removable-volumes]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:40
#, no-wrap
msgid "Click on the icon to automatically mount the volume. Right-click the icon to unmount the drive or eject the media from the drive. Note however that this feature requires [HAL](https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Software_2fhal) and is therefore only available for Linux 2.6.x and FreeBSD 6.x and above at the time of this writing (there is limited removable media support for FreeBSD 4.x and 5.x which does not require HAL).\n"
msgstr "Prema na icona para montar automaticamente o volume. Prema co botón dereito sobre a icona para desmontar a unidade ou expulsar o medio da unidade. Nótese, porén, que esta función require [HAL](https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Software_2fhal) e, polo tanto, só está dispoñíbel para Linux 2.6.x e FreeBSD 6.x ou posterior ao momento da escritura deste artigo (hai unha compatibilidade de soportes extraíbeis limitado para FreeBSD 4.x e 5.x que non require HAL).\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "Text Editor"
msgstr "Editor de texto"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:44
#, no-wrap
msgid "The new text editor **MousePad** is included with this release. **MousePad** provides all the basic editor functionality, nothing more, nothing less.\n"
msgstr "O novo editor de texto <b>MousePad</b> inclúese con esta versión. O <b>MousePad</b> fornece toda a funcionalidade dun editor básico, nin máis nin menos.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:46
#, no-wrap
msgid "![MousePad][img-mousepad]\n"
msgstr "![MousePad][img-mousepad]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:48
#, no-wrap
msgid "You can think of **MousePad** as the equivalent to **NotePad** on Windows. It starts up very fast, usually in less than one second, even on older systems.\n"
msgstr "Pode pensar en <b>MousePad</b> como o equivalente a <b>NotePad</b>en Windows. Iníciase moi rápido, xeralmente en menos dun segundo, incluso en sistemas máis antigos.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:52
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfwm4** continues to be the window manager of the hearts.\n"
msgstr "O <b>Xfwm4</b> segue sendo o corazón do xestor de xanelas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:54
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfwm4 ARGB32][img-xfwm4-argb32]\n"
msgstr "![ARGB32 do Xfwm4][img-xfwm4-argb32]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:56
#, no-wrap
msgid "This release features an enhanced compositor, supporting transparent ARGB windows, shadows, window frame transparency and much more.\n"
msgstr "Esta versión presenta un compositor mellorado, que admite xanelas ARGB transparentes, as sombras, transparencia do marco da xanela e moito máis.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:58
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfwm4 Switcher][img-xfwm4-switcher]\n"
msgstr "![Trocador do Xfwm4][img-xfwm4-switcher]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:60
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfwm4** also includes a brand new application switcher, as shown in the screenshot above, which displays all windows from the current workspace with icons and window titles.\n"
msgstr "O <b>Xfwm4</b> tamén inclúe un novo trocador de aplicacións, como se amosa na captura de pantalla anterior, que amosa todas as xanelas desde o espazo de traballo actual con iconas e títulos das xanelas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:62
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfwm4 Themes][img-xfwm4-themes]\n"
msgstr "![Temas de Xfwm4][img-xfwm4-themes]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:64
#, no-wrap
msgid "Further on support for multiple image formats for window decoration themes was added, including `PNG`, `GIF` and `SVG` images.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:66
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfwm4 Tweaks][img-xfwm4-tweaks]\n"
msgstr "![Axustes do XFwm4][img-xfwm4-tweaks]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:68
#, no-wrap
msgid "Advanced controls for the window manager were also added, allowing thorough tweaking of window behavior.\n"
msgstr "Tamén se engadiron controis avanzados para o xestor de xanelas, que permiten axustar completamente o comportamento da xanela.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:72
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **Xfce4-panel** was completely rewritten for the Xfce 4.4 release. Multiple panels are supported *out of the box* now and can easily be configured using the new **Panel Manager** shown in the screenshot below.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:74
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Panel Manager][img-panel-manager]\n"
msgstr "![Xestor de paneis][img-panel-manager]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:76
#, no-wrap
msgid "One of the major problems in previous Xfce releases was that every plugin had to be run in the same process as the panel, and hence every plugin was able to crash the whole panel. To address this issue, support for external plugins was added to the panel.\n"
msgstr "Un dos principais problemas nas versións anteriores do Xfce foi que todos os complementos tiveron que ser executados no mesmo proceso que o panel e, polo tanto, todos os complementos eran quen de quebrar todo o panel. Para solucionar este problema, engadiuse ao panel a posibilidade de execución de engadidos externos.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:78
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Panel Add Item Dialog][img-panel-additem]\n"
msgstr "![Diálogo de engadir elemento ao panel][img-panel-additem]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:80
#, no-wrap
msgid "Developers of panel plugins can now decide whether the plugin should run as external process or as part of the panel process, depending on the stability of the plugin.\n"
msgstr "Os desenvolvedores de engadidos de panel agora poden decidir se o engadido debería executarse como un proceso externo ou como parte do proceso do panel, dependendo da estabilidade do complemento.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:82
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Panel Icon Box Plugin][img-panel-iconbox]\n"
msgstr "![Engadido de caixa de icona do panel][img-panel-iconbox]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:84
#, no-wrap
msgid "Since there is now support for multiple panels, the separate **Xftaskbar4** and **Xfce4-iconbox** utilities are no longer required. Instead, both the taskbar and the iconbox are available as panel plugins now.\n"
msgstr "Xa que agora son compatíbeis múltiples paneis, as utilidades separadas <b>Xftaskbar4</b> e <b>Xfce4-iconbox</b> xa non son necesarias. No seu canto, tanto a barra de tarefas como a caixa de iconas están dispoñíbeis agora como engadidos de panel.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:86
#, no-wrap
msgid "Most of the additional panel plugins, available via the [Xfce Goodies Project](https://goodies.xfce.org/), have been updated for the new panel, and several new plugins were added. For example, the brand new **xfce4-xfapplet-plugin** allows users to add GNOME panel applets to the Xfce panel.\n"
msgstr "A maioría dos engadidos de panel adicionais, dispoñíbeis a través do [Proxecto de Extras do Xfce](https://goodies.xfce.org/), foron actualizados para o novo panel e engadíronse varios engadidos novos. Por exemplo, o novo <b>xfce4-xfapplet-plugin</b> permite aos usuarios engadir miniaplicacións do panel de GNOME ao panel do Xfce.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:87
#, no-wrap
msgid "Time Management"
msgstr "Xestión do tempo"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:90
#, no-wrap
msgid "The new time management application **Orage** replaces the **Xfcalendar**, which was introduced with Xfce 4.2.0. **Orage** provides several features to efficiently manage your time.\n"
msgstr "A nova aplicación de xestión do tempo <b>Orage</b> substitúe ao <b>Xfcalendar</b>, que foi introducido con Xfce 4.2.0. O <b>Orage</b> fornece varias funcións para xestionar de xeito eficiente o seu tempo.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:92
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Orage][img-orage]\n"
msgstr "![Orage][img-orage]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:94
#, no-wrap
msgid "While **Orage** is very lightweight and easy to use, it supports all the important features found in larger calendar applications like **Outlook** or **Evolution**. While **Xfcalendar** used the custom `dbh` format in the past to store your settings, **Orage** is based on `ical` and therefore compatible with other calendar applications.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:95
#, no-wrap
msgid "Terminal Emulator"
msgstr "Emulador do terminal"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:98
#, no-wrap
msgid "While **Terminal** was already available during the 4.2 days, it was not mature enough at that time to be part of the core. With this major release, it was moved into the core desktop.\n"
msgstr "Aínda que <b>Terminal</b> xa estaba dispoñíbel durante a versión 4.2, non era maduro o suficiente como para formar parte do núcleo. Con este gran lanzamento, foi trasladado ao núcleo do escritorio.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:100
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Terminal][img-terminal]\n"
msgstr "![Terminal][img-terminal]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:102
#, no-wrap
msgid "Besides the basic features which you might expect from a terminal emulator, it includes some nice additional features, like multiple tabs per window, customizable toolbars and the ability to configure nearly every aspect of the application via *hidden options*. As can be seen in the screenshot above, this release also supports real transparency using **Xfwm4**'s integrated composition manager.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:103
#, no-wrap
msgid "Printing"
msgstr "Impresión"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:106
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfprint**, the Xfce printing management application, saw several small improvements with this release. First, the `a2ps` converter is not mandatory anymore, whilst still recommended. Support for `CUPS` 1.2 was added and **Xfprint** is now able to display the printer state with the `CUPS`-backend.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:108
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfce Printing][img-xfprint]\n"
msgstr "![Impresión con Xfce][img-xfprint]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:110
#, no-wrap
msgid "**Xfprint** also integrates with **MousePad** to provide generic printing support for different kinds of text documents using the `a2ps` converter.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:112
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfce Print Dialog][img-xfprint-dialog]\n"
msgstr "![Diálogo de impresión de Xfce][img-xfprint-dialog]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:114
#, no-wrap
msgid "As you can see the print dialog still looks relatively similar to that of Xfce 4.2, but the internal workings of the printing support were improved, especially the `CUPS` support. Besides that, the printing management functionality was moved to a library, so other applications can use the API to access the printer configuration.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:115
#, no-wrap
msgid "Autostart"
msgstr "Inicio automático"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:118
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.4.0 implements the new [Autostart Specification](https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Standards_2fautostart_2dspec) - actually Xfce was the first desktop to implement said feature, but the others were faster to release. ;-)\n"
msgstr "O Xfce 4.4.0 leva a cabo a nova [especificación de autoarranque](https://freedesktop.org/wiki/Standards_2fautostart_2dspec) en realidade, o Xfce foi o primeiro escritorio en poñer en funcionamento esta característica, máis os outros foron máis rápidos de en publicar. ;-)\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:120
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Xfce Autostart Editor][img-autostart]\n"
msgstr "![Editor do autoarranque do Xfce][img-autostart]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:122
#, no-wrap
msgid "The specification consists of two parts, the *Autostart of Applications During Startup*, which is implemented in **xfce4-session** and the *Autostart Of Applications After Mount* which is implemented in [thunar-volman](http://foo-projects.org/~benny/projects/thunar-volman/index.html). This release also includes the **xfce4-autostart-editor**, shown in the screenshot above, which allows users to easily add, remove or disable autostarted applications.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:126
#, no-wrap
msgid "This release introduces new options to customize the desktop to your needs. Some examples of new settings dialogs were already shown in the sections above.\n"
msgstr "Esta versión engade novas opcións para personalizar o escritorio ás súas necesidades. Algúns exemplos de diálogos de configuración novos xa se amosaron nas seccións anteriores.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:128
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Preferred Applications][img-preferences-applications]\n"
msgstr "![Aplicacións preferidas][img-preferences-applications]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:130
#, no-wrap
msgid "The preferred applications framework, which was previously only available in **Terminal**, was imported into Xfce, so users no longer need to edit shell profiles to specify which browser and terminal emulator should be used by Xfce applications. The goal was to make it as easy as possible to change an application for a certain category (GNOME users may have already noticed that GNOME adopted this approach, because it is such simple).\n"
msgstr "O marco de traballo de aplicacións preferidas, que previamente só estaba dispoñíbel en <b>Terminal</b>, foi importado ao Xfce, polo que os usuarios xa non precisan modificar os perfís do intérprete de ordes para especificar que navegador e emulador de terminal debe empregar as aplicacións do Xfce. O obxectivo era facelo o máis sinxelo posíbel para cambiar unha aplicación para unha determinada categoría (os usuarios de GNOME xa notaron que o GNOME adoptou este enfoque porque é moi sinxelo).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:132
#, no-wrap
msgid "![Keyboard Shortcuts][img-preferences-keyboard]\n"
msgstr "![Atallos do teclado][img-preferences-keyboard]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:134
#, no-wrap
msgid "And then there was the problem with the keyboard shortcuts in Xfce 4.2... Xfce 4.2 limited the number of freely available keyboard shortcuts, while people wanted to assign any number of keyboard shortcuts. With Xfce 4.4 this limitation is history and the application shortcuts are now separated from the window manager shortcuts.\n"
msgstr "E logo estaba o problema cos atallos de teclado en Xfce 4.2... quen limitou o número de atallos de teclado dispoñíbeis de xeito gratuíto, mentres que a xente quería asignar calquera número de atallos de teclado. Co Xfce 4.4 esta limitación é historia e os atallos de aplicacións agora están separados dos atallos do xestor de xanelas.\n"

#. type: Title ##
#: content/about/tour44.md:135
#, no-wrap
msgid "Feedback"
msgstr "Comentarios"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:138
#, no-wrap
msgid "Please post comments on this article in my [blog](http://xfce-diary.blogspot.com/2007/01/visual-tour-of-xfce-440.html) and use the [xfce](/community/lists) mailinglist if you have questions about Xfce 4.4.0 or trouble with the installation.\n"
msgstr "Publica comentarios sobre este artigo na miña [bitácora](http://xfce-diary.blogspot.com/2007/01/visual-tour-of-xfce-440.html) e usa a lista de distribución do [xfce](/community/lists) se tes preguntas sobre Xfce 4.4.0 ou problemas coa instalación.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/tour44.md:143
#, no-wrap
msgid "[Thunar website](http://thunar.xfce.org/)\n"
msgstr "[Sitio web de Thunar](http://thunar.xfce.org/)\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/tour44.md:147
#, no-wrap
msgid "Written by Benedikt Meurer, 21 Jan 2007\n"
msgstr "Escrito por Benedikt Meurer, o 21 de xaneiro de 2007\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.20 released"
msgstr "Xfce 4.20 publicada"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "After almost two years of work, we are happy to announce the release of Xfce 4.20 !\n"
msgstr "Despois de case dous anos de traballo, estamos encantados de anunciar a publicación do Xfce 4.20!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Since Xfce 4.18 a lot of major development happened. Our team added many nice new features, did a gazillion of bug fixes and did various minor improvements. Finally, all that was released for your pleasure.\n"
msgstr "Desde Xfce 4.18 houbo moitos desenvolvementos importantes. O noso equipo engadiu varias funcións novas, fixo unha gran cantidade de correccións de erros e fixo varias melloras menores. Finalmente, todo isto foi liberado para o seu pracer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "<img src=\"//cdn.xfce.org/about/screenshots/4.20-1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Xfce 4.20 screenshot\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"/>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "The major focus during this development cycle was the preparation of the codebase to be ready for Wayland. So that we meanwhile have experimental Wayland support for most components. More details in the links below.\n"
msgstr "O principal foco durante este ciclo de desenvolvemento foi a preparación da base de código para estar lista para Wayland. De xeito que, mentres tanto, temos compatibilidade experimental de Wayland para a maioría dos compoñentes. Máis detalles nas ligazóns a continuación.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Assuming you have installed Xfce 4.18, here is an overview on the major changes you will see on an upgrade to Xfce 4.20:\n"
msgstr "Supoñendo que instalou Xfce 4.18, aquí ten unha visión xeral dos principais cambios que verá nunha anovación ao Xfce 4.20:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "A detailed overview of the changes between Xfce 4.18 and Xfce 4.20 releases can be found on the following page:\n"
msgstr "Na seguinte páxina pode atopar unha visión detallada dos cambios comparando a versión do Xfce 4.18 coa versión do Xfce 4.20:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:26 content/about/news/1671062400.md:26
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:45 content/about/news/1565568000.md:57
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:59 content/about/news/1335571200.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "This release can be downloaded either as a set of individual packages or as a single fat tarball including all these individual versions:\n"
msgstr "Esta versión pode descargarse como un conxunto de paquetes individuais ou como un único e grande ficheiro comprimido que inclúe todas estas versións individuais:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1734220800.md:29 content/about/news/1671062400.md:29
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:48 content/about/news/1565568000.md:60
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:66 content/about/news/1335571200.md:33
#: content/about/news/1295136000.md:39
#, no-wrap
msgid "Best regards,<br />The Xfce development team\n"
msgstr "Saúdos.<br />O equipo de desenvolvemento de Xfce.\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.18 released"
msgstr "Xfce 4.18 liberado"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "After almost two years of work, we are happy to announce the release of Xfce 4.18 !\n"
msgstr "Despois de case dous anos de traballo, temos o pracer de anunciar a publicación do Xfce 4.18.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Since Xfce 4.16 a lot of major development happened. Our team added multiple nice new features, did a gazillion of bug fixes and did various minor improvements. Finally, all that is going to be released for your pleasure.\n"
msgstr "Desde Xfce 4.16 houbo moitos desenvolvementos importantes. O noso equipo engadiu varias funcións novas, fixo unha gran cantidade de correccións de erros e fixo varias melloras menores. Finalmente, todo isto vai ser liberado para o seu pracer.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "<img src=\"//cdn.xfce.org/about/screenshots/4.18-1.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Xfce 4.18 screenshot\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"/>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "This development cycle was influenced a lot by [GSoC 2021](https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/archive/2021/organizations/5706869816950784) and [GSoC 2022](https://summerofcode.withgoogle.com/programs/2022/organizations/xfce), which led to various new features, most of them for Thunar, the Xfce File Manager. Though as well multiple other Xfce components got a lot of love and many improvements were done under the hood.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Assuming you have installed Xfce 4.16, here is an overview on the major changes you will see on an upgrade to Xfce 4.18:\n"
msgstr "Supoñendo que instalou Xfce 4.16, aquí ten unha visión xeral dos principais cambios que verá nunha anovación a Xfce 4.18:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1671062400.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "A detailed overview of the changes between Xfce 4.16 and Xfce 4.18 releases can be found on the following page:\n"
msgstr "Na seguinte páxina pode atopar unha visión detallada dos cambios comparando a versión do Xfce 4.16 coa versión do Xfce 4.18:\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.16 released"
msgstr "Xfce 4.16 publicada"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "Today, after 1 year and 4 months of work, we are happy to announce the release of the Xfce desktop 4.16, a new stable version that supersedes Xfce 4.14.\n"
msgstr "Hoxe, despois de 1 ano e 4 meses de traballo, temos o pracer de anunciar a versión de escritorio do Xfce 4.16, unha nova versión estábel que substitúe ao Xfce 4.14.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "4.16 was a special cycle in many respects (not only pandemic-wise, but also). One of the corner-stones of the non-code changes concerns our migration to GitLab, which is a change in development workflow and a huge step forward in terms of becoming more contributor-friendly and welcoming. In parts, the [humungous changelog of Xfce 4.16](https://www.xfce.org/download/changelogs/4.16) can be attributed to new contributors proposing merge requests (288 merge requests were merged or closed against our core components alone!). We also created a reference Docker container ([xfce/xfce-build](https://hub.docker.com/r/xfce/xfce-build)) and added CI pipelines to all components to ensure we don´t break the build. None of this would have been possible without our hosting being sponsored by [Gandi](https://gandi.net) and [Fosshost](https://fosshost.org)!\n"
msgstr "4.16 foi un ciclo especial en moitos aspectos (non só pandémico, máis tamén). Unha das pedras angulares dos cambios non relacionados co código foi á nosa migración a GitLab, que supón un cambio no fluxo de traballo de desenvolvemento e un enorme paso adiante en canto a ser máis amigábeis e receptivos cos contribuidores. En partes, o [enorme rexistro de cambios de Xfce 4.16](https://www.xfce.org/download/changelogs/4.16) pode ser atribuído a novos colaboradores que propoñen solicitudes de combinación (288 solicitudes de combinación foron combinadas ou pechadas só nos compoñentes fundamentais!). Tamén creamos un contedor Docker de referencia ([xfce / xfce-build](https://hub.docker.com/r/xfce/xfce-build)) e engadimos canalizacións CI a todos os compoñentes para garantir que non rompemos a compilación. Nada disto non sería posíbel sen que [Gandi](https://gandi.net) e [Fosshost](https://fosshost.org) patrocinasen o noso aloxamento.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Another big change concerns our visual identity, which we updated from a strange mix of random (partly Tango-based) icons and not following any naming scheme to a new, visually consistent set (following the freedesktop.org naming specification and a fixed color palette). We´re aware this will generate some work for icon theme maintainers (if they really want to override our gorgeous icons ;)) but we believe the longterm benefit outweighs this one-time effort.\n"
msgstr "Outra gran mudanza refírese á nosa identidade visual, que actualizamos dunha estraña mestura de iconas aleatorias (en parte baseadas en Tango) e que non seguen ningún esquema de nomeamento a un novo conxunto visualmente consistente (seguindo a especificación de nomes freedesktop.org e unha paleta de cores fixa ). Somos conscientes de que isto xerará algo de traballo para os mantedores de temas de iconas (se realmente queren anular as nosas fermosas iconas;)) pero cremos que o beneficio a longo prazo supera este esforzo puntual.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "<img src=\"//cdn.xfce.org/about/tour/4.16/upstream-icons.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"upstream-icons\" style=\"max-width: 100%;\"/>\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "And then finally we did some housekeeping (e.g. by dropping Gtk2 support code) and we also added features and improvements - all while sticking to a reasonable release cycle timeframe.\n"
msgstr "E finalmente fixemos algunhas tarefas de limpeza (por exemplo, eliminando o código de compatíbel con Gtk2) e tamén engadimos funcións e melloras, todo isto manténdonos nun prazo de ciclo de publicación razoable.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "So without further ado, here go the **main highlights of this release**:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [window manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfwm4/start) received lots of updates and improvements again in the area of compositing and GLX. If a primary display was set, the alt-tab dialog will now only be shown there. Furthermore some handy new options to zoom the cursor along with rest of the display as well as an option to keep minimized windows in the most recently used list complement this release.\n"
msgstr "O [xestor de xanelas](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfwm4/start) recibiu moreas de actualizacións e melloras de novo na área de composición e GLX. Se se configurou unha pantalla principal, o cadro de diálogo Alt-Tab só se amosará alí. Ademais, algunhas novas e útiles opcións para ampliar o cursor xunto co resto da pantalla, así como unha opción para manter as xanelas minimizadas na lista usada máis recentemente complementan esta versión.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "We added a new plugin to the [panel](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-panel/start) dubbed “statustray” which combines both StatusNotifier and legacy Systray items. An animated autohide transition now clearly shows the user “where the panel has gone” and a dark mode (enabled by default) makes the panel drop into the background a bit more with bright themes like the Gtk default Adwaita. Quite a few more smaller improvements were also introduced like accessing desktop actions from a Launcher´s right-click menu, the Window Buttons plugin now offering to `Launch a new instance` of an application and the Workspace Switcher now optionally showing automatic numbering for workspaces.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support for fractional scaling was added to the [display dialog](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/display), along with highlighting the preferred mode of a display with an asterisk and adding aspect ratios next to resolutions. Falling back to a working mode after misconfiguring the display layout has also been made more robust.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse compatibilidade para a escala fraccionada á [xanela da pantalla](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/display), xunto co realzado do modo preferido dunha pantalla cun asterisco e o engadido das relacións de aspecto a carón das resolucións. Volver ao modo de traballo anterior despois dunha mala configuración no deseño da pantalla tamén se fixo máis robusto.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new tab in the “About Xfce” dialog shows basic system information like CPU or GPU type. Furthermore the layout and visuals of the dialog were improved.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [settings manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/start) has improved search and filter capabilities. Furthermore all settings dialogs now use window decorations drawn by Gtk (client side decorations).\n"
msgstr "O [xestor de configuración](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/start) mellorou as capacidades de busca e filtrado. Ademais, todos as xanelas de configuración agora usan decoracións de xanelas debuxadas por Gtk (decoracións do lado do cliente).\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The “Mime Settings” and “Preferred Applications” dialogs were merged into the “Default Applications” dialog - making it easier for users to set which application handles which filetype or action from one place.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Our file manager [Thunar](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/start) received a boatload of fixes and quite a few notable features, including pause for copy/move operations, support for queued file transfer, remembering view settings per directory and support for transparency in Gtk themes.\n"
msgstr "O noso xestor de ficheiros [Thunar](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/start) recibiu unha chea de correccións e bastantes funcións salientábeis, incluíndo unha pausa para operacións de copiar/mover, capacidade para a transferencia de ficheiros en cola, lembrar a configuración de visualización por cartafol e compatibilidade para a transparencia nos temas Gtk.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Our [thumbnailing service tumbler](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/tumbler) became more flexible by being able to exclude paths. Furthermore support for .epub (e-book format) was added.\n"
msgstr "O noso [servizo de miniaturas tumbler](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/tumbler) volveuse máis flexíbel ao poder excluír as rutas. Ademais engadiu compatibilidade co formato .epub (formato de libro electrónico).\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [session manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-session/start) offers improved support for GPG agent 2.1 and the setting dialog was visually improved.\n"
msgstr "O [xestor de sesións](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-session/start) fornece compatibilidade mellorada para o axente GPG 2.1 e a xanela de configuración mellorouse visualmente.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [power manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-power-manager/start) received a lot of bugfixes and some smaller features - among them a cleanup of its settings dialog, an optional visual indicator for when `Presentation Mode` is enabled, more accurate battery status icons and automatically dismissing low-power notifications upon the connection of a charger.\n"
msgstr "O [xestor de enerxía](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-power-manager/start) recibiu moitas correccións de erros e algunhas funcións máis pequenas, entre elas unha limpeza da súa xanela de configuración, un indicador visual opcional para cando está activado o «Modo de presentación», iconas de estado da batería máis precisas e o descartado automático das notificacións de baixo consumo cando está conectado a un cargador.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [desktop](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfdesktop/start) mostly received bugfixes and small improvements - and the new default wallpaper!\n"
msgstr "O [escritorio](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfdesktop/start) recibiu principalmente correccións de erros, pequenas melloras e o novo fondo de pantalla predeterminado.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Our menu library [garcon](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/garcon/start) received new APIs and now doesn´t launch applications as children of the process hosting the menu anymore. The previous behavior led to applications crashing along with e.g. the panel.\n"
msgstr "A nosa biblioteca de menús [garcon](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/garcon/start) recibiu novas APIs e agora xa non inicia aplicacións como fillos do proceso que aloxa o menú. O comportamento anterior provocou o fallo das aplicacións xunto con, por exemplo, o panel.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [applicaton finder](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-appfinder/start) now allows for sorting applications by “frecency” - a combination of frequency and recency.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:35
#, no-wrap
msgid "Dependency updates: Drop Gtk2, add LibGTop, bump Gtk &gt;= 3.22, GLib and GDBus &gt;= 2.50\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:37
#, no-wrap
msgid "An online tour of the changes in Xfce 4.16 can be viewed here:\n"
msgstr "Pode facer unha visita para ver os cambios do Xfce 4.16 aquí:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1608595200.md:41
#, no-wrap
msgid "A detailed overview of the changes between Xfce 4.14 and Xfce 4.16 releases can be found on the following page:\n"
msgstr "Na seguinte páxina pode atopar unha visión detallada dos cambios comparando a versión do Xfce 4.14 coa versión do Xfce 4.16:\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.14 released"
msgstr "Xfce 4.14 publicada"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "Today, after 4 years and 5 months of work, we are pleased to announce the release of the Xfce desktop 4.14, a new stable version that supersedes Xfce 4.12.\n"
msgstr "Hoxe, despois de 4 anos e 5 meses de traballo, temos o pracer de anunciar a versión de escritorio do Xfce 4.14, unha nova versión estábel que substitúe o Xfce 4.12.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "In this 4.14 cycle the main goal was to port all core components to Gtk3 (over Gtk2) and GDBus (over D-Bus GLib). Most components also received GObject Introspection support. Along the way we ended up polishing our user experience, introducing quite a few new features and improvements (read below) and fixings a boatload of bugs (read changelog).\n"
msgstr "Neste ciclo 4.14 o obxectivo principal era transportar todos os compoñentes principais a Gtk3 (desde Gtk2) e GDBus (desde D-Bus GLib). A maioría dos compoñentes tamén recibiron compatibilidade con GObject Introspection. Ao longo do camiño acabamos pulindo a nosa experiencia de usuario, introducindo bastantes funcións e melloras novas (lea máis abaixo) e arranxando unha chea de erros (lea o rexistro de cambios).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "The **main highlights of this release** are:\n"
msgstr "Os aspectos máis salientábeis desta versión son:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [window manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfwm4/start) received a slew of updates and features, including support for VSync (using either Present or OpenGL as backend) to reduce or remove display flickering, HiDPI support, improved GLX support with NVIDIA proprietary/closed source drivers, support for XInput2, various compositor improvements and a new default theme.\n"
msgstr "O [xestor de xanelas](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfwm4/start) recibiu unha serie de actualizacións e funcións, incluído a compatibilidade con VSync (usando Present ou OpenGL como infraestrutura) para reducir ou eliminar o escintileo da pantalla, compatibilidade HiDPI, compatibilidade GLX mellorado con controladores de código propietario/pechado NVIDIA, compatibilidade con XInput2, varias melloras do compositor e un novo tema predeterminado.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [panel](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-panel/start) got support for RandR's primary monitor feature, improved window grouping in the tasklist plugin (better UX, visual group indicator etc), a per-panel \"icon-size\" setting, a new default clock format and clock format evaluator as well as an improved default panel layout.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [desktop](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfdesktop/start) now has support for RandR's primary monitor feature, an orientation option for icon arrangement, a \"Next Background\" context menu option to advance the wallpaper and it now syncs the user's wallpaper selection to AccountsService.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "A completely new settings dialog to [manage color profiles](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/color) has been created. For most users this means out of the box support for color-managed printing (through cupsd) and scanning (through saned). For monitor profiles you will have to install an additional service like xiccd.\n"
msgstr "Creouse unha xanela de configuración completamente novo para [xestionar os perfís de cor](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/color). Para a maioría dos usuarios, isto significa compatibilidade directa coa impresión xestionada en cor (a través de cupsd) e a dixitalización (a través de saned). Para os perfís de pantalla terá que instalar un servizo adicional como xiccd.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [display dialog](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/display) received a lot of attention during this cycle and a big feature: Users are now able to save and (automatically) restore complete multi-display configurations, which is especially helpful for those who frequently connect their laptop to varying docking stations or setups. Furthermore a lot of time was spent on making the user interface more intuitive and a hidden option was added to support RandR display scaling (configured via Xfconf).\n"
msgstr "A [xanela de visualización](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/display) recibiu moita atención durante este ciclo e unha gran característica: os usuarios agora poden gardar e (automaticamente) restaurar configuracións completas de pantalla, o que resulta especialmente útil para aqueles que conectan o seu portátil con frecuencia a diferentes estacións de acoplamento ou configuracións. Ademais, empregouse moito tempo a facer a interface de usuario máis intuitiva e engadiuse unha opción agochada para admitir a escala de visualización RandR (configurada a través de Xfconf).\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "We added an option to enable Gtk window scaling to the [appearance dialog](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/appearance) and a monospace font option as well. However we had to drop theme previews as they didn't produce consistent results with Gtk3.\n"
msgstr "Engadimos unha opción para activar a escala de xanelas Gtk na [xanela de aparencia](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-settings/appearance) e tamén nunha opción de fonte monoespazo. Non obstante, tivemos que retirar as vistas previas de temas xa que non produciron resultados consistentes con Gtk3.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "While we decided to drop splash screens from the [session manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-session/start), we added lots of features and fixes instead. Among them are hybrid sleep support, improvements to the default session startup avoiding race conditions, a feature to add and edit autostart entries, a switch user button in the logout dialog and improved session chooser and settings dialogs (the latter with a new tab that shows saved sessions). Furthermore you can now run commands not only \"autostart style\" at login time, but also when your computer suspends, logs out etc. Finally Gtk applications are now session-managed over DBus and screensavers are also communicated with (e.g. inhibited) over DBus.\n"
msgstr "Mentres decidimos eliminar as pantallas de presentación do [xestor de sesión](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-session/start), no seu lugar engadimos moitas funcións e correccións. Entre elas están a compatibilidade de suspensión híbrida, melloras no inicio de sesión predeterminado evitando as condicións de competición, unha funcionalidade para engadir e modificar entradas de inicio automático, un botón de cambio de usuario na xanela de saída da sesión e un mellor selector de sesións e xanelas de configuración (este último cunha nova lapela que amosa sesións gardadas). Amais, agora pode executar ordes non só «estilo de inicio automático» no momento do inicio de sesión, senón tamén cando o computador se suspende, desconecta, etc. Finalmente, as aplicacións Gtk agora están xestionadas por sesión por medio de DBus e os protectores de pantalla tamén se comunican  (por exemplo, inhibición) a través de DBus.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "As always, [Thunar](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/start) - our file manager - received a lot of features and fixes. Among the visible changes are the completely reworked pathbar, support for larger thumbnails as well as support for a \"folder.jpg\" file altering the folder's icon (e.g. for music album covers). Power users will also notice the improved keyboard navigation (zooming, tab navigation). Thunar's volume manager has gained Bluray support.\n"
msgstr "Como sempre, o [Thunar](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/start), o noso xestor de ficheiros, recibiu moitas funcións e correccións. Entre os cambios visíbeis están a barra de ruta completamente reelaborada, compatibilidade con miniaturas máis grandes, así como a compatibilidade cun ficheiro \"folder.jpg\" que modifica a icona do cartafol (por exemplo, para portadas de álbums de música). Os usuarios avanzados tamén notarán a mellorada navegación por teclado (zoom, navegación por tabulacións). O xestor de volumes do Thunar engadiu compatibilidade con Bluray.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "Our [thumbnailing service tumbler](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/tumbler) received a lot of fixes and support for the Fujifilm RAF format.\n"
msgstr "O noso [servizo de miniaturas tumbler](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/thunar/tumbler) recibiu moitas correccións e engadiu compatibilidade co formato RAF de Fujifilm.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [application finder](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-appfinder/start) can now optionally be opened as a single window and can now be more easily navigated with the keyboard only.\n"
msgstr "O [buscador de aplicacións](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-appfinder/start) agora pode abrirse opcionalmente como unha única xanela e navegar máis doadamente só co teclado.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:26
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [power manager](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-power-manager/start) received a lot of bugfixes and some smaller features, including support for the XF86Battery button and for the newly created xfce4-screensaver. The panel plugin also saw several improvements: it can now optionally show the remaining time and/or percentage and it now relies on UPower's standard icon names to work with more icon themes out of the box. With LXDE moving on to a QT base the LXDE panel plugin was dropped.\n"
msgstr "O [xestor de enerxía](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/xfce4-power-manager/start) recibiu moitas correccións de erros e algunhas funcións máis pequenas, incluído a compatibilidade para o botón XF86Battery e para o recentemente creado xfce4-screensaver. O engadido de panel tamén inclúe varias melloras: agora pode amosar opcionalmente o tempo e/ou a porcentaxe restantes e agora depende dos nomes de iconas estándar de UPower para traballar con máis temas de iconas de fábrica. Con LXDE pasando a unha base QT, eliminouse o engadido de panel LXDE.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "A lot of **applications and plugins** that are part of the Xfce eco-system - often dubbed \"goodies\" - are part of what makes Xfce great. A lot of those have also seen important changes along the timeline of the 4.14 release. To highlight a few:\n"
msgstr "Moitas **aplicacións e engadidos** que forman parte do ecosistema Xfce - a miúdo chamados «extras» - forman parte do que fai que Xfce sexa xenial. Moitos deles tamén viron cambios importantes ao longo da liña de tempo da versión 4.14. Para destacar algúns:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "Our [notification service](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/notifyd/start) has gained support for persistence - in other words: notification logging - and a \"Do Not Disturb\" mode, which suppresses all notifications. A new panel plugin was created that shows missed notifications (especially helpful during \"Do Not Disturb\" mode) and gives quick access to toggling \"Do Not Disturb\" mode. Finally support for showing notifications on RandR's primary monitor was added.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "Our media player [Parole](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/parole/start) received improved support for network streams and podcasts, as well as a new \"mini mode\" and automatic choosing of the best available video backend. Furthermore it also inhibits both screensavers and power managers during video playback now, making sure users don't have to go wiggle their mouse periodically while enjoying a movie.\n"
msgstr "O noso reprodutor multimedia [Parole](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/parole/start) recibiu mellor compatibilidade para fluxos de rede e podcasts, así como un novo «modo mini» e a elección automática da mellor infraestrutura de vídeo dispoñíbel. Admais, tamén inhibe o protector de pantalla e os xestor de enerxía durante a reprodución de vídeo agora, asegurándose de que os usuarios non teñan que mover o rato periodicamente mentres gozan dun filme.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "Our image viewer [Ristretto](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/ristretto/start) has seen various user interface improvements and support for setting the desktop wallpaper. It has recently also seen its first Gtk3-based development release.\n"
msgstr "O noso visor de imaxes [Ristretto](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/ristretto/start) viu varias melloras na interface de usuario e compatibilidade para configurar o fondo de escritorio. Recentemente tamén viu a súa primeira versión de desenvolvemento baseada en Gtk3.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [screenshooter](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/screenshooter/start) now allows users to move the selection rectangle and at the same time displays its width and height. The imgur upload dialog was revamped and the command line allows for more flexibility.\n"
msgstr "A [captura de pantalla](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/screenshooter/start) agora permite aos usuarios mover o rectángulo de selección e ao mesmo tempo amosar a súa largura e altura. A xanela de carga de imgur renovouse e a liña de ordes permite máis flexibilidade.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "Our [clipboard manager](https://docs.xfce.org/panel-plugins/clipman/start) now has improved keyboard shortcut support (through a port to GtkApplication), improved and more consistent icon sizing as well as a new application icon.\n"
msgstr "O noso [xestor do portapapeis](https://docs.xfce.org/panel-plugins/clipman/start) agora mellorou a compatibilidade cos atallos de teclado (a través dun porto para GtkApplication), co tamaño da icona mellorado e máis consistente e cunha nova icona de aplicación.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [pulseaudio panel plugin](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/pulseaudio-plugin/start) received MPRIS2 support to be able to remotely control media players and desktop-wide multimedia key support, essentially rendering xfce4-volumed-pulse a superfluous additional daemon.\n"
msgstr "O [engadido de panel pulseaudio](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/pulseaudio-plugin/start) recibiu compatibilidade con MPRIS2 para poder controlar remotamente reprodutores multimedia e compatibilidade coas teclas multimedia para todo o escritorio, convertendo esencialmente a xfce4-volumed-pulse nun servizo adicional superfluo.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:36
#, no-wrap
msgid "And finally the [terminal emulator](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/terminal/start) saw a huge amount of bug fixes and improvements since Xfce 4.12.\n"
msgstr "E finalmente o [emulador de terminal](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/terminal/start) obtivo unha gran cantidade de correccións de erros e melloras desde o Xfce 4.12.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:38
#, no-wrap
msgid "There is also a group of **new projects** that have become part of our project. Say hi to:\n"
msgstr "Tamén hai un grupo de novos **proxectos que pasaron** a formar parte do noso proxecto. Diga ola a:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "We finally have our own [screensaver](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/screensaver/start) (yes - we realize it's 2019 ;)). With lots of features and tight Xfce integration (obviously) it is a great addition to our catalog.\n"
msgstr "Por fin temos o noso propio protector de pantalla (si, dámonos conta de que é 2019;)). Con moitas funcións e unha forte integración Xfce (obviamente) é unha gran adición ao noso catálogo.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "The [status notifier panel plugin](https://goodies.xfce.org/projects/panel-plugins/xfce4-statusnotifier-plugin) provides a next-generation system tray where applications can show indicators. It supersedes the Ubuntu-centric xfce4-indicator-plugin for most application indicators.\n"
msgstr "O [engadido de panel de notificacións de estado](https://goodies.xfce.org/projects/panel-plugins/xfce4-statusnotifier-plugin) fornece unha zona do sistema de nova xeración onde as aplicacións poden amosar indicadores. Substitúe o xfce4-indicator-plugin centrado en Ubuntu para a maioría dos indicadores de aplicacións.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "[Catfish file search](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/catfish/start) is like an old friend for most Xfce users - now it's officially part of Xfce!\n"
msgstr "A [busca de ficheiros Catfish](https://docs.xfce.org/apps/catfish/start) é como un vello amigo para a maioría dos usuarios de Xfce. Agora é oficialmente parte de Xfce!\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:43
#, no-wrap
msgid "Finally [Panel Profiles](https://git.xfce.org/apps/xfce4-panel-profiles/about/), which allows you to backup and restore your panel layouts, has moved under the Xfce umbrella.\n"
msgstr "Finalmente, o [Perfís de panel](https://git.xfce.org/apps/xfce4-panel-profiles/about/), quen lle permite facer copias de seguranza e restaurar a disposición dos seus paneis, moveuse baixo o paraugas do Xfce.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:45
#, no-wrap
msgid "As always it’s also time to say goodbye to some older **unmaintained or deprecated projects**. (Luckily our projects only go to the attic aka the archive on git.xfce.org when they die.) With a salty teardrop of sadness we bid farewell to:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:47
#, no-wrap
msgid "garcon-vala, gtk-xfce-engine, pyxfce, thunar-actions-plugin, xfbib, xfc, xfce4-kbdleds-plugin, xfce4-mm, xfce4-taskbar-plugin, xfce4-windowlist-plugin, xfce4-wmdock-plugin and xfswitch-plugin\n"
msgstr "garcon-vala, gtk-xfce-engine, pyxfce, thunar-actions-plugin, xfbib, xfc, xfce4-kbdleds-plugin, xfce4-mm, xfce4-taskbar-plugin, xfce4-windowlist-plugin, xfce4-wmdock-plugin e xfswitch-plugin\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "An online tour of the changes in Xfce 4.14 can be viewed here:\n"
msgstr "Pode facer unha visita para ver os cambios do Xfce 4.14 aquí:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1565568000.md:53
#, no-wrap
msgid "A detailed overview of the changes between Xfce 4.12 and Xfce 4.14 releases can be found on the following page:\n"
msgstr "Na seguinte páxina pode atopar unha visión detallada dos cambios comparando a versión do Xfce 4.12 coa versión do Xfce 4.14:\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.12 released"
msgstr "Xfce 4.12 publicada"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.12 is be the best release ever (yes, we like to party!)!\n"
msgstr "O Xfce 4.12 é a mellor versión de todas (si, gústanos festexalo!).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Source : Internet comments.\n"
msgstr "Fonte: Comentarios da Internet.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Today, after 2 years and 10 months of work, we are pleased to announce the release of the Xfce desktop 4.12, a new stable version that supersedes Xfce 4.10.\n"
msgstr "Hoxe, despois de 2 anos e 10 meses de traballo, temos o pracer de anunciar a versión de escritorio do Xfce 4.12, unha nova versión estábel que substitúe o Xfce 4.10.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "This long period can only be explained by how awesome Xfce 4.10 was. But as all things, it needed some refreshing - and for that we saw lots of new contributors providing valuable feedback, features and bugfixes. As always, Xfce follows its steady pace of evolution without revolution that seems to match our users' needs.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "In this 4.12 cycle, we mainly focused on polishing our user experience on the desktop and window manager, and on updating some components to take advantage of newly available technologies.\n"
msgstr "Neste ciclo 4.12 centrámonos principalmente na limpeza da nosa experiencia de usuario no xestor de escritorio, xestor de xanelas e na actualización dalgúns compoñentes para aproveitar as novas tecnoloxías dispoñíbeis.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "The main highlights of this release are:\n"
msgstr "Os aspectos máis salientábeis desta versión son:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "The window manager gained a new themable Alt+Tab dialog with optional windows preview and a list mode. Initial Client side decoration support was implemented, window tiling mode was improved providing support for corner-tiling, and a new zooming mode was added. A HiDPI Xfwm theme was also added.\n"
msgstr "O xestor de xanelas gañou un novo diálogo Alt + Tab personalizábel con vista previa de xanelas e un modo de lista opcionais. A compatibilidade inicial para a decoración do lado do cliente foi engadida, o método de axuste de xanelas foi mellorado fornecendo compatibilidade para o recheo de esquinas e engadiuse un novo modo de zum. Engadiuse tamén un tema HiDPI Xfwm.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel can now intelligently hide itself, supports Gtk3 plugins, and saw lots of its third-party plugins updated to take full advantage of the features added in 4.10.\n"
msgstr "O panel agora pode ocultarse de forma intelixente, é compatíbel cos complementos de Gtk3 e moitos dos engadidos de terceiros foron actualizados para sacar o máximo proveito das características engadidas na versión 4.10.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "The desktop has a new wallpaper settings dialog, per workspace wallpaper support, and better multi-monitor handling. It also supports displaying folder cover art and emblems on icons now.\n"
msgstr "O escritorio ten un novo diálogo de opcións de fondo, permite configurarse por espazo de traballo e mellora o manexo para múltiples pantallas. Agora tamén engade a posibilidade de visualización de imaxes para o cartafol e emblemas nas iconas.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Our session manager was updated to use logind and/or upower if available for hibernate/suspend support. For portability and to respect our users' choices, fallback modes were implemented relying on os-specific backends.\n"
msgstr "O noso xestor de sesións foi actualizado para usar «logind» e «addower» se están dispoñíbeis para axudar a hibernar/suspender. Para a portabilidade e para respectar as opcións dos nosos usuarios, engadíronse modos de recuperación baseándose nos indicadores específicos do sistema operativo.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Support for multi-monitor use was improved in a new display settings dialog and a quick setup popup on monitor plugging.\n"
msgstr "A compatibilidade para o uso de múltiples pantallas foi mellorado nun novo diálogo de opcións de visualización e unha xanela configuración rápida que emerxe cando se conecta a pantalla.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "The appearance dialog now showcases previews for icons and themes.\n"
msgstr "O diálogo de aparencia agora amosa vistas previas para iconas e temas.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfsettingsd now supports libinput.\n"
msgstr "O «Xfsettingsd» agora admite «libinput».\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Power management was not forgotten: A new panel plugin was created, logind/upower support was added to handle battery/lid/brightness events, and locking via light-locker was implemented. The settings dialog was also revamped, and support for X11 screenblanking was added.\n"
msgstr "Non se esqueceu a xestión de enerxía: engadiuse un novo engadido de panel, engadiuse compatibilidade «logind»/«upower» para manexar os eventos de batería/tampa/brillo e foi engadido o bloqueo a través do «light-locker». O diálogo de opcións tamén se renovou e engadiuse a compatibilidade para o apagado da pantalla vía X11.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Our file manager, the beloved Thunar, saw an insane amount of improvements: tab support, tons of bug fixes, speed-ups, key shortcuts for custom actions, better naming of file copies and links, nice freespace bar in properties, tweaks for the renamer and other dialogs, improved keyboard navigation, fixes for the treeview pane, better wallpaper support, Gtk3 bookmarks support, multiple file properties... need we say more?\n"
msgstr "O noso xestor de ficheiros, o amado Thunar, recibiu unha gran cantidade de melloras: compatibilidade con lapelas, toneladas de correccións de fallos, melloras na velocidade, atallos de teclado para accións personalizadas, mellor nomeamento de copias de ficheiros e ligazóns, barra de espazo libre nas propiedades, axustes para a renomear e outros diálogos, mellorouse a navegación por teclado, correccións para o panel de vista en árbore, mellorouse a compatibilidade con fondos de escritorio, compatibilidade de marcadores de Gtk3, propiedades de ficheiros múltiples... precisamos dicir máis?\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "To prepare the future of Xfce with Gtk3, which no longer requires theme engines, we are stopping the development of our Gtk theme engine, and dropping our Gtk3 engine - theme makers, please update your themes to CSS if you want them to work on the next Xfce version.\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Due to gstreamer1.0 having dropped the mixer-interface entirely, and xfce4-mixer and xfce4-volumed relying on this interface with gstreamer0.10, our mixer application and volume daemon cannot be ported to 1.0 and are consequently not maintained anymore.\n"
msgstr "Debido a que «gstreamer1.0» deixou completamente de lado a interface de mesturado, e «xfce4-mixer» e «xfce4-volumed» dependen desta interface co «gstreamer0.10», a nosa aplicación de mesturas e servizo de volume non pode ser migrado a 1.0 e, polo tanto, xa non se manterá.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:34
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce wouldn't be what it is right now without all its goodies. In this area, we also saw a flurry of activity, most notably:\n"
msgstr "O Xfce non sería o que é agora sen todos os seus extras. Nesta área, tamén vimos unha grande actividade, entre a que destaca:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfburn gained BluRay Disc burning support.\n"
msgstr "O Xfburn gañou compatibilidade de gravación de disco BluRay.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Task manager UI was totally revamped, and got ported to Gtk3.\n"
msgstr "A interface se usuario do xestor de tarefas foi totalmente renovada e migrouse a Gtk3.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Parole's UI was totally redone, parts of it rewritten with many features added. Furthermore it was ported to Gtk3 and gstreamer1.0.\n"
msgstr "A interface de usuario de Parole foi totalmente refeita, partes dela reescrita con moitas características engadidas. Ademais foi migrado a Gtk3 e «gstreamer1.0».\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Mousepad was totally rewritten and got an initial port to Gtk3.\n"
msgstr "Mousepad foi totalmente reescrito e ten unha migración inicial para Gtk3.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Imgur.com support was added to the screenshooter.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse compatibilidade con Imgur.com á captura de pantalla.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new GNOME-Shell-like dashboard named xfdashboard is now available.\n"
msgstr "Xa está dispoñíbel un novo panel de control tipo «GNOME-Shell» chamado «xfdashboard».\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new alternative menu for the panel named whiskermenu was added.\n"
msgstr "Engadiuse un novo menú alternativo para o panel chamado whiskermenu.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "The GNOME2 hardware monitor plugin was ported to our panel.\n"
msgstr "O engadido de monitorización do soporte físico de GNOME2 foi migrado ao noso panel.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Weather plugin got a totally new user interface with powerful customization options and provides tons of detailed information.\n"
msgstr "O engadido das predicións meteorolóxicas ten unha interface de usuario totalmente nova con opcións para personalizar poderosas e fornece toneladas de información detallada.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Eyes plugin uses 3D coordinates to calculate its eye position, so even more sometimes scary, sometimes funny eyes will spy on you!\n"
msgstr "O engadido de Ollos usa coordenadas 3D para calcular a súa posición nos ollos, para que unhas veces asusten, e outras sexan máis divertidos, mentres o espían.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Netload plugin works with the new udev net interface names and can be configured to show transfer rates in the panel.\n"
msgstr "O engadido Netload funciona cos novos nomes da interface de «udev»net e pode configurarse para amosar taxas de transferencia no panel.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Clipboard manager plugin optionally displays a QR code.\n"
msgstr "O engadido do xestor de portapapeis amosa un código QR opcionalmente.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Cpufreq plugin now supports the intel pstate driver and can adapt better for different panel sizes and information displayed.\n"
msgstr "O engadido Cpufreq agora é compatíbel co controlador pstate de intel e pode adaptarse mellor aos diferentes tamaños de panel e información amosada.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:49
#, no-wrap
msgid "Nearly all plugins have been improved to give the same look and feel and to support the new deskbar panel mode.\n"
msgstr "Case todos os engadidos foron mellorados para dar a mesma aparencia e ser compatíbeis co novo modo do panel da barra de escritorio.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:51
#, no-wrap
msgid "An online tour of the changes in Xfce 4.12 can be viewed here:\n"
msgstr "Pode facer unha visita para ver os cambios do Xfce 4.12 aquí: \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:55
#, no-wrap
msgid "A detailed overview of the changes between Xfce 4.10 and Xfce 4.12 releases can be found on the following page:\n"
msgstr "Na seguinte páxina pode atopar unha visión detallada dos cambios comparando a versión do Xfce 4.10 coa versión do Xfce 4.12:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:63
#, no-wrap
msgid "A warm thank you all the contributors, translators and packagers for your efforts in making this release possible. We would also like to thank our fantastic users and occasional contributors who submitted bug reports, helped us find issues and sometimes provided patches. We are currently reviewing all patches sent to us and will include many more fixes to Xfce in the next release. We would also like to thank the many people who donated money to our project via Bounty Source. This will help us meet and hack on Xfce in the future!\n"
msgstr "Un cálido agradecemento a todas as persoas colaboradoras, tradutoras e empaquetadoras polo seu esforzo en facer posible esta versión. Tamén queremos agradecer aos nosos fantásticos usuarios e colaboradores ocasionais que enviaron informes de erros, axudaron a atopar problemas e ás veces proporcionaron parches. Actualmente estamos revisando todos os parches que nos enviaron e incluiremos moitas máis correccións para Xfce na próxima versión. Tamén queremos agradecer a moita xente que doou cartos ao noso proxecto a través de Bounty Source. Isto axúdanos a xuntarnos a facer que o Xfce sexa aínda mellor no futuro!\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1425081600.md:65
#, no-wrap
msgid "As always, we welcome everyone who would like to contribute to the development of Xfce! You can either [test Xfce](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/building) and [report bugs](https://bugzilla.xfce.org), you can help us with [translations](https://www.transifex.com/tag/xfce/) and [documentation](https://docs.xfce.org), with [usability and user experience](https://wiki.xfce.org/design/start) by packaging Xfce into your distribution, and by [submitting patches](https://wiki.xfce.org/dev/howto/contribute) or entirely new features! You can get in touch with us on the Freenode IRC channel #xfce-dev and our [mailing list](https://mail.xfce.org/mailman/listinfo/xfce4-dev).\n"
msgstr "Como sempre, damos a benvida a quen desexen contribuír ao desenvolvemento do Xfce! Pode [probar Xfce](https://docs.xfce.org/xfce/building) e [informar de fallos](https://bugzilla.xfce.org), pode axudarnos con [traducións](https://www.transifex.com/tag/xfce/) e [documentación](https://docs.xfce.org), con [usabilidade e experiencia de usuario](https://wiki.xfce.org/design/start), empaquetando o Xfce na súa distribución e [enviando parches](https://wiki.xfce.org/dev/howto/contribute) ou funcións completamente novas. Pode poñerse en contacto connosco na canle IRC de Freenode#xfce-dev e a nosa [lista de correo](https://mail.xfce.org/mailman/listinfo/xfce4-dev).\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/news/1335571200.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.10 released"
msgstr "Xfce 4.10 publicada"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1335571200.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "Today, after 1 year and 4 months of work, we are pleased to announce the release of the Xfce desktop 4.10, a new stable version that supersedes Xfce 4.8.\n"
msgstr "Hoxe, despois de 1 ano e 4 meses de traballo, temos o pracer de anunciar a versión de escritorio do Xfce 4.10, unha nova versión estábel que substitúe ao Xfce 4.8.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1335571200.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "In the 4.10 cycle we mainly focused on polishing the desktop and improving the user experience in various ways. Highlights of this release are:\n"
msgstr "No ciclo 4.10 centrámonos principalmente en pulir o escritorio e mellorar a experiencia do usuario de varias maneiras. Os máis destacado desta versión é:\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1335571200.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new application finder that has been completely rewritten and combines the functionality of the old xfce4-appfinder and xfrun4.\n"
msgstr "Un buscador de aplicacións novo que foi completamente reescrito e combina a funcionalidade do antigo «xfce4-appfinder« e «xfrun4».\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1335571200.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "The panel now has an alternative vertical display mode (a deskbar). What is more, panel plugins can be arranged in multiple rows, which is particularly useful in the deskbar mode.\n"
msgstr "O panel agora ten un modo de visualización vertical alternativo (unha barra de escritorio). Ademais, os engadidos de panel poden ser organizados en varias filas, o que é particularmente útil no modo de barra de escritorio.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1335571200.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "A new MIME type editor that allows you to easily change applications used for opening different file types. The mouse and touchpad settings dialog and the settings editor were extended in terms of functionality. The former now supports tablets in a much better way.\n"
msgstr "Un novo editor de tipo MIME que permite mudar doadamente as aplicacións empregadas para abrir diferentes tipos de ficheiros. O diálogo de configuración do rato e da área táctil así como o editor de opcións estendéronse en función da funcionalidade. O primeiro agora admite tabletas dun xeito moito mellor.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1335571200.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "It is now possible to launch applications and open files on the desktop with a single click of the mouse. In addition, the 4.10 desktop can display thumbnails and automatically advance through the wallpaper list.\n"
msgstr "Agora pode iniciar aplicacións e abrir ficheiros no escritorio cun só clic do rato. Ademais, o escritorio 4.10 pode amosar miniaturas e avanzar automaticamente pola lista de fondos.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1335571200.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "The window manager can be configured to tile windows when dragging them to the screen edges. The tab window (Alt+Tab) supports more flexible theming and cursor key navigation.\n"
msgstr "O xestor de xanelas pode configurarse para axustar a mosaico as xanelas ao arrastralas aos bordos da pantalla. A xanela de lapelas (Alt Tab) admite maior flexibilidade en temas de navegación e navegación coas frechas do teclado.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1335571200.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "An online tour of the changes in Xfce 4.10 can be viewed here:\n"
msgstr "Pode facer unha visita para ver os cambios do Xfce 4.10 aquí: \n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1335571200.md:24
#, no-wrap
msgid "A detailed overview of the changes compared to Xfce 4.8 and Xfce 4.10 preview releases can be found on the following page:\n"
msgstr "Na seguinte páxina pode atopar unha visión detallada dos cambios comparando a versión do Xfce 4.8 coa versión preliminar do Xfce 4.10:\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1335571200.md:32
#, no-wrap
msgid "Thank you all the contributors, bug reporters, as well as translators and packagers for your efforts in making this release possible.\n"
msgstr "Grazas a todos os contribuidores, aos informadores de fallos, así como aos tradutores e empaquetadores polos seus esforzos para facer posíbel esta versión.\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/news/1334361600.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.10pre2 released"
msgstr "Xfce 4.10pre2 publicada"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1334361600.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Xfce development team is proud to announce the second preview release for Xfce 4.10. Together with this preview release, the Xfce project announces the string and code (only critical bug fixes or regressions) freeze for the final 4.10 release which is set to be pushed out to the world on April 28th, 2012.\n"
msgstr "O equipo de desenvolvemento do Xfce está orgulloso de anunciar a segunda versión preliminar do Xfce 4.10. Xunto coa publicación da versión preliminar, o proxecto Xfce anuncia o fixado das cadeas a traducir e o código (só se farán correccións de fallos críticos ou as regresións) para o lanzamento final da 4.10 que será publicada para o mundo o 28 de abril de 2012.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1334361600.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "This release incorporates some new features like improved responsiveness of file operations in Thunar and tiling improvements in Xfwm4. Everything else is bug fixes and a _lot_ of translation updates.\n"
msgstr "Esta versión incorpora algunhas características novas como a capacidade de resposta mellorada das operacións de ficheiros no Thunar e melloras do mosaico no Xfwm4. Todo o resto son correccións de fallos e un _bo feixe_ de actualizacións de traducións.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1334361600.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "We hope you will enjoy this release. Please give us feedback by sharing your thoughts, blogging, tweeting or by filing bug reports! With your help, 4.10 will be the best release ever (at least until 4.12)!\n"
msgstr "Agardamos que goce desta versión. Envíenos comentarios engadindo os seus pensamentos, publicando na bitácora, chiando ou achegando informes de fallos. Coa súa axuda, a 4.10 será a mellor versión (polo menos até a 4.12).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1334361600.md:16 content/about/news/1333238400.md:22
#, no-wrap
msgid "Kind regards and thanks to everyone who has contributed to this release,<br />The Xfce development team\n"
msgstr "Saúdos e grazas a todos os que contribuíron a esta versión.<br />O equipo de desenvolvemento do Xfce.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1334361600.md:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "[Download](http://archive.xfce.org/xfce/4.10pre2/)\n"
msgstr "[Descargar](http://archive.xfce.org/xfce/4.10pre2/)\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1334361600.md:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "[Changes in this release](/download/changelogs/4.10pre2)\n"
msgstr "[Cambios desta versión](/download/changelogs/4.10pre2)\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/about/news/1334361600.md:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "[Permalink](/about/news/1334361600/)\n"
msgstr "[Ligazón permanente](/about/news/1334361600/)\n"

#. type: Yaml Front Matter Hash Value: title
#: content/about/news/1333238400.md:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Xfce 4.10pre1 released"
msgstr "Xfce 4.10pre1 publicada"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1333238400.md:8
#, no-wrap
msgid "The Xfce development team is proud to announce the first preview release for Xfce 4.10. Together with this preview release, the Xfce project announces the feature freeze for the final 4.10 release which is set to be pushed out to the world on April 28th, 2012.\n"
msgstr "O equipo de desenvolvemento do Xfce está orgulloso de anunciar a primeira versión preliminar do Xfce 4.10. Xunto con esta versión provisoria, o proxecto Xfce anuncia a fixación de características para a versión final 4.10 que estará lista para o 28 de abril de 2012.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1333238400.md:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "This release incorporates major changes to the core of the Xfce desktop environment and hopefully succeeds in fulfilling a number of long time requests. Among the most notable updates is the new application finder that merges the functionality of the old appfinder and xfrun4. The Panel also has a new vertical mode [aka Deskbar] for better space usage on wide-screen monitors and a new actions plugin. On the settings side the settings helper is integrated in xfsettingsd, saving 1 running process. There is also a reworked settings dialog with categories and pluggable dialogs enabled by default. Basic Synaptics and Wacom settings in the Mouse settings and a new MIME-Type editor. Thunar gained a more polished layout to reduce space usage and more responsive interaction with the thumbnail generator. Because we have not decided on how to merge the desktop functionality into Thunar yet, Xfdesktop has instead received various improvements, including single-click support, desktop icon thumbnails and better pasting of files. The Session Manager has improved power management code, tips have been removed and cleanup sessions from the interface. Last but not least, the Window Manager now has support for tiling windows and arrow key navigation in the task switcher.\n"
msgstr "Esta versión incorpora importantes modificacións no núcleo do contorno de escritorio do Xfce e, con sorte, consegue cumprir unha serie de solicitudes solicitadas hai tempo. Entre as actualizacións máis destacadas está o buscador de aplicacións que combina a funcionalidade do vello «appfinder» e «xfrun4». O Panel tamén ten un novo modo vertical [aka Deskbar] para un mellor uso de espazo en pantallas panorámicas e un novo engadido de accións. No lado das opcións o asistente de configuración está integrado no «xfsettingsd», aforrando 1 proceso en execución. Tamén hai un diálogo de configuración remodelado con categorías e diálogos conectábeis activados de xeito predeterminado. A configuración básica de Synaptics e Wacom foi integrada na configuración do rato. Desenvolveuse un novo editor de tipos MIME. O Thunar recibiu un deseño máis pulido para reducir o uso do espazo e unha interacción máis sensíbel co xerador de miniaturas. Porque aínda non decidimos como combinar a funcionalidade de escritorio en Thunar, Xfdesktop recibiu varias melloras, incluíndo a posibilidade de unha soa pulsación para activar os elementos, miniaturas de iconas de escritorio e un mellor pegado de ficheiros. O xestor de sesións mellorou a xestión de enerxía, elimináronse suxestións e a limpeza de sesións desde a interface. Finalmente, o xestor de xanelas xa admite o mosaico de xanelas e a navegación por teclas de frecha no selector de tarefas.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1333238400.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "Another big change for users is the removal of user documentation of the packages and introduction of [docs.xfce.org](https://docs.xfce.org). The reason for this change is the limited contribution of documentation since Xfce 4.8, so we hope the wiki will attract more contributors. The help buttons in the interface still work, but you'll be asked to open the documentation website in your web browser.\n"
msgstr "Outro gran cambio para os usuarios é a eliminación da documentación do usuario dos paquetes e a introdución de [docs.xfce.org](https://docs.xfce.org). O motivo deste cambio é a contribución limitada da documentación desde o Xfce 4.8, polo que esperamos que a wiki atraia máis colaboradores. Os botóns de axuda na interface aínda funcionan, pero solicitaralle que abra o sitio web da documentación no seu navegador web.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1333238400.md:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "Furthermore we dropped xfce-utils. Its content has either been removed or moved to other Xfce packages. All other dependency changes are listed in the 4.10pre1 ChangeLog. The Xfce core also gained a couple of new components because we think they are critical for a minimal desktop: xfce4-power-manager (power management), tumbler (thumbnail generation for Thunar and other components), garcon (menu library, was already a dependency in 4.8), thunar-volman (volume manager for Thunar).\n"
msgstr "Ademais retiramos o xfce-utils. O seu contido eliminouse ou mudouse a outros paquetes do Xfce. Todos os outros cambios de dependencia están listados no rexistro de cambios da 4.10pre1. O núcleo do Xfce tamén obtivo un par de novos compoñentes porque pensamos que son críticos para un escritorio mínimo: xfce4-power-manager (xestor de enerxía), tumbler (xerador de miniaturas para Thunar e outros compoñentes), garcon (biblioteca de menú, xa tiña dependencia na 4.8), thunar-volman (xestor de volumes para Thunar).\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1333238400.md:18
#, no-wrap
msgid "Of course translations also improved a lot, thanks to the amazing work of our translation teams.\n"
msgstr "Por suposto, as traducións tamén melloraron moito, grazas ao sorprendente traballo dos nosos equipos de tradución.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/about/news/1333238400.md:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "We hope you will enjoy this release. Please give us feedback by sharing your thoughts, blogging, tweeting, denting or by filing bug reports. With your help, 4.10 will be the best release ever (at least until 4.12)!\n"
msgstr "Agardamos que goce desta versión. Envíenos comentarios engadindo os seus pensamentos, publicando na bitácora, chiando ou achegando informes de fallos. Coa súa axuda, a 4.10 será a mellor versión (polo menos até a 4.12)!\n"

